40026055	Jisas re rene keikerem tame nugwape remne op wem. Kem anne potte yawo, kem bisi a tame potbokap yawo. Kem wor paku kirkir sen ek yawo. Mapurke kem etop yawo? An bisi a tame bo. Aboyei yabel an God reri Kworborke wuren sin kemne tuma wesowbem. Opkap kem anne etek kiyi be keikerem?
40026056	Kemri nenbokap kem bupo boker nenbo. Kiyiri tame remri basrasemkap, kem etopwou nenbo. Op wemke, reri anepoi tame rem rene mesegenen amen yim.
40026057	Jisas rene keikerem tame rem rene panen yim. God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Kaiafas, reri akek panen yim. Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame etem, Juda remri keryen tame etem rem etek wuriwouke simenem.
40026058	Rene panen yibem, Pita re remne kaike tiptuwumenem, Kaiafas reri akek yam. Re makelek sin nause yen remkene etek simenem. Rem Jisas rene nente wos late kowen simenem.
40026059	God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yenkene Saberawiykene Tamekene rem tame wuri sopem. Yike tame re Jisas rene tuma yikokote, rem Jisas rene ek pen sate. Etopkap tame rem sopem.
40026060	Nugwape tame rem yan rene tuma yikokom, rem tuma wuriwou be wem. Rem agerbo agerbo tuma wem. Eker keryen yen rem rene pen sate tuma tobo be wuri metem. Sene tame pes rep yan op wem.
40026061	Er tame re kiyi op wem. An God Reri Kwobor berayewon sene yabel murke an sene kebese nente. Kiyi re op wem.
40026062	God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen re teten Jisas rene op wem. Berke repri weye tuma ne tuma sein be webo?
40026063	Jisas re tuma be wuri wem. Re tuma ribo tem. Keryen yen re rene sene yaye op wem. Ne nemne wete. Ne kap yikokote. Ne yikokote, Hevenke tetane God re etop mette. Ne kap God eter lebam tame? Kap ne God Eterri Yen o bo? Ne opu sein we.
40026064	Jisas re sein op wem. Ne tuma sekene weye. More Tame Tem Tame, re gwor nowsel mesegente, kem rene be late. Yuri an Hevenke yaute, an keryen yen ten kitimenakene God reri let mame yokwok sitek, kem anne late. Yuri an nelke sene yate, kem anne late. Op wem.
40026065	Rem op metemke, keryen yen re pap yokem, re reri tame oub keren pekan op wem. Re God rene tuma yaper webo. Reri weye tuma yaper kem metye. Nem agerbo tame remne reri yaper nenbokap sene be wemette, rem nemne be wesowte.
40026066	Kem map habobo? Nem rene berke nente? Rem rene sein op wem. Re yaper weye. Ne rene pen sate, et tuma bo.
40026067	Op wemke, rem reri bitmi sablokwo soboyewon rene letke powyek puwburowem.
40026068	Rane rem reri bitmi subkeren mesegenen rem rene powyek puwburowpiti pete yan op wem. Ne webo, ne Krais, God re nene lebam. Kap et tuma et sekene, ne nemne wete, yike nene peye? Rem rene tame kwuyen etop wem.
40026069	Pita re makelek simenem, God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen reri yaku nen ta te yan lan Pita rene op wem. Kiyi ne Galili tame, Jisas, eterkene sewurbem.
40026070	Op wemke, nugwape tatame rem rene leklek temenem, re tuma nesen op wem. Aren bo. Neri webo tame an be mettene.
40026071	Op wem, Pita re wayen opre yin tetemenem, agerbo ta te rene lam, te etek simenem tame remne op wem. Er tame re Nasaret kwomri tame, Jisas, eterkene sewurbem.
40026072	Pita re op metem, re warege puromon op wem. Neri weye tame an rene be mettene.
40026073	Op wem, kerakap ten etek temenem tame rem rene op wem. Et sekene. Ne Jisas reri anepoi tame remri wuri. Jisas re Galiliri tame. Neri namrebo tuma et Galili tatame remri namrebo tumakap.
40026074	Op wemke, Pita re tuma nowbke op wem. Re warege puromon op wem. An kemne sekenewai webo. An kemne sekenek be wete, God re anne pete. Kemri webo tame an rene be mettene. Op webemke, kwokwo ek wem.
40026075	Wemke, Pita re Jisas reri wem tuma sene ek habom. Jisas re kiyi op wem. Kwokwo be wementek, tewo mur ne ari sig neste. Op sene habomke, re sebera yam, re wuran kenakem kiram.
40027001	Ei berabem, God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Juda remri keryen tame rem wuriwouke sin Jisas rene pen sate tuma namrem.
40027002	Rem rene kepke bogen rene Keryen Yen Pailat reri akek panen yim. Pailat re agerbo nowselri tame, sene re Juda tatame remri keryen yen temenem.
40027003	Jisas rene reri peiktame remne peteram tame, Judas, re metem, rem Jisas rene panen yim, rene tuma nenem. Etop metemke, re wuribai sene habom. Sene habolaweyemke, rem rene newom kel re poten God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yen remne, Juda tatame remri keryen tame remne sene yin op wem.
40027004	Jisas re yaper be nenem. An kemne, rene peteram, an yaper nenye. Kem rene pen sate, kem tame yenbo rene pen sate. Rem sein op wem. Et nemri wos bo. Et neri wos.
40027005	Judas re kel God reri Kwoborke septi wurem, sene re yin kep poten wakke tenen kirpen sam.
40027006	God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen rem God reri akek septi wurem kel poten op wem. Gwor kel et tame pen sate newom kel. Gwor kel nem God reri Kwoborke tetane kel nem etek kirkir sirte, et yaper. Nem etop nente, nem Moses Reri Wule biragiyete.
40027007	Tuma etop namrem, er kel rem poten ou rasbem tame remri sel tupan op wem. Ya tame rem gwor Jerusalem kwomke sate, nem remne er selke pertaite.
40027008	Er sel et gwopte som tetane. Rem sel sig op webo. Nep Yerem Sel.
40027009	Kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Jeremaia, reri basrasem tuma et sekene tem. Er sel rem bupo boker be tupam. Jeremaia reri basrasemkap rem etop tupam. Re op basrasem. Juda tame rem op wem. Nem rene tupate. Nem tame wuriri ok letpeis (30) kel poten rene tupate.
40027010	Er kel rem poten ou rasbo tame remri sel tupate. Haneyen re anne etop nente wem. Jeremaia re op basrasem.
40027011	Rem Jisas rene Keryen Yen Pailat reri bitmik wen tetem, Pailat re Jisas rene wemeten op wem. Ne Juda remri kwom panen si keryen yen? Jisas re sein op wem. Neren ne etop weye.
40027012	Sene God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yen etem, Juda remri keryen tame etem rem Jisas rene tuma yaper wem. Jisas re remri tuma yaper metem, re tuma ribo tem, re sein be wem.
40027013	Pailat re etop lam, re rene op wem. Kap remri nene nenbo tuma ne be mettene? Berke neri nenem woskap ne remne tuma sein be weye?
40027014	Jisas re Pailat reri wem tuma sein be wem. Re wanwouke metem. Op nenem, Pailat re danekene sekem.
40027015	Aboyei nabe Juda tatame rem God Re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabel, keryen yen re pap met wule nenbem, re kwomri tatame remne op wemetbem. Ake yaperke tetane tame wuri rene akwulke wen yite. Kap an yikene wen yite? Kem anne wesowte. Op wemetbemke, rem rene sig wesowbem, re er tame rene akwulke sene wen yibem. Etop nenbem.
40027016	Er yabel tame yaperwai re ake yaperke temenem, reri sig Barabas.
40027017	Nugwape tatame rem wuriwouke simenem, Pailat re remne op wemetem. An yikene wen akwulke yite? An Barabas rene wen yite, o Jisas, rem rene Krais webo, an rene wen yite? Kap. Kem anne wesowte.
40027018	Pailat re etop bupo boker wem. Re metem, Jisas re yaper be nenem, rem rene bupo me pap yokem, rem rene tuma nenem. Eker re Jisas rene werasen akwulke yite selem. Pailat re op habom. Kap rem sene habolaweite, rene sene werasen akwulke yite? Eker re remne etop wemetem.
40027019	Pailat re tuma sin metbo wolbayek simenemke, reri ta te rene tuma sewaipitin op wem. Ne er tame yenbo rene be wos kap nente. Re yaper wos wuri be nenem. Ne rene werasen yite. Neirke an etop nugsi tuknalaye, an pap yaperwai teye. Te rene op sewaipitim.
40027020	God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yen etem, Juda remri keryen tame etem rem nugwape tatame remne tuma wen sewurem. Rem op wem. Kem Pailat rene op wete. Ne Barabas rene werasen akwulke yite, Jisas rene pen sate. Kem rene etop wete. Rem etop wem.
40027021	Sene keryen yen re remne sene wemetem. An yikene werasen re akwulke yite? Rem sein op wem. Barabas eterne.
40027022	Pailat re remne wemetem. Jisas, rem rene Krais webo, eterne an berke nente? Rem sein op wem. Ne me kwuren peiken rene etek peikkerete.
40027023	Pailat re op wem. An reri yaper nenem wos be wuri laye. Kem anne wesowte, re be gwule nenem? Op wemke, rem yaye sein op wem. Rene me kwuren peiken pen sate.
40027024	Pailat re op habom. Ari tuma rem be metbo. Remri weye tuma an be nente, rem eike ten naite. Op habomke, re reri let nugwape tatame remri bitmik ok keyan op wem. An rene pen sate muweye. Kem rene pen sate, et keremri woskem. Et ari wos bo. Kem anne ker kap raste. Eker re remri bitmik let ok keyam.
40027025	Etek temenem nugwape tatame rem op wem. Neri weye tuma nem metye. Nerem, nemri yennankene nem op wete. Nem rene pen sam.
40027026	Op wemke, Pailat re Barabas rene akwulke yite werasem. Re ei nai tame remne op wem. Kem Jisas rene kep sekenak wurbote. Sene rem rene mek kwuren peikerete panen yim.
40027027	Keryen Yen Pailat reri ei nai tame rem Jisas rene keryen yen reri akek panen wurem, nugwape ei nai tame rem yan tetkukwuryewon rene leklek tem.
40027028	Rem rene yikokon rem reri tame oub lug potem, sene rem keryen yen remri kerap, kupkap tame oub rene woleruwen rem rene wukeyebem.
40027029	Sene rem kwokwolobu poten keryen yen remri tare gurere nenen reri tarek gurereruwem. Rem rene sene yikokon sebo pakukap rene wuri newom, rem rene gulke pan rene tame kwuyen op wem. Ne Juda tatame remri keryen yen. Ne heyar temente.
40027030	Op wemke, rem rene sablokwo kwuspan rene newom paku rem sene poten rene tarek pem.
40027031	Rem rene tuma yaper wen mesegenen rem kupkap tame oub sene lug poten reri tame oub sekene rene sene wuruwem. Rem rene panen yin rene me kwuren peikeren pen sate panen yim.
40027032	Rem Jisas rene panen yibem, rene peikkerete me mutame eter re semenem, rem tame wuri, reri sig Saimon, rene lam. Re Sairini kwomri tame. Rem rene neluwen yak rin op wem. Ne Jisas rene kwobo lan rene peikkerete me sen yite.
40027033	Rem kwow eisowke yawum. Kwow sig Golgota. Et sig reri tobo et Tame Tare Bai.
40027034	Rem wain okkene sowkaye okkene luwben rene newom, re alaweyem, re be am.
40027035	Ei nai tame rem rene mek peikkeren rem reri tame oub wesate, teya lite, yike tame re reri tame oub potte.
40027036	Etop nenemke, rem rene peikkerem emik sin leklek tebem.
40027037	Rem me wulale wuri poten tuma etek basrasen reri tare ya yokwok peikkerem. Remri rene nenem tuma rem op basrasem. GWOR JISAS. RE JUDA ETEMRI KERYEN YEN. Op basrasem.
40027038	Sene rem bisi abem tame pes repne me kwuren peiken peikerem. Wuri rene rem Jisas reri let mame yokwok teteruwem, wuri rene reri let giriy yokwok teteruwem.
40027039	Jisas re etek peikkeremenem, tatame rem er kelowke yi yabem, rem rene lan tame kwuyebem, tare kwarbem.
40027040	Rem op webem. Ne kiyi op wem. An God Reri Kwobor berayewon yabel murke sene nente. Op wem. Rem rene op wem. Ne God Eterri Yen, ne kworer kwobo late, ne me mesegenen sene yerte. Rem rene tame kwuyen etop webem.
40027041	God Reri Kwoborke yaku nenbem tame remri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame etem, Juda remri keryen tame etem mere, rem tame kwuyen op wem.
40027042	Kiyi re tatame remne kwobo labem, gwopte re kworer kebese be late. Re kiyi wem. An Juda remri keryen yen. Re me mesegenen yertek, nem lan op wete. Et sekene, re Keryen Yen.
40027043	Kiyi re wem. An God Eterri Yen, God re anne kwobo late. Op webem, gwopte nem late. Kap God re rene kwobo late o bo? Rem op webem.
40027044	Bisi abem tame pes, repne me kwuren peiken peikkerem tame pes, etop mere rep rene etopwou tame kwuyebem.
40027045	Yabel nina let kere temenemke, nowsel neir tektekwunem, yabel sene ek pasem.
40027046	Yabel sene ek paste nenbem, Jisas re remri tumak yaye op tem. Eli, eli, lema sabaktani. Er tuma tobo re gwop. Ari Apiy God, ne berke anne mesegenye?
40027047	Op wemke, rane tame rem etek meknik temenem, rem reri wemkap kebese be metem, rem op wem. Metye. Re kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, eterne kap tebo.
40027048	Remri tame wuri re amen yan yam owb poten sen yan kwole yabem wain okke sokwunen keyen gwonik leyen Jisas rene ate sen tetem. Jisas re ate muwem.
40027049	Rane tame rem op wem. Wai. Nem late. Kap God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, re rene kwobo late yerte o bo?
40027050	Jisas re tewo wuriwou taye yaye piten reri wow kworer werasen yin re ek sam.
40027051	God Reri Kwobor eismenem mate re ya yokwok pekan yeren kelare kelare tem. Nina bukre yam, pa bukre rem borke pekam.
40027052	Sele mei nugwape rem tagwoyewom, God reri kiyi sam tatame nugwape rem wow sene poten rem sele mei mesegenen yim.
40027053	Yuri Jisas re sele mesegenen sene wayen sim yabel, sele meike wayem tame rem Jerusalem kwomke yim, nugwape tatame rem remne etek lam.
40027054	Ei nai tamekene remri keryen yenkene rem Jisas rene leklek temenem, rem ninakene agerbo woskene lam. Rem kenakem aken op wem. Sekenewai. Er tame re God Eterri Yen.
40027055	Rane ta rem kaike kera teten labem. Kiyi Jisas re Galili mesegenen yam, er ta rem rene sumowen yan rene kwobo labem.
40027056	Er ta remri wuri te Makdala kwomri Maria. Wuri te agerbo Maria, Jemskene Josepkene etepri nawo. Wuri te Sebedi reri yen pes repri nawo.
40027057	Perpe Arimatea kwomri tame, kelkene tame, re yam. Reri sig Josep. Re Jisas reri tuma omuteke habobem tame.
40027058	Re Pailat rene yin Jisas reri kupa potte rene wemetem. Pailat re kirkir tem, rem Jisas reri kupa Josep rene newom.
40027059	Josep re poten wulkap mate agerke leirasem.
40027060	Leirasen sen yim, Josep reri yeki nenem pa puri rem kupa etek rasem. Rem pa bukre gelkwun yan pa puri eru rageren rem akwulke sene yim.
40027061	Makdala kwomri Maria te agerbo Mariakene rep etek pa puri meknik sin lakerebem.
40027062	Jisas re samke, kwokwos God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yenkene Farisi tamekene rem Pailat rene lasyin op wem.
40027063	Haneyen, nem tuma wuri haboye. Kiyi er yikoko tame, Jisas, re temenem, re op wem. An sate, yabel mur tetek, an sene wayen site. Re op wem.
40027064	Ne kirkir wete, ei nai tame rem yin yabel mur sele lakerebet. Jisas reri anepoi tame rem kap yan reri kupa bisi kap poten tatame remne kap op yikokote. Jisas re selek sene wayen sim. Rem op yikokote, et kiyi yokokom tuma teitkwunte tetane.
40027065	Op wemke, Pailat re op wem. Kem ei nai tame remne panen yite, rem sele heyar lakerebet.
40027066	Rem remne panen yin sele rem heyar ragerem. Rem yop lekten etek rasruwem, rem ei nai tame remne wen lakerebem.
40028001	Juda tatame remri Egesi Yabel kiyi temke, ei berabemke, Makdala kwomri Maria, agerbo Maria tekene rep sele late yim.
40028002	Yibemke, nina ek yam, God reri kwomri tame wuri re nelke yan yerem. Re pa puri eru ragermenem pa gelkwunen re pa luwke simenem.
40028003	Er tame reri bitmi oknelkap malebem. Reri tame oub et wulkapwai.
40028004	Er sele lakerebem nause tame rem rene lam, rem aken polpolen selke waren tuknateren sa tamekap tem.
40028005	Ta rep yam, God reri kwomri tame re repne op wem. Kep mane akte. An metye. Mek kwuren peiken peikkerem Jisas rene kep late yawo.
40028006	Re gwor be tetane. Re sene wayen siye. Kiyi re op wem. An sate, an sene wayen site. Reri wem tumakap re etop nenem. Re wayen siye. Kep opu yan la. Reri kupa rasem emi kep late.
40028007	Kep agetage sene yin reri anepoi tame remne op wete. Re selek sene wayen sim. Re Galili yokwok kemne temnas yim. Kem rene etek yin late. Kep etop wesowte.
40028008	Op wemke, ta pes rep akem, rep sele mesegenen amen yim. Rep akem, rep okbop kirkir tem. Op temke, rep anepoi tame remne wesowte yim.
40028009	Yibem, Jisas re repne kelowke lan repne pir wem. Rep op metem, rep gulke pan reri tewo keren rene lom yokwom.
40028010	Jisas re repne op wem. Kep mane akte. Kep yin ari mase remne op wete. Kem Galilike yite, kem anne etek late. Op wete.
40028011	Ta pes rep yibemke, sele lakere ei nai tame rem kwomke sene yim. Rem God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen remne remri lam wos wesowem.
40028012	God Reri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yenkene Judari keryen tamekene rem er tuma namrem. Rem ei nai tame remne kel nugwape newon op wem.
40028013	Kem tatame remne tuma yikokon op wete. Neir nem tuknamenye, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem yan reri kupa bisik potye. Tatame remne kem etop wesowte.
40028014	Kemri keryen yen re etop mette, re eike tetek, nem rekene namrete, re kemne be pete. Rem op wem.
40028015	Nause tame rem kel poten keryen tame remri wem tuma rem tatame remne etop yikokom. Juda tatame rem er tuma omuteke habom. Gwopte mere rem som omuteke metbo.
40028016	Jisas reri anepoi tame, letpeis wuri kere tame, rem Galilike yim, rem Jisas reri wem kwowke yin yawum.
40028017	Rem Jisas rene lam, rem rene lom yokwom. Rane rem wuribai pes ten op habom. Kap gwor tame re Jisas o re agerbo tame?
40028018	Jisas re mekni yan remne op wem. God re anne kitimena newom, an nowselkene nelkene kwom panen site.
40028019	Eker kem yin nugwape nowselri tatame remne ari tuma remne wesowte. Rem ari tame tete, kem remne okke tirmunte, kem Apiy reri sig, ari sig, God Reri Wow reri sigkene wen remne okke tirmunte.
40028020	Ari kemne wesowem tuma kem tatame remne wete, rem er tuma meten nente. Tuma wuri kem kap serte. An kemne be mesegente. An keremkene som temente tetane. Nowselkene nelkene yaper tete yabel an keremkene som temente tetane.
41001001	Jisas Krais re God Reri Yen. Reri Tuma Yenbo gwotek basrastene.
41001002	Aisaia re God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, re tuma kiyi siglowke op basrasem. Kem wan tai. Gwor tame re ari tuma wesowte tame. An rene weraste, re temnas yin ari tuma wesowte, re neri yate kelow heyar nente. (Malakai 3:1)
41001003	Tame wuri re tamekene bo emik temente, re yaye op tete. Haneyen re yate. Kem reri yate kelow heyar nen. (Aisaia 40:3)
41001004	Opkap Jon re etek yam. Re tamekene bo emik yin temenem, re tatame remne tuma op wesowbem. Kem keremri yaper nen wos mesegente, an kemne okke panen waren tirmunen nenewayete. God re keremri yaper nen wos poten ek septite, re kemne tuma sene be wete.
41001005	Judia nowselri tatame, Jerusalem kwomri tatame rem aboyei Jon rene lasyim. Rem remri yaper nenbem wos wesowemke, Jon re remne Jordan Peikke panen waren okke tirmunem.
41001006	Jon re kamel por weske nenem tame oub wubem, re somokep borborke simenem. Re boulri awos, muskene wiyi yenkene abem.
41001007	Re tuma wesowbem, re op wem. An temnas yam, tame wuri re tiptuwu yate tetane. Re tame bukre, re tame yenbowai. An tame eisow. An tame yenbo bo, nes wolbaye wurik be site. An eisow yen, an selke site.
41001008	An kemne okke waren tirmunte. Yuri yate tame re God Reri Wow kemne newote.
41001009	Yuri Jisas re Nasaret kwom mesegenen yim. Nasaret kwom et Galili yokwok tetane. Re Jordan Peikke yin tem, Jon re rene Jordan Peikke waren tirmunem.
41001010	Jisas re ok mesegenen wayen niruw labem. Gwan berabem, God Reri Wow re nelke ap bourkap yan yeren Jisas rene yeren sim.
41001011	Tuma wuskiy wuri nelke op wem. Ne areri meseke mogul Yen. An nene okbop tebo.
41001012	God Reri Wow re Jisas rene werasem, re tamekene bo emik yim.
41001013	Re neir tame pesri ok, yabel tame pesri ok etek temenemke, gambo remri keryen yen, Satan, re rene seilabem. Re temenem emi hekna habona tame tabo por tob rem etek temenem. God reri kwomri tame rem yan rene heyarbem.
41001014	Yuri Jon re ake yaperke temenem, Jisas re Galili yokwok yin God Reri Tuma Yenbo etek wesowen op wem.
41001015	God re Keryen Yen, re kwom panen site yabel matnaye. Kem wuribai yaper mesegente, sene kem wuribai yenbo pot. Kem God Reri Tuma Yenbo meten omuteke habote.
41001016	Jisas re Galili wame barke sewurbem, re lakemase per Saimonkene Andrukene repne lam. Rep omyen potbem tame, rep wuli wamek rasen omyen potbem.
41001017	Jisas re repne op wem. Kep arenkene yite. Kep omyen potbokap sene an kepne muwkuwteken peterate, kem tatame etopkap potte.
41001018	Op wemke, agetage rep etepri wuli mesegenen rekene yim.
41001019	Re kera sene yibem, re agerbo lakemase per, Jemskene Jonkene, repne lam. Rep Sebedi reri yen. Rep perek sin wuli let mate nabem.
41001020	Jisas re repne yate wem. Hakene reri yaku nenbem tamekene rem perek temenem, rep remne mesegenen Jisas rekene yim.
41001021	Rem yim, rem Kaperneam kwomke yan tem, Egesi Yabel ten Jisas re God reri akek wuren tatame remne tuma wesowem.
41001022	Rem reri tuma metem, rem danekene sekem. Re remne Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame remri wesowbemkap be wesowem. Keryen yen remri wesowbemkap re remne etop wesowem. Opkap rem danekene sekem.
41001023	Et yabel gambo gureremenem tame wuri re God reri akek temenem, re yan wuram.
41001024	Re yaye op wem. Jisas, ne Nasaret kwomri tame. Ne kap nesne berke nente? Kap, ne nesne botkute yawo? An nene latene. Ne God reri tame yenbo. Re nene werasen yam.
41001025	Jisas re rene tuma op wem. Ne elen me te. Ne tame rene pelebiten yi.
41001026	Gambo re tame rene selke terem, tame reri let tewo negnegem. Gambo re taye piten tame rene mesegenen yim.
41001027	Nugwape tatame rem op lam, rem danekene sekem, rem etemwou etemwou op wemetem. Et mapkap tuma? Jisas re kitimenakene keryen yenkap webo. Gambo rem reri tuma metbo, rem tame mesegenen yibo.
41001028	Agetage Galili yokwori tatame aboyei rem Jisas reri nenem wos metkeipem.
41001029	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem God reri ake mesegenen yim, Saimonkene Andrukene repri akek yin wurem. Jonkene Jemskene rep kirkir yin wurem.
41001030	Saimon reri owyit te yaper metem, te tiyke tuknamenem. Jisas re akek wuram, egegekene rem rene op wem. Gwot ta te yaper metbo.
41001031	Jisas re yin tene let keren nenewayen siruwem. Op nenem, teri yaper boyem, te wayen remne awos nenem.
41001032	Yabel warbem, tatame rem sikanuma nenbem tatame, gambo gureremenem tatame remne panen Jisas rene lasyam.
41001033	Nugwape kwomri tatame rem ake eruk yan teteyewom.
41001034	Jisas re hekna habona sikanuma nen tatame remne heyarbem, re gambo remne wekroken yim. Gambo rem Jisas rene sanem, eker Jisas re remne sewayem, rem tuma kap namrete.
41001035	Neir tepke Jisas re wayen ek yim. Re tatame be temenem emik yim, re Apiy God rekene tuma namrem.
41001036	Saimon, rekene temenem tamekene rem Jisas rene sopen yim.
41001037	Rem rene lam, rem rene op wem. Nugwape tatame rem nene late yawo.
41001038	Jisas re remne op wem. Etop mesegente. Nem agerbo agerbo kwomke yite. An remne tuma kirkir wesowte. An er yaku nente yam.
41001039	Jisas re Galili yokwok yin sewurbem, re kwomri kwomri God reri akek wuren tuma wesowbem, gambo remne wekrokbem.
41001040	Numape tame wuri re yan gulke pan Jisas rene op wem. Ne selte, ne anne heyarte, an yenbo sene tete.
41001041	Jisas re rene pap metem, re rene let kerelan op wem. An nente selbo. Ne heyar sene te.
41001042	Tuma egegekene rene temenem pemenem numa re sok tem, re heyar tem.
41001043	Jisas re rene werasen omuteke op wem.
41001044	Metye. An nene heyar nenye. Ne yike tamene etop kap wesowte. Ne sagunan yin neri wes God reri Kwoborke yaku nenbo tame rene peterate. Re nene lakeipte, ne Moses re kiyi wemkap, ne etop nente, ne God rene kwar pete. Op nentek, sage tatame rem mette, ne heyar tetane.
41001045	Er tame re yin nugwape tatame remne Jisas re nenemkap wesowem. Op tem, tatame nugwape rem Jisas rene late wem, Jisas re kwomke mapurke yim. Tame be temenem emik re etek yin temenem. Kwomri kwomri tatame nugwape rem rene etek lasyam.
41002001	Yuri Jisas re Kaperneam kwomke sene yim, tatame rem lam, re akek temenem.
41002002	Etop lam, nugwape tatame rem wurik wurem, ake aboyei pulawem. Tatame rem yan ake eru tetlaweyem. Jisas re ake purik temenem, re tuma etek wesowbem.
41002003	Tame eis rem yam, rem kuw let tewo negel met tame wuri rene sen yam.
41002004	Tatame nugwape yan temenem, ake pulaumenem, rem er tame rene mapurke etek sen wurte wem. Sen wurlaweyen rem rene ake magelke sen yawum, ake ropo okmei wuri regen tamewopkene newokwunem. Rem Jisas reri gwai ganke newokwunen rasem.
41002005	Jisas re lam, rem reri kitimena omuteke habobem, eker re kuw let tewo negel met tame rene op wem. Areri yen, an neri wule yaper poten septiye.
41002006	Op wemke, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem op metem, rem remri wuribaike op habom.
41002007	Er tame re mapurke etop webo. Re God rene tuma yaper webo. Tame rem wule yaper be poten septibo. God eterwou re poten septibo. Rem op habom.
41002008	Jisas re remri wuribai lam, re remne wemetem. Kem berke opkap wuribai teye?
41002009	Be yaku et yaku bukre? An er kuw let tewo negel met tame rene wete, neri yaper nen wos an poten septiye. O an rene wete, ne wayen teten neri tukna wos poten sen yi?
41002010	An More Tame Tem Tame, an kemne peterate, God re anne kitimena newon an nowselri tatame remri yaper nen wos kebese poten septite. Kem la. Op wemke, re kuw let tewo negel met tame rene op wem.
41002011	An nene webo. Ne wayen teten neri tukna wos poten sen akwulke yi.
41002012	Tatame rem leklek temenem, tame re wayen teten reri tukna wos poten sen ek yim. Rem etop lam, rem danekene seken God rerne tuma yenbo op webem. Opkap wos nem kiyi be lam.
41002013	Jisas re kwom mesegenen Galili wame barke sene yim. Nugwape tatame rem yan wuriwouke wurem, re remne tuma wesowem.
41002014	Re sene yibem, re Livai rene lam. Livai re Alfius reri yen, re takis kel potbem akek sin tatame remri kel potbem. Jisas re rene op wem. Ne arenkene yite. Re wayen Jisas rekene yim.
41002015	Nugwape takis kel potbem tame, yaper wos nenbem tame rem Jisas reri tuma metem, rem rene semowbem. Jisas re Livai reri akek yin sin awos abem, rene semowbem rane tame rem Jisas rekene reri anepoi tamekene kirkir sin abem.
41002016	Moses Reri Wule tuma peikbem tamekene Farisi tamekene rem lam, Jisas re takis kel potbem tamekene yaper wos nenbem tame remkene sin abem, rem Jisas reri anepoi remne op wemetem. Mapurke Jisas re takis kel potbo tame remkene yaper wos nenbo tame remkene awos sin abo.
41002017	Jisas re remri wem tuma metem, re remne sein op wem. Heyar tetane tatame rem dokta rene be lasyibo. Sikanuma nen tatame etemwou rem dokta rene lasyibo. Rane tatame rem kworer op habobo. An tame yenbo. Opkap tatame an remne kwobo be late yam. Rane tatame rem kworer op habobo. An tame yaper. Opkap tatame an remne kwobo late yam. Jisas re op wem.
41002018	Tewo wuri tatame remne Okke Waren Tirmunbo Tame, Jon, reri anepoi tamekene Farisi tamekene rem ok tuknaben God rene habobem. Rane tatame rem yan Jisas rene op wemetem. Berke Jon reri anepoi tamekene Farisi tamekene rem wule yenbo sebo, rem ok tuknabo, neri anepoi tame rem wule yenbo be sebo, rem ok be tuknabo?
41002019	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Tame re ta panete, re reri tametiy remne ta pane kisen awos ate ten yate. Kap, rem ok tuknabo? Yehow. Ta panete tame re remkene temente, rem ok be tuknate.
41002020	Yuri tete yabel wuri rem ta panete tame rene poten panen yite, rem ok ek tuknate tetane.
41002021	Tame rem weyartene mate suba tetane, rem mate meg ager be poten etek kambo. Etop nente, weyartene mate suba re bukrewai sene weyarte.
41002022	Re tuma sene op wem. Yuri nenem wain ok, tatame rem kiyiri ok tibo girbuw subak be yewobo. Op nentek, yuri nenem wain ok re wayen pulaubo wule, girbuw suba re pekan ok re selke sirpitibo. Op tebo, girbuw re yaper tebo. Yuri nenem wain ok rem girbuw agerke yewobo.
41002023	Yuri Egesi Yabel tem, Jisas reri anepoi tamekene rem wit nowke yibem, reri anepoi tame rem yin wit supa kwosbem.
41002024	Farisi tame rem etop lam, rem Jisas rene op wem. Ekla. Neri anepoi tame rem Egesi Yabelke wit supa kwosen abo, rem nemri wule biragiyebo. Et yaper.
41002025	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Devit re kiyi temenem keryen yen. Re kiyi nenem wos rem basrasem, kem kap er tuma be latene. Devit reri anepoi tamekene rem sikwoi sam, rem kap be awos am?
41002026	Sikwoi samke, rem God reri akek wurem. Er yabel Abiatar re temenem, re God reri akek yaku nen tame remri keryen yen. Devit re God rene newon rasem geil poten am. Re rekene temenem tame remne newon am. Nemri wule rem biragiyen am. Nemri wule gwopkap. God rene newobo geil God reri akek yaku nen tame remwou rem abo. Agerbo tame rem be abo. Devit reri anepoi tamekene rem am, God reri akeri tame rem remne tuma be wem.
41002027	Jisas re remne sene op wem. God re tatame remne kwobo late habom, eker re Egesi Yabel nenem. Tatame rem Egesi Yabel kwobo late, re be wem.
41002028	Egesi Yabel re More Tame Tem Tame reri kulke tetane. Jisas re op wem.
41003001	Jisas re God reri akek sene wuren lam, ya yaper tame re etek temenem.
41003002	Rane tame rem Jisas rene tuma nente kelow sopte wem. Op tem, rem rene leklek temenem, rem op habobem. Gwopte et Egesi Yabel. Re kap ya yaper tame rene heyar nente o bo? Re op nente, nem rene tuma wete.
41003003	Jisas re ya yaper tame rene op wem. Ne gwok ya.
41003004	Jisas re tatame remne op wemetem. Moses Reri Wule re nemne map webo? Egesi Yabel nem berke nente? Egesi Yabel nem tatame remne yenbo wos nente, o nem remne yaper wos nente? Egesi Yabel nem tame rene kwobo lan heyarte, o rene pen sate? Op wem, rem tuma sein be wem.
41003005	Jisas re remne lan kwuren re remne pap yokem. Rem purerekene bo, rem mangure tem, eker re remne pap kirkir metem. Re ya yaper tame rene op wem. Ne let tai. Tame re let tayem, reri let heyar tem.
41003006	Farisi tame rem God reri ake mesegenen yim, rem Herot reri sukuw remkene namrem. Rem op wem. Nem Jisas rene pen sate.
41003007	Jisas re reri anepoi tame remkene wamek yim. Nugwape Galili yokwori tatame rem rekene yim.
41003008	Judia yokwori tatame, Jerusalem kwomri tatame, Idumea yokwori tatame, Jordan Peik yabel waibo yokwok temenem tatame, Tairkene Saidonkene kwom sag pes meknik temenem tatame rem aboyei yam. Jisas reri nenbem wos rem metem, eker rem rene lasyim.
41003009	Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. Nugwape tatame rem anne kap yan teitkukwur yewote. Eker kem anne pere wuri poten meknik tete.
41003010	Jisas re nugwape tatame remne heyar nenbem, eker nugwape sikanuma tatame rem rene kerelate natginbem.
41003011	Gambo gureremenem tatame rem rene lamke, rem gulke pan rene yaye op tem. Ne God Reri Yen.
41003012	Op temke, Jisas re gambo remne werageren op wem. An God Reri Yen. Kem tatame remne etop mane wesowte.
41003013	Sene Jisas re kwowke yawun re rane tame remne wen yam.
41003014	Jisas re letpeis tewo pes kerem tame remne lebam. Re remne op wem. Kem arenkene tete. An kemne weraste, kem kwomke kwomke yin ari tuma wesowte.
41003015	An kemne kitimena newote, kem omugambo remne ari kitimenak kebese wekrokte.
41003016	Letpeis tewo pes kerem tame remri sig gwor. Wuri re Saimon, Jisas re rene agerbo sig Pita tem.
41003017	Agerbo pes rep Jemskene reri mase Jon rekene. Rep Sebedi reri yen. Jisas re agerbo sig repne tem. Sig et Boanerges. Sig tobo gwopkap. Wakte kwute tame.
41003018	Agerbo rem Andru, Filip, Bartolomyu, Matyu, Tomas, Jems. Jems re Alfius reri yen. Agerbo rep Tadiuskene Saimon Selotkene.
41003019	Agerbo re Judas Iskariot. Yuri re Jisas rene yena tem.
41003020	Jisas re akek yim, nugwape tatame rem etek sene duwem. Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene, rem yaku bukre nenem, rem awos be am.
41003021	Tatame rem Jisas rene op wem. Re me beleye. Op wem, eker Jisas reri nawo, reri mase rem reri nenem yaku tuma metem, rem rene panen yite yam.
41003022	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem Jerusalem kwomke mesegenen yam, rem op wem. Satan re gambo remri keryen yen. Reri agerbo sig Belsebul. Re Jisas rene gureren rene kitimena newobo, eker re gambo remne wekrokbo.
41003023	Op wem, Jisas re tatame remne wen yam, re sikur sakur tuma remne op wem. Re remne wemetem. Satan re mapurke kworer werokbo?
41003024	Keryen yen wuri reri anepoi tame rem pekan etemwou etemwou naite, rem sou be tete. Rem yikwute yakwutete tetane.
41003025	Ha wuri reri yen rem etemwou etemwou naite, rem sou be tete. Rem yikwute yakwutete tetane.
41003026	Satankene arkwu gambokene rem opkap tete. Satan re reri anepoi tamekene naitek, rem sou be tete. Rem yikwute yakwutete, rem heyar sou be tete.
41003027	Jisas re sikur sakur tuma sene op wem. Tame yaper re kitimenakene tame reri akek wuren wos potte wete, kiyi re yin er kitimenakene tame rene kepke poten bograste. Bograstek, re kebese wuren wos ek potte.
41003028	An kemne sekeneker webo. Tatame rem wule yaper nentek, rem tuma yaper wete, God re er yaper nen woskene tuma yaperkene poten septite, re remne tuma sene be wete.
41003029	Tatame rem God Reri Wow rene tuma yaper wete, God re remri wule yaper be poten septite. Gwopte, yuri mere, re remri yaper wos be poten septite.
41003030	Rane tatame rem op wem. Gambo re Jisas rene gureretene, eker re gambo remne wekrokbo. Op wemke, Jisas re remne er tuma eker wem.
41003031	Jisas reri nawokene masekene rem yan kwom geike tetpete wuramenem. Rem Jisas rene tuma wepoten op wem. Nem nekene tuma namrete.
41003032	Op wemke, nugwape tatame rem Jisas rekene meknik simenem, rem rene op wem. Metye. Neri nawokene masekene rem nene kwom geike kowen tebo.
41003033	Jisas re sein op wem. Ari nawo, ari mase, an kemne peterate.
41003034	Rekene meknik simenem tatame Jisas re remne lan kwuren op wem. Ekla. Gwor tatame rem ari nawokene gesmasekene.
41003035	Tatame rem God Reri Tuma meten sete, er tatame etem rem ari nawokap ari gesmasekap. Re remne op wem.
41004001	Yuri Jisas re Galili wame barke yin temenem, re tatame remne tuma etek sene wesowbem. Tatame nugwapewai rem yan tetkukwur yewom, eker re perek waren simenem. Pere re wamek temenem, nugwape tatame rem wame barke tetyewomenem.
41004002	Re nugwape sikur sakur tuma remne wesowbem, remne op wem.
41004003	Metye. Tame re wit supa nowke yin seiten sewurem.
41004004	Rane supa rem kelowke yerem, ap rem yan akeipem.
41004005	Rane supa rem pa luwke yerem, sel om bo, pawou temenem. Op temke, agetage wit supa rekwan bupo me wayem.
41004006	Supa remri nen eisow temenem, yabel pasem, rem sok ten sayewom.
41004007	Rane supa rem negiri esekwaye somok yeren rekwan sim, negiri esekwaye rem punen borgeyem, rem supa be yam.
41004008	Rane supa rem sel yenbok yeren rem rekwan bukre tem, supa nugwape yam. Rane rem supa tame wuriri ok letpeis (30) yam. Rane rem supa tame murri ok (60) yam. Rane rem supa nugwapewai (100) yam.
41004009	Re sene op wem. Wan tetane tatame kem wan wurik mette.
41004010	Nugwape tatame rem sene yim. Jisas re, letpeis tewo pes kere anepoi tame remkene agerbo tamekene rem temenem, rem Jisas rene sikur sakur tuma tobo wemetem.
41004011	Jisas re remne op wem. God re kwom panen site tuma, et berastene tuma. An wesowbo, keremwou kem tuma tobo heyar sanebo. Agerbo tatame an remne sikur sakur tumawouke webo.
41004012	Rem wos labo, rem wos tobo be labo. Tuma rem wanwouke metbo, rem tuma tobo be sanebo. Rem heyar sanete wem, rem God rene omuteke habote wem. God re remri yaper nen wos poten septite wem.
41004013	Jisas re remne op wemetem. Ari weye sikur sakur tuma kem metye o kem be metye? Kem be metbo, yuri wete sikur sakur tuma kem mapurke mette?
41004014	God Reri Tuma wesowbo tame re wit supa seiten sewurem tamekap.
41004015	Tatame rem tuma bupo me metbo, rem kelowke yerbo wit supakap. Rem metbo, sene Satan re yabo, re er tuma poten septibo.
41004016	Rane tatame rem tuma metbo, rem pa luwke yerbo supakap. Rem tuma agetage poten okbop tebo.
41004017	Sene rem tuma heyar be sebo. Yaper wos remne tebo, o tame rem remne tame kwuyen yaper nenbo, rem God Reri Tuma mesegenbo.
41004018	Rane tatame rem tuma metbo, rem negirikene esekwayekene somok yerbo wit supakap. Rem God Reri Tuma metbo,
41004019	rem nowselri woskene kelkene metkereke woskene habobo, er wos remne penen borgeibo. Rem God Reri Tuma sene be habobo, reri yaku be nenbo.
41004020	Rane tatame rem tuma metbo, rem sel yenbok yerbo supakap. Rem tuma meten pap yewobo, rem God reri yaku op nenbo. Supa rem 30 supa yabokap, rem God reri yaku yenbo kera nenbo. Supa rem 60 supa yabokap, rem God reri yaku nugwape kera nenbo. Supa rem 100 supa yabokap, rem God reri yaku nugwapewai nenbo.
41004021	Jisas re remne op wemetem. Tatame rem lam yaren sen wurbo, rem mak tukbo? Rem ouke gumkerebo? Rem tukna tiy kulke tukbo? Yehow. Rem op be nenbo. Rem tiyke tukbo.
41004022	Gwopte berastene wos yuri nugwape tatame rem heyar late tetane. Gwopte nugwape wos subtene, yuri rem mette tetane.
41004023	Kem wan tetane, kem wan wurik mette.
41004024	Be tuma kem mette, kem heyar meten habote. Be tuma o be wos kem tatame remne se petekap, God re kemne sene etopkap se pete tetane. Re kemne kenakem se pete.
41004025	Wuribai yenbo tetane tame rem ari tuma metbo, rem tuma tobo kirkir metbo. Er tame an remne tuma nugwape som wesowte. Wuribai yaper tetane tame rem ari tuma kera metbo, tuma tobo rem be metbo, er tame remri kera metbokap, an sene potte tetane.
41004026	Jisas re tuma som op wesowem. God reri panen si kwom re gwopkap. Tame re awos supa seitbo.
41004027	Neirke er tame re tuknabo, yabel re sewuren yaku nenbo. Op nenbo, awos supa rem rekwan wayebo. Tame re be labo, awos supa mapurke rekwan wayebo.
41004028	Awos supa selke rekwan sibo. Kiyi yig pam temenbo, yuri take senen sibo, kworekwore tebo, ge senen supa yabo.
41004029	Awos okwobo wule, now mutame re kita sen yin awos peren sen yan ek abo.
41004030	Jisas re remne wemetem. God reri panen si kwom kem mapkap late? An kemne sikur sakur tuma wuri wesowte.
41004031	God reri pane si kwom et mastet awoskap. Reri supa et agerbo supa sikabekap bo. Et supa eisowsubuwai. Tame re er supa poten reri nowke rasbo.
41004032	Sene supa rem rekwan sibo, yuri rem bukre tebo. Agerbo me rem eisow, er me re bukrewai. Er me re tewo bukre, ap rem yan reri tewok tawek sibo, reri take kulke nes etek kwutebem.
41004033	Jisas re tatame remne agerbo agerbo sikur sakur tuma wesowbem. Rem reri tuma habobem, re remne agerbo sene wesowbem. Rem kebese be habobem, re remne agerbo sene be wesowbem.
41004034	Jisas re remne sikur sakur tumawou wesowbem. Yuri Jisas re anepoi tamekene rem wiysage temenem, re remne sikur sakur tuma tobo ek heyar wesowbem.
41004035	Yabel warbem, Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. Nem peik kelaruwke kwuren wute.
41004036	Op wemke, rem nugwape tatame remne mesegenen yim. Jisas re simenem perek anepoi tame rem etek waren rene panen yim. Agerbo pere rem kirkir etek yim.
41004037	Yibem, marye bukre yam, ok burow perek teyen yewobem, pere ok pulaute nenbem.
41004038	Jisas re pere berai yokwok mate tare suwk putuwen tuknamenem. Anepoi tame rem rene teren sin rene op wem. Nem sate nenbo. Ne nemne pap be metye.
41004039	Jisas re wayen tetem, re maryekene ok burowkene sewayen op wem. Kep tebei. Op wem, maryekene okburowkene tebeyem.
41004040	Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. Kem berke akbo? Kem anne omuteke be habobo. Ari kitimena kem be habobo.
41004041	Rem kenakem akem, rem etemwou etemwou namren op wem. Gwor yike tame? Maryekene ok burowkene rep reri tuma meten tebeiwo.
41005001	Rem sene yibem, rem Galili wame kelaruwke wun Gerasa remri yokwok yim.
41005002	Rem pere gairuwen yan tame wuri re tame sele emik sewurbem, re Jisas rene lasyam. Er tame rene gambo gureremenem.
41005003	Er tame re sele emik temenem. Re kitimena bukre, tatame rem rene keikeren bograslaweyem. Rem kitimenakene kep mere rem bograslaweyem.
41005004	Tewo nugwape rem rene let tewo kitimenakene kepke rene bogbem, re let kep roberasbem. Re pa poten tewo bogbem kep etek regrasbem. Re kitimena bukre, rem rene heyar be keikerebem.
41005005	Aboyei yabel re sele kelowke yibem, kwowke yibem, re taye yaper pitbem, re pa poten reri wes retebem.
41005006	Op tem, Jisas re kaike temenem, er tame re rene lam, re amen yan gulke pam.
41005007	Re Jisas rene yaye op wem. Jisas, ne Ikya Tetane Keryen Yen God Reri Yen. Ne anne berke nente? God reri sigke ne anne pap met. Ne anne kap pete. Re op wem.
41005008	Kiyi Jisas re gambo rene op wem. Ne tame rene mesegen. Opkap, tame re er tuma Jisas rene etop wem.
41005009	Jisas re rene wemetem. Neri sig be? Re sein op wem. Ari sig Nugwape Ei Nai Tame. Nem gambo nugwape, opkap ari sig Nugwape Ei Nai Tame.
41005010	Op wem, re Jisas rene tewok tewok webem. Setate. Hadebas. Ne nemne agerbo emik mane wekroken yite. Op wem.
41005011	Por nugwape rem meknik temenem, rem kwowke an sewurbem.
41005012	Gambo rem Jisas rene op wem. Ne nemne wekrokte, ne nemne wen por remne yin gurerete.
41005013	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem opu yi. Op wemke, gambo rem tame rene mesegenen yin por remne yin gurerem. Er por rem agetage amekiren yin emi yaperke warkwuten peikke kirpen rem ok an sayewom. Por rem nugwapewai (2,000).
41005014	Por lakerebem tame rem etop lam, rem amekiren yin kwom sagri tatamekene boul kwomri tatamekene remne remri lam wos wesowbem. Tatame rem metem, rem er wos late yim.
41005015	Jisas rene, kiyi gambo gureremenem tame rene rem repne late yim. Er tame kiyi reri sig rem op webem. Nugwape Ei Nai Tame. Yin lam, tame re tame oub wun etek simenem. Reri wuribai heyar sene tem. Tatame rem rene lam, rem akem.
41005016	Er wos remri lek lam tatame rem agerbo tatame remne etop wesowem. Gambo re tame rene gurerem tumakene por tumakene rem remne wesowem.
41005017	Tatame rem etop tuma metem, rem Jisas rene op wem. Ne nemri sel mesegenen yi. Rem akem, rem etop rene wem.
41005018	Jisas re perek waren yite nenem, kiyi gambo gureremenem tame re rene kwobke op wem. An nerenkene yite.
41005019	Jisas re rene sewayen op wem. Ne neri akwulke sene yi. Ne neri tame tep remne lasyite. Keryen Yen re nene pap metye, nene yenbo wos nenye tuma ne remne etop wesowte.
41005020	Op wem, tame re yin Dekapolis yokwori tatame remne wen sewurbem. Re op wem. Jisas re anne heyar nenem. Tatame rem op metem, rem danekene sekem.
41005021	Jisas re perek waren Galili wame kelaruwke sene yim, tatame nugwape rem rene lasyam.
41005022	God reri akek yaku lakerebo tame wuri, reri sig Jairus, re yam. Re Jisas rene lam, re yan re Jisas reri tewo tobok waren rene op wem.
41005023	Areri yen te sate nenbo. Ne yan tene let kerete, te be sate. Te heyar tete.
41005024	Op wemke, Jisas re rekene yim. Nugwape tatame rem rekene naleren yibem, Jisas re borborke tem.
41005025	Op tem, ta wuri te wuta suwbem, nabe letpeis tewo pes kerem, te wuta suwbem.
41005026	Te mus bukre metbem, te dokta nugwape remne lasyibem, te teri tokwo remne ab newobem. Op tebem, wuta be tebeibem, te wuta bukrewai som suwbem.
41005027	Op tem, te Jisas reri nenbemkap metem, te nugwape tatame remkene yan reri kin yokwok yan tetem.
41005028	Te op habom. An reri tame oub let keretek, anne suwbo wuta tebeite.
41005029	Te let kerem, teri suwbem wuta tebeyem, te metem, teri wesom kwuye metem.
41005030	Agetage Jisas re metem, te reri kitimena potem. Re petkwo lan nugwape tatame remne op wemetem. Yike ari tame oub let kereye?
41005031	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem rene sein op wem. Ekla. Nugwape tatame rem nekene nalaren yibo. Berke ne op weye, yike anne let kereye?
41005032	Jisas re lan kwuren reri oub let kerem ta som sopem.
41005033	Ta te habom. Anne suwbo wuta tebeiwo, an kwuye metye. Reri kitimena anne heyarye. Te etop metem, te aken polpolen Jisas reri tewo tobok gulke pan te op wem. Aren, an nene let kereye.
41005034	Jisas re tene op wem. Ari yen, ne anne omuteke op haboye. Re anne heyar nente. Opkap neri suwbo wuta tebeiwo. Ne pap yenbo ten yin site.
41005035	Jisas re tekene som namrebem, tame rem Jairus reri ake mesegenen yan Jairus rene op wem. Neri yen te saye. Ne Tuma Peikbo Tame rene kap panen yate.
41005036	Jisas re er tuma metem, re Jairus rene op wem. Ne mane akte. Ne anne omuteke habote.
41005037	Op wem, re rene bogen yibem tatame remne op wem. Kem gwotek temen. Pita, Jems, reri mase Jon, remwou rem ankene yite.
41005038	Op wem, rem God reri akek yaku nenbem tame reri akek yan Jisas re lam, nugwape tatame rem kiraterbem.
41005039	Jisas re akek wuren op wem. Kem berke opkap kiraterbo? Er yen te be satene. Te bupo me tuknatene.
41005040	Op wem, rem rene sak keyeterem. Jisas re nugwape tatame remne wekrokem, re et yen teri nawoha etop, rekene temenem tame, rem yen teri tukna emik yin wurem.
41005041	Jisas re yen teri let keren Hibru tumak op wem. Talita, kum. Er tuma tobo re gwop. An nene webo. Yen, ne opu wayen si.
41005042	Op wemke, agetage yen te wayen teten sewurem. Yen teri nabe letpeis tewo pes kere temenem. Tatame rem op lam, rem danekene sekem.
41005043	Jisas re remne op sewayem. Kem mane wesowte. Re remne sene op wem. Kem et yen tene awos newon ate.
41006001	Jisas re er emi mesegenen re reri maime kwom Nasaretke yim. Reri anepoi tame rem rekene yim.
41006002	Egesi Yabel tem, Jisas re God reri akek wuren remne tuma wesowem. Nugwape tatame rem reri tuma metem, rem danekene seken op wem. Nugwape tuma yenbowai re wesowbo. Purere lei yike rene newom? Yike rene opkap tuma peikem? Re bukre wos nenbo, kitimena re mak potem?
41006003	Re ake nenbo tame. Re Maria teri yen. Re Jems, Josep, Judas, Saimon remri lake. Reri gesi rem nemkene tetane. Op wemke, rem rene magel tayem.
41006004	Jisas re remne op wem. God Reri Tuma wesowbo tame remne agerbo kwomri tatame rem op webo. Rem tame yenbo. Reri tame beigkene reri kwomri tatamekene rem remne magel taibo. Jisas re op wem.
41006005	Opkap Jisas re nugwape bukre wos reri maime kwomke be nenem. Re sikanuma nen tame pesketwou repne let kerem, rep kwuye metem.
41006006	Tatame rem rene omuteke be habobem, Jisas re etop metem, re danekene sekem. Jisas re et yokwori kwomke kwomke sewurbem, tatame remne God Reri Tuma wesowbem.
41006007	Jisas re reri anepoi tame, letpeis tewo pes kere tame, remne wen yam. Re remne pesri pesri kwomke kwomke werasen yite op wem. An kemne kitimena newote, kem gambo kebese wekrokte.
41006008	Kem kwomke kwomke yite, kem nugwape wos mane sete. Kwokulwou kem sete. Awos, ayer, kel kem mane sete.
41006009	Kem tewo bus wute. Tame oub pes kap sen yite. Wuriketwou wute, et yow.
41006010	Re remne sene op wem. Kem ma kwomke yite, kemne pap yewobo tame reri akewouke ten yin sene ek yite.
41006011	Kwomri tatame rem kemne pap be yewote o kemri tuma be mette, kem remri kwom mesegenen yite. Kem tewo sibuw nubtite. Rem op latek, rem op wete. Nem repne yaper nenye, yuri God re nemne yaper sein nente tetane.
41006012	Op wemke, letpeis tewo pes kerem tame rem kwomke kwomke yin tuma wesowbem. Rem op webem. Kem wuribai yaper mesegente, kem wuribai yenbo potte.
41006013	Rem gambo nugwape remne wekrokbem, nugwape sikanuma nenbem tatame remri tarek kwar kerebem, tatame rem kwuye metbem.
41006014	Nugwape tatame rem Jisas reri nenbem wos namrebem, Keryen Yen Herot re op metem. Rane tame rem op webem. Tatame remne Okke Waren Tirmunbem Tame, Jon, re sam, re selek sene wayen yim, opkap re kitimenakene re bukre wos nenbo. Op webem.
41006015	Rane tatame rem op webem. Re Elaija. Re God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame. Rem op webem.
41006016	Herot re Jisas reri nenbem wos metem, re habon op wem. Re tatame remne Okke Waren Tirmunbem Tame, Jon. Kiyi an rene wak regen re ek sam, re selek sene wayen yim.
41006017	Jon reri sam tuma gwopkap. Kiyi Herot re Jon rene keikeren kepke bogen ake yaperke wen wurem. Bupo bokem. Herot re reri mase Filip reri ta, Herodias, tene kerepoten panem.
41006018	Kiyi Jon re Herot rene op webem. Neri mase reri ta ne tene kerepoten panem, et yaperwai. Ne etop nenem, ne wule biragiyem. Herot re etop metem, re pap yoken re tame werasen yin Jon rene keikeren ake yaperke wen wurem.
41006019	Herot reri ta, Herodias, te Jon rene pap kirkir yokem. Te habom. An tame rene werasen Jon rene pen sate. Te rene pen sate selem, Herot re tene sewayem, te op be nenem.
41006020	Herot re habom. Jon re tame yenbowai. Op habom, Herot re Jon rene ake yaperke berasem, tame wuri re rene kap pete. Herot re Jon reri tuma mette selbem. Re tewok tewok metbem, re pap yaper meten wuribai pes tebem.
41006021	Yabel wuri nugwape tatame rem yan Herot rekene wurem, rem Herot rene nawo wurem yabel habon awos nenem. Yam tame rem gwop. Rem gavman tame, ei nai taresi tame, Galili yokwori keryen tame. Awos nenem, Herodias te habom. Gwopte yabel an Jon rene pen sate.
41006022	Op temenem, Herodias teri yen, te muyensi yen ta, te wuran teten yage taibem. Herot re agerbo tamekene sin awos abem, rem teri taibem yage lam, rem okbop tem. Herot re tene op wem. Nem nene okbop tebo. Ne be wos potte selbo, ne anne wete, an nene newote.
41006023	Re warege puromon op wem. An nene sekeneker webo. An nene newote tetane. Ne ari tetkeren sitene susag potte wete, an borke kwosen nene newote, ne potte.
41006024	Op wemke, muyensi yen ta te wuren nawot Herotias tene op wemetem. An rene be wos wemette? Nawo te sein op wem. Tatame Remne Okke Waren Tirmunbo Tame, Jon, reri tare ne wemette.
41006025	Op wemke, agetage te wuran Keryen Yen Herot rene op wem. Ne Tatame Remne Okke Waren Tirmunbo Tame, Jon, rene wak regen reri tare ne warek yewon anne newote.
41006026	Op wemke, Herot re pap yaper tem. Re Jon rene wak regte muwem. Re sene habom. Nugwape tatame rem arenkene awos abo, rem ari tene weye puromon tuma metye. Teri weye tuma an etop nente.
41006027	Herot re reri ei nai tame wuri werasen yim, rene op wem. Jon reri tare ne sen yate. Ei nai tame re ake yaperke yin Jon rene wak regem.
41006028	Re reri tare warek yewon sen yin muyensi yen ta tene newom. Te poten sen yin nawo tene newom.
41006029	Jon reri anepoi tame rem etop metem, rem yan reri kupa poten pertayem.
41006030	Jisas reri werasen yi tame rem sene Jisas rekene wuriwouke wurem. Remri nenbem yaku, remri peikbem tuma rem Jisas rene wesowem.
41006031	Nugwape tatame rem etek yi yabem, Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem yaku bukre nenbem, rem awos be am. Jisas re remne op wem. Kem arenkene yite. Nem tamekene bo emik yin egesite.
41006032	Op wemke, rem pere poten tamekene bo emik yin tem.
41006033	Nugwape tatame rem etop lan op wem. Jisas re yibo. Op wem, nugwape tatame rem aboyei kwom mesegenen selke amekiren yim. Tatame rem kiyi temnan kelowke yim, yuri Jisas re perek yam.
41006034	Jisas re yan gayen re nugwape tatame remne lam, re remne pap meten op habom. Rem sipsipkap. Remne lakere tamekene bo. Opkap re remne nugwape tuma peikbem.
41006035	Kweikwei webem, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem rene yan op wem. Yabel warbo. Gwo emi et tamekene bo emi.
41006036	Ne tatame remne meknik tetane kwomke remne werasen yite, rem awos tupate.
41006037	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kerem, kem remne awos newon ate. Rem rene sein wemetem. Ne map habobo, nem 200 kel rasen awos ek tupate?
41006038	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem geil mapsen tetane? Kem opu yin la. Rem yin lan op wem. Nem geil letrane, omyen sok peswou tetane.
41006039	Jisas re nugwape tatame remne op wem. Kem girik girik topke site.
41006040	Rem girik girik sim, tatame tame letraneri ok (100) rem girik girik sim. Rane rem tame pesri ok letpeis (50) girik girik sim.
41006041	Jisas re geil letrane, omyen sok pes poten nelke neruwen God rene wese an mesegenem, re geil belokteyewon reri anepoi tame remne newom. Rem poten tatame remne newopiti pete yam. Sene re omyen sok pes poten pekayewon reri anepoi tame remne newom. Rem poten tatame remne newopiti pete yam.
41006042	Rem ab an si ketem.
41006043	Geil tep, omyen tep temenem, anepoi tame rem eip poten yewon sewuren eip letpeis tewo pes kerem etop pulawem.
41006044	Awos am tame rem nugwapewai (5,000).
41006045	Sene Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. Kem pere agetege waren peik kelaruwke kiyi temnan yite. Kem Betsaida kwomke yi. Re etek ten nugwape tatame remne remri akwulke sene werasen yim.
41006046	Remne pir wen mesegenen re kwowke God rekene tuma namrete yawum.
41006047	Neir tektebem, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem perek yibem, rem peik mei borke temenem. Jisas re wiysage wame barke temenem.
41006048	Jisas re remne lam, remri piyabem pere tewo be liyesebem. Poli marye me natbanebem. Ei berate nenbemke, Jisas re ok luwke remne lasyim. Re remne pelebitete nenbem,
41006049	reri anepoi tame rem lam, Jisas re ok luwke yabem, rem taye piten op wem. Ekla, er gambo.
41006050	Rem aboyei rene lan kenakem akem, Jisas re remne op wem. Kem mane akte. Gwor aren. Kem mol tete.
41006051	Op wemke, re perek yin waren sim, marye tebeyem. Rem danekene seken op habo op habom.
41006052	Kiyi Jisas re nugwape tatame remne awos newon am, reri anepoi tame rem etop lam, rem heyar be sanen wor tem. Eker rem danekene sekem.
41006053	Rem wame kelaruwke kwuren wun Genesaret kwomke yin gayen pere etek tenem.
41006054	Rem barke yaukwutem, tatame rem yan Jisas rene agetage lan sanem.
41006055	Sene rem er yokwori kwomke kwomke yin tatame remne etop wesowem. Rem metem, rem sikanuma nenem tame remne tamewopke poten sen yam, Jisas re temenem emik etek yan rasbem.
41006056	Jisas re mak sewurbem, eisow kwomkene kwom sagkene, tatame rem sikanuma nenem tatame remne poten sen yam, kwom genek sen yan rasbem. Rem Jisas rene omuteke op webem. Sikanuma nenbo tatame rem neri wutene tame oub tumakupa nem kerete, rem kwuye mette. Tame oub kerem tatame rem aboyei kwuye metem.
41007001	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem Jerusalemke yan temenem, Farisi rem remkene ten rem Jisas rene lasyim.
41007002	Rem lam, Jisas reri rane anepoi tame rem awos abem, rem Farisi etemri wulekap let ok be keyabem.
41007003	Farisi tamekene Juda tatamekene rem yeiwarenge remri wule ab sebo, rem let ok keyabo wule sen awos ek abo.
41007004	Rem get yin awos tupan sen yabo, rem awos ok kiyi keyan remri let ok kiyi kirkir heyar keyan ek abem. Rem kwusi, ou, weti ware, tukna tiy, aboyei ok keyabo. Yeiwarege wule rem nugwape sebem.
41007005	Opkap Farisi tame, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem Jisas rene wemetem. Neri anepoi tame rem yeiwarege wule be setene. Rem awos abo, rem let ok be keyabo. Mapurke rem opkap nenbo?
41007006	Jisas re remne op wem. Aisaia re kemne habon tuma sekene basrasem. Kem tuma yikokobo tame. Re op basrasem. Gwor tatame rem anne tuma yenbo bupo me webo. Rem anne pap be yewobo.
41007007	Rem tamek nenbo wulewou peiken op webo. Gwor wule et God reri wule. Eker rem anne bupo me lom yokwobo. (Aisaia 29:13)
41007008	Jisas re sene op wem. Kem God reri wule mesegenem, kem tame remri wulewou setene.
41007009	Kem kemri wule setene, kem op habobo. Nem God reri wule setene. Nem heyarke nenbo. An kemne sekeneker webo. Kem God reri wule be setene.
41007010	Moses re kiyi op wem. Kem nawoha repne heyar nente. Re sene op wem. Tame re nawoha repne tuma yaper wetek, er tame rene kem pen sate.
41007011	Kerem, kem agerbo tuma op webo. Tame re nawoha repne wos newote weye, sene er wos re God rene newote weye. Etop weye, yuri nawoha rep yan yen rene, remne newote wos wemette, re repne be newote.
41007012	Er tame re op nenbo, re nawoha repne yaper nenbo.
41007013	Kem opkap tuma peikbo, kem God reri wule biragiyebo. Nugwape yaper wos kem etop nenbo. Jisas re op wem.
41007014	Jisas re nugwape tatame remne sene wen yam, re remne op wem. Kem aboyei wan tai. Kem purere pot.
41007015	Tame abo awos et tame remne yaper be nenbo. Yehow. Tame remri wuribaike wurabo wos, et rene yaper nenbo.
41007016	Wan tetane tatame kem heyar met.
41007017	Op we mesegenen Jisas re tatame remne mesegenen akek wurem. Reri anepoi tame rem er sikur sakur tuma tobo rene wemetem.
41007018	Jisas re remne op wem. Kerem mere, kem purerekene bo. Kem be sanetene. Tame rem awos abo, rem yaper be tebo.
41007019	Awos et tame remri wuribaike be wurbo? Yehow. Tame rem awos abo, er awos re sigowkke warbo. Sene er sigowkke tetane awos et mekwokrek yibo. Jisas reri wem tuma tobo re gwo. Aboyei awos tatame remkene ate.
41007020	Jisas re op wem. Tame rem be wos nente o be tuma wete, er woske tame rem yaper tete.
41007021	Tame remri wuribai yaper tetane, rem yaper wos nenbo, rem yaper wos habobo. Rem takene kep pebo, rem bisi abo. Rem alwo pi pebo.
41007022	Rem remri ta pelebiten agerbo takene kep pebo. Rem wos nugwape potte habobo. Rem agerbo agerbo wos yaper nenbo. Rem yikokobo. Rem wule yenbo be nenbo. Rem ayekutebo. Rem tatame remne yaper webo, rem kworer sig bukre webo. Rem purerekene bo.
41007023	Er yaper wos, tame rem remri wuribaike habobo, er woske tame rem yaper tebo. Jisas re op wem.
41007024	Jisas re wayen teten re er kwom mesegenen Taia kwomri yokwok yim. Re ake wurik wurem. Tatame rem reri temenem emi mette, re muwem. Re kworer beraslaweyem. Tatame rem metem, re yan temenem.
41007025	Ta wuri te metem, Jisas re gambo wekrobo. Et ta te yentenyen wuri akwulke mesegenem. Gambo re er yen tene gureremenem. Et ta te agetage yan Jisas reri tewo tobok warem.
41007026	Ta te Juda ta bo, te Fonisia yokwo, Siria nowselri ta. Te Jisas rene omuteke op wemetem. Setate. Ne ari yen teri gambo wekrokte.
41007027	Jisas re tene sein op wem. Nem yen remne awos kiyi newon ate. Nem yen remri awos kap poten wale remne kap newote.
41007028	Te sein op wem. Haneyen, yen rem awos abo, awos tep selke yerbo, wale rem yan poten abo.
41007029	Jisas re tene sein wem. Ne heyar sein weye, an neri yen heyar nenye. Ne tene lasyite. Gambo re neri yen tene mesegenye.
41007030	Op wemke, ta te akwulke sene yin lam, yen te tiyke heyar me tuknamenem. Gambo re kiyi yim.
41007031	Jisas re Taia kwomri yokwo mesegenen re Saidon kwomri yokwok yim. Sene re Dekapolis yokwo yin mesegenen Galili wamek yim.
41007032	Tatame rem tame wuri panen yam. Er tame re wan tektemenem, tuma tibo temenem. Rem Jisas rene omuteke op wem. Ne rene let raste, re heyar tete.
41007033	Jisas re er tame rene panen nugwape tatame remne mesegenen yin etepwou temenem. Jisas re tame reri wan tauk let bor etek rasen sablokwo kwuspan re let bor tame reri taulek kerem.
41007034	Re nel niruwen yumu apowem, er tame rene Hibru tumak op wem. Efata. Tuma tobo et neri wan puyekete.
41007035	Op wemke, reri wan puyekem, taule yenbo tem, re tuma welepem.
41007036	Jisas re er tame rekene rep tatame rem temenem emik sene yim, re tatame remne op wem. Kem agerbo tatame remne ari nenye wos bukre kap wesowte. Jisas re remne sewayem, rem be berasbem, rem me wesowbem.
41007037	Tatame rem er tuma metem, rem danekene seken op webem. Re aboyei wos yenbo nenbo. Wan tektemenem tatame rem tuma sene metbo. Tuma tibo temenem tatame rem tuma sene namrebo. Jisas re remne kebese heyarbo. Tatame rem op webem.
41008001	Rane yabel tem, nugwape tatame rem sene wuriwouke wurem. Remri kereneyam awos rem ab akeipem, Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne wen yam. Re remne op wem.
41008002	An tatame remne pap metye. Yabel mur rem arenkene tetane, remri kereneyam awos rem ab akeipem.
41008003	Rem kai kwomke yam. An remne sene akwulke werasen yite, an remne awos be newon an ek yite, rem kap kwoiwurig san kelowke le parerete.
41008004	Op wemke, reri anepoi tame rem rene wemeten sein wem. Nem geil mak poten newon ate? Gwor tamekene bo emi.
41008005	Jisas re remne sein wemetem. Kem geil mapsen tetane? Rem op wem. Nem letrane kelare pes kere tetane.
41008006	Jisas re tatame remne op wem. Kem selke site. Sene re geil letrane kelare pes kere poten God rene wese am, re geil belokteyewon reri anepoi tame remne newom. Rem nugwape tatame remne newopiti pete yam.
41008007	Rem omyen pes eisow temenem, Jisas re poten God rene wese an reri anepoi tame remne newon op wem. Kem tatame remne newopiti pete yate.
41008008	Rem wesan newopiti pete yam, tatame rem an si ketem. Reri anepoi tame rem awos tep poten eip letrane kelare pes kere etek yewon pulawen sim.
41008009	Awos am tame rem nugwapewai, 4,000.
41008010	Jisas re tatame remne werasen yim, sene re, reri anepoi tamekene rem yin pere poten Dalmanuta yokwok yim.
41008011	Rem Dalmanuta yokwok yam, Farisi tame rem yan Jisas rekene nauram. Rem Jisas rene op wemetem. Ne God reri yaku nen tame, ne nemne kitimena bukre wos peterate, nem op wete. God re nene werasen yam. Op wem, rem Jisas rene seilam.
41008012	Jisas re etop metem, re pap yaper tem, re yumu apowen op wem. Gwopte tetane tatame mapurke rem anne kitimena bukre wos nente webo? An kemne sekene webo. Gwopte tetane tatame rem kitimena bukre wos be late.
41008013	Jisas re Farisi tame remne mesegenen yim, re reri anepoi tamekene rem pere waren peik kelaruwke sene wum.
41008014	Anepoi tame rem wuribai seremke, rem geil be poten sen yam. Geil wuriketwou perek yewomenem.
41008015	Jisas re remne ei me pen op wem. Kem heyar met. Kem Farisi tamekene Herotkene remri geil pelbo wos, yis, kem kap potte. Et wos yaper.
41008016	Anepoi tame rem op metem, rem etemwou etemwou op namrem. Nem geil be sen yawo, re eker weye.
41008017	Jisas re remri tuma metem, re op wem. Kem mapurke op webo, nem geil bo? Kap, ari kitimena kem be habobo? Kap, kem wor teye?
41008018	Kem le tetane, kem be latene. Kem wan tetane, kem be mettene. Kiyi nem awoskene bo. Kap, an nenem wos kem me serem?
41008019	Kiyi an geil letrane belokteyewom, nugwape tame (5,000) remne newon am. Tep kem eip mapsen poten yewon pulawem? Rem sein op wem. Nem eip letpeis tewo pes kerem yewon pulawem.
41008020	Jisas re sene wemetem. Kiyi an geil letrane kelare pes kerem poten belokteyewom, nugwape tame (4,000) remne newon am, tep kem eip mapsen poten yewon pulawem? Rem sein op wem. Nem eip letrane kelare pes kerem op yewon pulawem.
41008021	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem etop lam, sene kem ari kitimena be habobo. Kem wor teye. Jisas re etop wem.
41008022	Rem yin Betsaida kwomke gayem. Kwomri tatame rem le si tame rene panen yan Jisas rene op wem. Ne gwor le si tame rene let rastek, re heyar tete.
41008023	Jisas re le si tame rene let keren panen yin kwom mesegenen opre kera yin re tame reri le sablokwo kwuspan re reri let tame reri lek rasen rene op wemetem. Ne wos labo?
41008024	Le si tame re op wem. Ekeya. An tatame remne labo, an remne me yi yabokap labo.
41008025	Jisas re let reri lek sene rasen le si tame re le welepe lam.
41008026	Jisas re tame rene akwulke werasen yin rene op wem. Ne kwomke mane wurte.
41008027	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Betsaida kwom mesegenem, rem Sisaria Filipai kwom sagri meknik tetame kwomke kwomke yim. Rem kelowke sewurmenem, Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wemetem. Tatame rem map webo, an yike?
41008028	Rem rene sein op wem. Rane rem op webo. Ne Jon, kiyi tatame remne Okke Warben Tirmunbem Tame. Rane rem op webo. Ne Elaija, God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame. Rane rem op webo. Ne God Reri Tuma wesowbem tame remri tame wuri.
41008029	Jisas re anepoi tame remne sene wemetem. Kerem, kem anne map webo, an yike? Pita re sein op wem. Ne Krais, God Re Lebam Tame.
41008030	Jisas re remne op wem. Et sekene. Kem agerbo tatame remne kap wesowte, an Krais.
41008031	Jisas re remne tuma op weiwem. An More Tame Tem Tame, an nugwape mus mette tetane. Juda etemri keryen tame, God Reri Kwoborke yaku nenbo tame etemri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbo tame rem anne magel tayen pen sate. Yabel pes tete, murwek God re anne wetek, an wow sene poten sene ek wayen site tetane.
41008032	Re remne tegek tuma etop wem, Pita re Jisas rene opre kera panen yin rene tuma op wem. Jisas ne etop mane wete.
41008033	Jisas re agerbo anepoi tame remne petkwo lan Pita rene tuma wem. Satan, ne sekiy. Neri weye tuma an kap mette. Et God reri wuribai bo. Et tame remri wuribai.
41008034	Op tem, Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene nugwape tatamekene remne wen yan op wem. Kem anne anepoi yite, kem gwopkap nente. Kem kworer teitkwunte. Kem kemri kwurtene me sete. Kem anne semowte.
41008035	Kem kworer wesomwou habote, yuri kem yaper tete tetane. Kem anne omuteke habon ari tuma yenbo kirkir omuteke habote, rem kemne pen sate, kem somsom heyar temente tetane.
41008036	Kem map habobo? Tatame rem nugwape nowselri wosbas potte, sene rem ker kwomke yite, et wos yenbo remne kwobo late? Yehow. Rem yaper tete tetane.
41008037	Tatame rem yenbo sene mapurke tete. Rem kel mapurke rasen sene yenbo tete.
41008038	Gwopte nugwape tatame rem God rene be habobo, rem wos yaper nenbo. Etop tetane, kem remri bitmik anne sebera yan ari tuma remne wesowte akte, More Tame Tem Tame re God reri kwomri tame yenbowai remkene reri Ha reri yabel rik pasrasbo wulek sene yate yabelke yate, re kemne sebera sein yate.
41009001	Jisas re remne sene op wem. An kemne webo, rane gwotek tetane tatame rem be samentek, rem late, God reri panen sibo kwom re kitimenakene yate. Rem etop late. Jisas re op wem.
41009002	Yabel letrane kelare wuri kere yimke, Jisas re Pita, Jems, Jon remne panen kwow bukrek yawum. Rem etemwou yawun etek temenem, rem op lam. Jisas reri wesom ligen agerbo tem.
41009003	Reri wumenem tame oub wulkapwai malebem. Selri tame rem opkap wulkap wos be nenem.
41009004	Jisas reri anepoi tame mur rem lam, kiyi temenem tame pes, Elaijakene Moseskene rep God reri kwomke yan yeren etek temenem, rep Jisas rekene tuma namrebem.
41009005	Rem etop lam, Pita re Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, nem gwotek tetane, et yenbo. Nem yabelake mur mauken nem etek tete. Neri wuri, Moses reri wuri, Elaija reri wuri nem etop maukte.
41009006	Rem aken be tuma wete habolaweyen Pita re eker etop wem.
41009007	Op wemke, nel gwan yan remne yan wusopetem. Gwanke yam tuma wuskiy rem metem. Er webem tuma re op wem. Er ari meseke mogul Yen. Kem reri tuma met.
41009008	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem petkwolam, Jisas eterwou re temenem. Rem agerbo tame be lam.
41009009	Rem kwow mesegenen yerbem, Jisas re remne sewayen op wem. Kemri laye wos kem gwopte kap wete. An More Tame Tem Tame, an sate, sene an wayen site yabel kemri laye wos kem ek wesowte.
41009010	Remri lam wos rem be wesowem, rem etemwou etemwou namren op wem. Jisas re op weye. An selek sene wayen site. Mapurke re selek sene wayen site?
41009011	Rem Jisas rene op wemetem. Moses Reri Wule peikbo tame rem op webo. God reri tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, re kiyi temnan yate, Krais re tiptuwu yate. Rem mapurke etopkap webo?
41009012	Jisas re remne sein wem. Rem sekeneker webo. Elaija re kiyi temnan yam, re Krais reri yate kelow nowbem. Kiyi rem tuma op basrasem. More Tame Tete Tame re nugwape mus mette tetane. Rem rene tuma yaper wete tetane. Mapurke rem etop basrasem?
41009013	An kemne webo. Elaija re kiyi yam. God Reri Siglowri Tuma webokap, tatame rem rene yaper nenem.
41009014	Rem kwowke yeren yam, Jisas reri anepoi tame tep temenem emik yam. Rem yan lam, nugwape tatame rem yan wuriwouke wurem. Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rane rem Jisas reri anepoikene rem naurabem.
41009015	Tatame rem Jisas rene lam, rem danekene sekem. Agetage rem yin rene pir wem.
41009016	Jisas re anepoi tame remne op wemetem. Kem berke remkene naurabo?
41009017	Nugwape tatame remri tame wuri re Jisas rene tuma sein op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Gambo re ari yen rene gureretene. Re tuma tibo tetane. Eker an ari yen rene nene panen yawo.
41009018	Gambo re rene gurerebo, re selke waren san tuknabo. Reri temas bulbal etek wurabo, poguwkene me borkekebo, re let kiki, tewo kiki tabo. An neri anepoi tame remne wemetye, rem gambo wekroklaweiwo.
41009019	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem anne omuteke be habobo. Kap, an kemkene yabel mapsen teten kem anne omuteke habote? Kem yen rene gwotek anne panen yate.
41009020	Op wemke, rem gambo gureremenem yen rene panen yam. Gambo re Jisas rene lam, re yen rene selke terem, yen re gelkwun bulbal me gaibem.
41009021	Jisas re yenri ha rene op wemetem. Yen re yabel mapsen etopkap temenem? Re sein op wem. Kiyi re eisow yen temenemke, re ek tem.
41009022	Nugwape yabel gambo re rene kerke remapiti warbem, o okke remapiti warbem. Re kerke ein sate, o okke yin sate, re etop habon rene seilabem. Ne nemne pap mette, nemne kwobo late. Kap, ne gambo rene kebese wekrokte?
41009023	Jisas re rene op wem. Ne berke opkap tuma wemetbo? Tame re God rene omuteke habote, God rekene nente.
41009024	Agetage yen reri ha re op wem. An omuteke habobo. Ari omuteke habobokap et eisow. Ne anne latek, an omuteke sekenewai habote.
41009025	Jisas re lam, nugwape tatame rem mekni meknik tetkukwur yewobem. Eker re gambo rene tuma kwobke wem. Ne tuma tibo gambo. Ne wan sitene gambo. Ne opu sekiy. Ne rene sene mane gurerete.
41009026	Gambo re taye piten yen rene selke teren mesegenen amen yim. Yen re kuw let tewok bop tem, re sa yenkap temenem. Tatame rem op lam, rem op wem. Re saye.
41009027	Op wemke, Jisas re yen reri let keren rene nenewayen teteruwem.
41009028	Op tem, Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem akek yin wurem. Etemwou temenem, anepoi tame rem Jisas rene op wemetem. Berke nem gambo wekroklaweiwo?
41009029	Jisas re remne op wem. God rekene tuma namrebo wulewouke, kem opkap gambo kebese wekrokte.
41009030	Rem er kwom mesegenen Galili yokwok yim. Jisas re op habom. Nem Galilike tetane, tatame rem etop kap mette.
41009031	Re reri anepoi tame remne tuma peikbem, eker re habom, tatame rem kap mette, ian gwok tetane. Re remne gwor tuma peiken op wem. An More Tame Tem Tame. Rem anne keikeren panen yin anne pen sate. Yabel pes tetek, murwek an sene wayen site.
41009032	Reri anepoi tame rem er tuma tobo be metem, rem Jisas rene wemette akem.
41009033	Rem Kaperneam kwomke yam, rem akek wuren tem, Jisas re remne op wemetem. Kem kelowke yabem, kem be tumaker nauraye?
41009034	Rem tuma ribo tem. Rem kelowke yabem, rem etemwou etemwou nasweibem. Nemri wuri yike re keryen yen? Eker rem tuma ribo tem.
41009035	Jisas re sin reri letpeis tewo pes kerem tame remne wen yan remne op wem. Tame wuri re keryen yen tete selte, re gwop nente. Re habote, an tame bukre bo. Op habote, re nugwape tatame remri yaku nente.
41009036	Jisas re eisow yen wuri remri borke panen yam. Re yen poten tetemenem, re rene let keren remne op wem.
41009037	Tame re anne omuteke habobo, re gwopkap yen rene pap yewobo, re anne mere pap yewobo. Anne pap yewobo, re annewou pap be yewobo. Yehow. Re anne werasem Tame rene mere kirkir pap yewobo. Jisas re remne op wem.
41009038	Jon re Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Nem lam, tame wuri re neri sig wem, re neri kitimenak gambo wekrokem. Er tame re nemri sukuw bo, eker nem rene sewayem.
41009039	Jisas re op wem. Kem rene mane sewaite. Tame rem ari sig wen wos bukre ari kitimenak nentek, rem anne tuma yaper be wete.
41009040	Tame rem nemkene gwule be nenbo, er tame rem nemri tametiy.
41009041	An kemne sekeneker webo. Tatame rem kemne lan op habote. Nem Jisas reri anepoi remne kwobo late. Rem etop habotek, rem kemne ok newon ate, God re er tatame remne yenbo sein nente tetane.
41009042	Tame wuri re yenkap anne omuteke habobo, sene agerbo tame wuri re rene sewaite, sene anne omuteke habobo yen re anne magel taite, et yaperwai. Yen rene sewaibo tame rene rem pa bukre wakke tenen okke sokwunte, re ek sate, et yenbowai.
41009043	-
41009044	Neri letke ne omuteke habobo wule mesegente, neri let ne gerekwon poten septite. Ne let wuriwou tementek, opkap ne God reri kwomke yin etek temente, et yenbo. Ne let pespes temente, ne ker kwomke yin temente, et yaperwai.
41009045	-
41009046	Neri tewoke ne omuteke habobo wule mesegente, ne neri tewo gerekwon poten septite. Ne tewo wuriwou temente, opkap ne God reri kwomke yin temente, et yenbo. Ne tewo pespes temente, ne kerkene kwomke yin temente, et yaperwai.
41009047	Neri leke ne omuteke habobo wule mesegente, ne le gwopoten septite. Ne le wuriwou temente, ne God reri panen si kwomke yin temente, et yenbo. Ne le pespes temente, ne ker kwomke yin temente, et yaperwai.
41009048	Er ker kwom muyow rem tatame remri wesom abo. Muyow rem be sate. Et ker tetane kwom, ker be sate. Tame rem mus bukrewai metbet tetane.
41009049	Tame rem wiyake God rene kwar pebokap, God re aboyei tatame remne kerke seilate, rem mus meten rem sene tatame yenbo tete.
41009050	Tuma kwute wiyake et yenbo wos. Wiyake re tuma be kwutete, et wiyake sega. Tuma kwutebo wiyakekap, kem yenbo wos nente. Kem gwule be tete, kem keremwou keremwou heyar me site.
41010001	Jisas re Kaperneam kwom mesegenen Judia yokwok yim, re Jordan peik kelaruwke wum. Nugwape tatame rem yan wuriwouke sim, re reri nenbem wule sene nenem, re remne tuma wesowem.
41010002	Farisi tame rem yan Jisas rene seilam. Rem op wemetem. Tame re ta tene pelebitete o bo? Moses Reri Wule map webo?
41010003	Jisas re remne tuma sein op wemetem. Kiyi Moses re kemne be tumake wem?
41010004	Rem rene sein op wem. Moses re op wem. Tame re ta tene pelebitete habobo, re siglow wuri basrasen ta tene newon re tene ek pelebitete. Moses re kiyi etop wem.
41010005	Jisas re tuma sein op wem. Kiyi Moses re lam, kem Juda tatame kem mangure tem, etopkap re er wule siglowke eker basrasem.
41010006	Kiyisapewai God re aboyei wosbas nenmenem, God Reri Siglowri Tuma op webo. God re takene tamekene nenem. (Stat 1:27, 5:2)
41010007	Etopkap, ta te teri nawoha repne mesegenen te yin tamer rekene rep etop tete.
41010008	Repri wesom wuriketwou. (Stat 2:24) Rep sene kena kena bo. Yehow. Repri wesom wuriketwou.
41010009	Be wos God re kiyi wemkap, tatame rem kap biragiyete. Tame re ta panete, ta te tame yite, et yenbo. Tame re ta tene kap pelebitete. Ta te agerbo tame kap yite.
41010010	Jisas re tuma wekeipen rem sene akek wurem. Ta pelebite tuma anepoi tame rem Jisas rene sene wemetem.
41010011	Jisas re remne op wem. Tame re kiyi panem ta pelebiten re agerbo ta sene panete, re muye bisi yibo wule nenbo.
41010012	Ta te teri tame rene pelebiten agerbo tame yite, te mare bisi yibo wule nenbo. Jisas re op wem.
41010013	Rane tatame rem eisow yen remne panen yam. Rem selem, Jisas re yen remne let rasen God rene wemette, re yen remne heyar nente. Rem remne eker panen yam, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem etop lan rem tatame remne tuma putuwem.
41010014	Jisas re remri tuma meten re gwule ten anepoi tame remne op wem. Kem yen remne kap sewaite. Yen rem hameya. Tatame rem God rene yenkap omuteke habote, rem God reri panen si kwomke yite.
41010015	An kemne tuma sekeneker webo. Yen rem God eteri panen si kwomke yite selbo. Yike tame re yen etemkap be tete, re God reri panen si kwomke be yite.
41010016	Jisas re yen remne wulare wulare poten reri kwuluwke sen sin let rasen op wem. God re kemne heyar nente.
41010017	Jisas re kelowke sene yite nenbem, tame wuri re yan gulke pan Jisas rene op wemetem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Ne tame yenbo. Mapkap wule yenbo an nentek, an heyar somsom ek temente?
41010018	Jisas re rene sein wemetem. Berke ne anne tame yenbo webo? Gwor nowselri tatame rem yike yenbo be wuri tetane. God eterwou re yenbo.
41010019	Ne God reri wule kiyi metem. Reri wule op webo. Kem alwo mane pen sate. Kem muye bisi mare bisi mane yite. Kem bisi mane ate. Kem mane yikokon agerbo tatame remne tuma nente. Kem tuma mane yikokote. Kem mane ayekutete. Kem nawoha remri tuma heyar mette.
41010020	Tame re sein op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, an eisow yen temenen yan gwopte an haneyen tem, an God reri wule heyar setene.
41010021	Jisas re rene leklek ten pap metem, re rene op wem. Wos wurinab ne nente. Ne yin neri nugwape wosbas getke rasen agerbo tatame rem tupate. Ne tokwo poten ne sen yin woskene bo tatame remne newote. Opkap ne yenbo wos God reri kwomke temente. Op ten ne yan arenkene sewurte.
41010022	Tame re er tuma meten re bitmi yaper tem, re pap yaper tem. Bupo boker. Reri nugwape wosbas newote, re muwem. Eker re bupo me yim.
41010023	Jisas re anepoi tame remne lan kwuren remne op wem. Woskene tame rem remri wosbas habobo, rem God reri panen si kwomke yite selbo, rem yaku bukre kerebo.
41010024	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem reri tuma metem, rem danekene sekem. Jisas re remne sene op wem. Ari yen. Tatame rem God reri panen si kwomke yite, rem yaku bukre kerete tetane.
41010025	Kamel por re mate kambo lag taukke wurte, re yaku bukre nente. Opkap, wosbaskene tame rem God reri kwomke yite wete, rem yaku bukrewai keren ek yite.
41010026	Rem op meten rem danekene seken etemwou etemwou op wem. Opkap tete, yike tame be wuri re heyar som temente? Bokem.
41010027	Jisas re remne leklek ten op wem. Tame rem kebese be nente. God eterwou re kebese nente. Hekna habona wos God re kebese nente.
41010028	Pita re op wem. Metye. Nem nugwape wos mesegenen nene anepoi yim.
41010029	Jisas re op wem. An kemne sekeneker webo. Anne habobo tatame rem ari Tuma Yenbo kirkir habobo, rem ake, lakemase, naregesi, nawoha, yen, now mesegente,
41010030	gwopte rem nugwape sein potte. Rem ake, lakemase, naregesi, nawoha, yen, now nugwapawai potte tetane. Rem mus kirkir mette. Agerbo tame rem remne yaper nente tetane. Yuri rem God reri kwomke etek heyar somsom temente tetane.
41010031	Gwopte rane tatame rem temnas yibo. Yuri rem tiptuwute tetane. Gwopte tiptuwubo tatame rem temnas yite tetane. Jisas re op wem.
41010032	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Jeruselemke yibem, Jisas re temnas yim. Anepoi tame rem op habo op habom. Remne semowebem tatame rem akem. Jisas re reri anepoi tame let pes tewo pes remnewou kena panen yim, re remne tatame rem rene yurik nentekap tuma sene wesowem.
41010033	Re op wem. Metye. Gwopte nem Jeruselemke yaute. Rem More Tame Tem Tame rene God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yenkene Moses Reri Wule peikbo tamekene remri letke raste, rem rene tuma nenen pen sate wete. Sene rem rene Juda bo tame remri letke raste.
41010034	Er tame rem rene tuma yaper wete, rene sablokwo kwuspate, rene paku pete. Rem rene pen sate. Yabel pes tetek, murwek re sene wayen yite tetane.
41010035	Jemskene Jonkene rep Sebedi reri yen, rep Jisas rene yan op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Ne nesne wos wuri nente.
41010036	Jisas re repne op wemetem. An kepne be wos nente?
41010037	Rep rene sein op wem. Yuri ne keryen yen ten ne wolbaye bukrek site, nes habobo, nes nerenkene site. Wuri let mamek site, wuri let giriyke site.
41010038	Jisas re repne op wem. Kepri wemetye tuma kep heyar be mettene. Rem anne yaper nente, an mus mette. Kap, kep ari mette muskap kep kirkir kebese mette? Kap, an okke wartekap kep kebese kirkir warte?
41010039	Rep sein op wem. Nes kebese. Jisas re repne op wem. Sekene. Yuri ari ate ok yaperkap kep kirkir ate. Yuri an ok wartekap kep kirkir warte.
41010040	Yike ari let giriyke site, yike ari let mamek site et ari wos bo. God re lebam tame remne re et wolbaye newon rem ek site.
41010041	Agerbo anepoi tame letpeis rem er tuma metem, rem Jemskene Jonkene repne gwule tuma wem.
41010042	Jisas re remne aboyei wen yan remne op wem. Kem sanetene. Nowselri tatame rem etemri keryen yen remri kulke tetane. Rem remri keryen yen remri webokap etopwou nenbo. Keryen yen rem remne kwobke nenbo, remne paku pebo.
41010043	Remri nenbokap, kem etopkap mane nente.
41010044	Yike re keryen tame tete habobo, re yaku nen tamekap tete.
41010045	An More Tame Tem Tame. Tatame rem anne yaku nente an be yam. Yehow. An yan an remri yaku nente yam. An nugwape tatame remne kwobo late yam. Rem anne pen sate, an nugwape tatame remne tupan remri wule yaper poten septite yam.
41010046	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Jeriko kwomke yam. Re Jeriko kwom mesegenen yibem, reri anepoi tamekene nugwape tatamekene rem remkene yim. Le si tame, re kelwur wemetbem tame, re kelow kelarek simenem. Reri sig Bartimeus, re Timeus reri yen.
41010047	Er tame re metem, Nasaret kwomri tame, Jisas, re yabem. Re Jisas rene yaye ten op wem. Jisas. Ne Devit Reri Yen. Ne anne pap met.
41010048	Nugwape tatame rem rene sewayen op wem. Ne elen me te. Re sene yaye ten op wem. Ne Devit Reri Yen. Ne anne pap met.
41010049	Jisas re teten op wem. Er tame rene ten hare ya. Rem le si tame rene op wem. Ne okbop te. Ne opu wayen tete. Jisas re nene teye.
41010050	Op ten le si tame eilik wumenem tame oub re agetage lugen septin re tetepoten re Jisas rene lasyim.
41010051	Jisas re rene wemetem. Ne map habobo, an nene berke nente? Le si tame re sein op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, an habobo, an le sene heyar late.
41010052	Jisas re rene op wem. Ne opu sene yi. Ne anne omuteke haboyek, neri le sene heyar teye. Agetagewai reri le heyar ten re welepe sene lam. Re Jisas rene kelowke semowen yim.
41011001	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Jerusalem meknik yabem, rem Oliv Kwowke tetane kwom Betfasikene Betanikene potem. Jisas re reri anepoi tame pes repne werasen yim.
41011002	Re repne op wem. Kep er meknik tetane kwomke yin wurte. Kep late, rem donki yen rene etek tentene. Er donki yen tame rem yike kiyi be sim. Kep yin kep sauken donki yen rene panen gwotek ya.
41011003	Kepne yike wemette. Kep donki yen berke saukbo? Kep rene sein op we. Haneyen re yaku tetane, re donki yen agetage sene panen yate tetane. Kep sein etop wete.
41011004	Rep kwomke yin wuren rep donki yen lam. Donki yen re kelow kelarek tetemenem, ake eruk tenmenem. Op ten rep donki yen ek saukem.
41011005	Etopkene meknik teteyewomenem tame rem repne op wemetem. Kep be woske nente, kep donki yen saukbo?
41011006	Jisas re repne wem tumakap, rep remne sein etop wem. Rem kirkir ten rep donki yen ek sauken panen yim.
41011007	Rep donki yen Jisas rene panen yam. Rep repri wumenem tame oub lagu lugen donki yen reri magel luwke petan Jisas re yawun etek sim.
41011008	Nugwape tatame rem remri wumenem tame oub lagu lugen kelowke petan yam. Agerbo tatame rem nowke yin me take tan sen yan kelowke petam.
