41011009	Jisas rene panemenem tatame, rane rem temnamenem, rane rem tiptuwumenem, rem yaye op tebem. Nem God rene okbop tebo. God re gwor tame rene heyar nente. Re Keryen Yen reri sigke yawo.
41011010	God re gwor keryen yen rene heyar nente. Re nemne kwom panen site. Gwor keryen yen re nemri yeiwarege remne kiyi kwom panen simenem tame Devit eterkap. Nem God reri sig bukre wete.
41011011	Op ten Jisas re Jerusalemke yin wuren re God Reri Kwobor ukrek wuren nugwape wos lan kwurem. Yabel warte nenbem, re reri anepoi tame letpeis tewo pes kere tame remkene Betani kwomke sene yim.
41011012	Kwokwos rem Betani kwom mesegenen yibem, Jisas re sikwoi sam.
41011013	Re lam, yipige me wuri re kai kerake tetemenem, er me re take nugwape temenem. Re supa kutete habom, re meknik yin laweyem, re supa wuri be lam. Re takewou lam. Et geil ame supa yate yabel bo.
41011014	Jisas re yipige me rene op wem. Yuri ne supa sene kap yate. Tatame rem neri supa sene be ate. Reri anepoi tame rem reri wem tuma metem.
41011015	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Jerusalemke yim. Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke wuren lam, tatame rem kel pot yaku etek nenem, re remne wekrokem. Tame rem kel natokwo tupa yaku nenbem, re remri kel rasbem tiy legalepitim. Ap bour tupabem tame remri wolebaye re kirkir poten legalepitim.
41011016	Jisas re remne tuma sewayen op wem. Tatame rem God Reri Kwoborke wosbas kap sen yi yate.
41011017	Sene re tatame remne tuma op wem. God Reri Siglowri Tuma op basrastene. Ari Kwobor et nugwape nowselri tatame remri ankene tuma namrebo ake. Kerem etop be nenbo. Kem bisi a tame remne gwotek berasbo. (Aisaia 56:7)
41011018	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yenkene Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene rem etop metem, rem rene pen sate kelow tobotan sopbem. Rem Jisas rene akbem kwobo gwor. Nugwape tatame rem Jisas reri peikbem tuma meten danekene sekem, eker rem Jisas rene akem.
41011019	Perpe tebem, Jisas re reri anepoi tame remkene rem Jerusalem mesegenen yim.
41011020	Kwokwos kerwu Jisas re reri anepoi tame remkene kelowke sene yibem, rem lam, yipige me re san tetemenem. Reri takekene nenkene aboyei sok tem.
41011021	Pita re Jisas reri wem tuma sene habon re Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Ne ekla. Yere ne er yipige me rene wem, re yaper tete. Gwopte re sok teye.
41011022	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem God rene omuteke habote.
41011023	Tame wuri re etop habote, re gwor kwow rene op wete. Kwow, ne yesen okke war. Er tame re wuribai pes be tete, re ometekewai habote, reri wete tuma etopkap tete. An kemne sekeneker webo, er wos re wemkap re etop tete.
41011024	Kem God rekene tuma namren rene wos wuri wemette, kem rene omuteke habon op wete. Ari wemette wos an potte tetane. An kemne webo, kemri wete woskap kem etop potte.
41011025	-
41011026	Kem teten God rekene tuma namremenbo, agerbo tame reri kemne nenemkap wule yaper kem habotek, kem rekene yin kelmenate. Kem etop nentek, kemri Hevenke tetane Ha re kemri nenem wule yaper sene be habote.
41011027	Rem Jerusalemke sene yam, Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke wuren sewurbem. Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame, Juda remri keryen tame rem Jisas rene yam.
41011028	Rem rene op wemetem. Neri sig bukre, neri nugwape wos nenbo kitimena ne mak potem? Yike nene sig newon nene et yaku nente wem.
41011029	Jisas re remne sein op wem. An kemne tuma wuri wemette. Ari kemne wemetbo tuma kem anne sein wetek, an kemne ek wesowte, yike anne sig bukre newom, yike anne et yaku nente wem.
41011030	Jon re tatame remne ok waren tirmunbem. Yike rene er yaku newom? Kap, God re Jon rene newom, o tame rem rene newom?
41011031	Rem etop metem, rem etemwou etemwou nauram. Nem map wete? Nem kap op wete. God re Jon rene yaku newom. Nem etop wete, Jisas re nemne kap op wemette. Mapurke kem Jon reri tuma be habom?
41011032	Nem kap op wete. Tame rem Jon rene yaku newom. Nem etop wete, yuri nugwape tatame rem nemne tuma wete tetane. Tatame nugwapa rem webo. Jon re God Reri Tuma wesowbem tame. Eker rem remne akbo.
41011033	Rem Jisas rene op wem. Nem be mettene, yike rene yaku newom. Jisas re remne sein wem. Kem anne be wesowye, yike Jon rene yaku newom. Aren mere, an kemne be wesowte, yike anne yaku newon an er yaku nenbo. Jisas re op wem.
41012001	Jisas re Juda remri keryen tame remne sikur sakur tuma op wem. Tame wuri re wain now nenem, re pisi ek peikem. Sene re wain supa ok wulte sel mei perem. Wulbo ok et wain ok. Re now mitiy ake wuri nenem. Tame rem etek sin now heyar lakerete. Sene re yaku nen tame remne er now lakerete op wem. An agerbo kwomke yite. Kem ari wain now yaku nenen heyar lakeretek, yuri an kemne wain supa ek newote. Op wemke, now mutame re now mesegenen gene kwomke yim.
41012002	Yuri supa okwomenem, now mutame re reri yaku bop nen tame wuri rene werasen now yaku nenbem tame remne lasyim. Re now mutame reri wain supa potte yim.
41012003	Now yaku nenbem tame rem yaku bop nen tame rene narsukem, rene paku pen werasen sene yim. Re let bop sene yim, re mutame reri supa be semenem.
41012004	Now mutame re agerbo yaku bop nen tame wuri rene werasen yim, rem reri tare geyen rene yaper nenem.
41012005	Now mutame re yaku bop nen tame wuri sene murwe werasem, er tame rene rem pen sam. Now mutame re nugwape yaku nen tame remne sene werasem, rane rem remne paku pebem, rane remne rem pen sabem.
41012006	Tame wuriwou som temenem, et now mutame reri meseke mogul yen sekene. Re reri yen wuriketwou, rekene temenem. Re op wem. Ari yen sekene reri tuma rem mette. Op wen re yener rene nowke werasen yim.
41012007	Now yaku nenbem tame rem yener rene lam, rem etemwou etemwou op wem. Yuri gwo yen re ha reri wos potte. Nem rene pen satek, reri now nem ek potte.
41012008	Op wemke, rem yen rene keikeren pen sam, reri kupa rem now kwopok septi wurem.
41012009	Jisas re sikur sakur tuma wekeipemke, re remne wemetem. Now mutame re now yaku nen tame remne berke nente? An kemne wete. Re yan er now yaku nen tame remne pen sate, re agerbo tame remne er now yaku newote.
41012010	Kap, God Reri Siglow basrastene Tuma kem lam? Siglowri Tuma op basrasem. Ake nenbem tame rem kiyi yaper wen septim seg, et nawo seg bukre tem.
41012011	Keryen Yen God re etop nenem. Nem etop lam, nem op wem. Et yenbowai. (Buk Song 118:22-23)
41012012	Juda tame remri keryen tame rem Jisas reri wem sikur sakur tuma metem, rem op habom. Jisas re nemne weye. Nem now yaku nenbem tamekap. Op habomke, rem rene keikerete wem. Rem nugwape tatame remne akem, eker rem rene be keikerem.
41012013	Keryen tame rem Farisi tamekene Keryen Yen Herot reri sukuwkene remne werasen Jisas rene lasyim, rene tuma yikokon wemette yim.
41012014	Rem yan Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Nem metbo, ne tuma be yikokobo. Ne tuma sekene wesowbo, ne tame wuri be akbo. Aboyei tatame remne ne tuma wuriketwou wesowbo. Sigkene tame sigkene bo tame ne remne tuma wuriwou wesowbo. Ne tatame remne God reri wuribaike habobokap wesowbo. Op tetane, ne nemne wesowte. Keryen Yen Sisar re agerbo nowselri tame, re Rom tame. Re nemne kwom panen sitene, re nemne takis kel raste webo. Kap, nem Sisar rene kel newote, o bo?
41012015	Op wemke, Jisas re remri yikokobo wuribai lam, re remne op sein wemetem. Kem anne berke seilabo? Kem kel wuri sen yan anne peterate.
41012016	Rem kel wuri sen yan peteram, Jisas re lan remne op wemetem. Gwor kel et tame wowkene basras sigkene. Kap, et yikeri wow, yikeri sig? Rem sein op wem. Et Romri Keryen Yen Sisar reri wow, reri sig.
41012017	Jisas re remne op wem. Sisar reri wos kem Sisar rene newote. God reri wos kem God rene newote. Rem reri tuma metem, rem danekene sekem.
41012018	Sadyusi tame rem webem, sam tatame yuri rem sene be wayen site. Rem yam, Jisas rene op wemetem.
41012019	Tuma Peikbo Tame. Kiyi Moses re nemne gwor Wule op basrasem. Tame re ta panete, sene re yenkene bo, re bupo me sate, reri mase re reri wane tene panen yen sete. Yen sete, er yen remne rem op webo. Rem laker reri yen. Moses re etop basrasem.
41012020	Op tetane, nem nene op wemetbo. Kiyi lakemase letrane kelare pes kerem rem temenem. Masetobo yen re ta panem. Yuri rep yenkene bo, re bupo me sam.
41012021	Mase re wane tene panem, rep yenkene bo, re bupo me sam. Bor tame re etopwou nenem.
41012022	Sene et mase letrane kelare pes kere rem etopwou etopwou nenbem, rem wane tene panebem, rem yenkene bo, rem bupo me sam. Yuri ta te etet mere te sam.
41012023	Aboyei lakemase letrane kelare pes kerem rem tene panemenem. Kap, et ta yuri te sele meike sene wayen site, te yikeri ta sekene tete? Rem rene etop wemetem.
41012024	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem tuma sekene be weye. Kem God Reri Siglowri Tumakene reri kitimenakene kem be latene, eker kem tuma sekene be webo.
41012025	Yuri sam tatame rem sene wayen site, rem God reri kwomri tamekap tete, rem sene be narpanete.
41012026	Sabo tame rem sene wayen site tuma, Moses re etop kiyi basrasem. Kap, kem be latene? Moses re ker eibem me eisow meknik tetemenem, God re Moses rene op wem. An yeiwarege Abraham, Aisak, Jekop remri Keryen Yen God.
41012027	God re sam tatame remri God bo. Re kelpe tetane tatame remri God. Eker kemri weye tuma et sekene bo. Jisas re op wem.
41012028	Jisas re Sadyusi tame remkene tuma namrebem, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame wuri re yan remri tuma metem. Jisas re tuma sein yenbo wem, re metem. Eker re Jisas rene op wemetem. Be wule et bukrewai?
41012029	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Israel tatame, kem met. Wule bukrewai re gwopkap. Neremnri Keryen Yen God eterwou re Keryen Yen.
41012030	Kem keremri Keryen Yen God rene pap yewote, kemri wuribai, purere, wesom, kitimenak kem rene pap yewo. Er wule et bukrewai.
41012031	Wule bukre peswe re gwor. Ne neri kworer wesom heyar nenbokap, ne agerbo tatame remne etopkap heyar nen. Er wule pes rep wule bukre, agerbo wule rem eisow.
41012032	God reri wule peikbem tame re Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Ne tuma sekene weye. Keryen Yen eterwou re God. Agerbo god be tetane. Eterwou re tetane.
41012033	Nem God rene omuteke pap yewote, nemri wuribai purere, wesom, kitimenake nem rene pap yewote. Nem kworer yenbo nenbokap, nem agerbo tatame remne etopkap nente. Er wule bukrewai pes et sipsipkene agerbo woskene God rene kwar pebo wule teitkwunbo.
41012034	Jisas re habom. Er tame re purere yenbokene. Op habom, re rene op wem. Ne God reri panen si kwom meknik teye. Jisas re etop wem, tatame rem rene tuma wuri sene be wemetem, rem me akem.
41012035	Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke temenem, re tatame remne tuma wesowem, re op wem. Moses Reri Wule peikbo tame rem op webo. God reri Lebam Tame, Krais, re Devit reri beigke tete. Mapurke rem opkap webo?
41012036	Kiyi Krais re nowselke be yamenem, God Reri Wow re Devit rene purere newom, Devit re op wem. Keryen Yen re ari Keryen Yen rene op wem. Ne ari let mame yokwok sin yin an neri peiktame remne neri kulke rasen temente. (Buk Song 110:1)
41012037	Devit re Krais rene Keryen Yen wem. Opkap, Krais re mapurke Devit reri yen. Nugwape tatame rem etek temenem, rem Jisas reri tuma metem, rem metekwasem.
41012038	Jisas re tatame remne tuma wesowen op wem. An kemne ei me pebo. Moses Reri Wule peikbo tame remri yaper nen wos kem heyar la. Rem selbo, tatame rem remne late, eker rem tame oub lagu wun ek sewurbo. Rem selbo, tatame rem remne pir wete, remne tame yenbo wete, eker rem get yin sewurbo.
41012039	Rem God reri akek wuren sigkene tame remri wolbayek site selbo. Awos bukre abo yabelke, rem emi yenbok sin awos ek ate.
41012040	Rem wane ta remne yikokon remri ake bisi potbo. Sene rem God Reri Kwoborke yin wurbo, rem yikokon God rekene tuma bukre namrebo. Op nenbo, rem habobo. Tatame rem etop labo, rem nemne tame yenbo wete. An webo, God re er tame remne yaperwai nente tetane. Jisas re op wem.
41012041	Jisas re God Reri Kwoborri kel yewobem ou meknik simenem, re lam, tatame rem kel sen yan ouke yewobem. Kelwurkene tame nugwape rem nugwape kel yewobem.
41012042	Wane ta wuri te kelkene bo, te kel eisow pesket sen yan yewom.
41012043	Op lam, Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne wen yan remne op wem. An kemne tuma sekeneker webo. Kelkene tatame rem kel nugwape yewoye. Kelkene bo wane ta te kel eisow pesket yewoye, teri yewoye kel pes et nugwape tame remri kel teitkwunye.
41012044	Kel nugwape tetane tame rem kel ranewou yewoye. Wane ta te kel nugwape bo, teri awos tupabo kel te aboyei yewokeipye. Jisas re op wem.
41013001	Jisas re God Reri Kwobor mesegenem, reri anepoi tame wuri re rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Gwor kwoborkene akek nenem pakene rem yenbowai.
41013002	Jisas re rene sein op wem. Kem gwor ake bukre remne laye. Yuri er pa rem agerbo pa luwke be tete tetane. Rem aboyei beran pete warte tetane. Jisas re op wem.
41013003	Jisas re Oliv Kwowke yawun sim, God Reri Kwobor op yokwok tetemenen re lam. Pita, Jems, Jon, Andru etemwou rem rekene yan temenem. Rem rene wemetem.
41013004	Ne nemne weye, tame rem God Reri Kwobor berate. Be yabel rem etop nente? Be wos nem kiyi lan sanete, rem God Reri Kwobor ek berate yabel et matnaye? Ne nemne wesowte.
41013005	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem heyar la. Tame wuri re kemne kap yikokote.
41013006	Nugwape tame rem yuri yan ari sig wete. Rem yikokon op wete. An Krais, an God re Lebam Tame. Nugwape tatame rem remri yikoko tuma omuteke mette tetane.
41013007	Yuri kem ei nai ken mette. Kem ei nai tuma mette, genek tetane tatame rem ei naibo. Kem etop mette, kem kap akte. Et wos re tete. Et nowsel yaper tete yabel bo. Er yabel re yuri tete.
41013008	Yuri kwom wuriri tatame rem agerbo kwomri tatame remkene naite. Keryen yen wuri reri sukuw rem agerbo keryen yen reri sukuw remkene naite. Nina bukre nugwape nowselke yate tetane. Tatame rem akwoi site tetane. Er wos et ta te yen wurte nenbo kin germebokap.
41013009	An kemne ei me pebo. Kem heyar la. Rane tame rem kemne keikeren tuma nente tetane. God reri akek rem kemne etek paku pete tetane. Areri sigke kem nowselri keryen yenkene saberawiykene tame remri bitmik teten ari Tuma Yenbo remne etek wesowte.
41013010	Ari Tuma Yenbo, tatame rem wesowte, aboyei kwomri kwomri tatame rem kiyi metkeiptek, yuri nowsel yaper tete yabel ek tete.
41013011	Yuri rem kemne tuma nente panen yite, kem mane akte. Kem mane op habote. Nem be tuma sein berke wete? Er yabel God re kemne tuma peterate, kem etop tuma sein wete. Kem wete tuma et kemri tuma bo. God Reri Wow re kemne gurerete, kem tuma sein kebese wete.
41013012	Tame rem remri lakemase remne agerbo tame remne weraste, rem lakemase remne tuma nenen pen sate tetane. Hanem rem remri yenem remne etopwou nente. Yen rem nawoha remne magel taite, remne agerbo tamene weraste, rem remne pen sate tetane.
41013013	Kem anne omuteke habobo, eker nugwape tatame rem kemne gwule tete tetane. Nowsel yaper tete yabel legete, anne som habobo tatame rem heyar somsom temente tetane.
41013014	Jisas re tuma som op webem. Yuri kem late, wos yaperwai et rene sewayem emik tetete. (Kem gwor siglow labo tatame, tuma tobo kem heyar habote.) Kem etop latek, kem Judia yokwok tetane tatame, kem kwowke amen yin tete.
41013015	Tame re akwul makele egesimente, re er yaper wos late, re ake kap wuren reri wos wuri kap potte. Yehow. Re agetage amen yite.
41013016	Tame re nowke temente, re er yaper wos late, re reri akek kap wuren reri tame oub kap potte.
41013017	Er yabel an yenkene ta yen muk newobo takene remne pap mette. Rem kebese agetage be amete tetane.
41013018	Kem Keryen Yen God rene wemette, er yaper wos re nigel yabo yabelke kap tete.
41013019	Er yabel nugwape yaper wos tete tetane. Kiyi opkap yaper wos be temenem. Kiyisape God re nowsel nenen yam, gwopte mere, opkap yaper wos kiyi op be tem. Er yaper wos legete, sene opkap be tete.
41013020	Er yabel God re borke be teregte wem, aboyei tatame rem saiwokeipte wem. God re reri kenem tatame remne habom, eker yuri re er yabel borke teregte.
41013021	Er yabel tatame rem kemne op wete. Ekla. Gwor Krais. O rem wete. Ekla. Re gwop yokwok tetane. Etop wetek, remri tuma kem kap omuteke mette.
41013022	Rane tame rem yan kemne yikokon op wete. An Krais, God Reri Lebam Tame. Rane rem yikokon op wete. An God Reri Tuma wesow tame. Er yikoko tame rem kitimenakene bukre wos nente, rem tatame remne yikokolate. Rem God reri kenem tatame remne yikokolaweite.
41013023	Kem ei si. Yuri tete wos an kemne kiyi aboyei wesowem.
41013024	Er yabel reri yaper wos re legetek, agetagewai yabel re neirkap tektete, liyp te be paste.
41013025	Sow rem nel pelebiten yerkwutete. Nina te nelke yate, nelri wos rem negnegen kena kena yite tetane.
41013026	Op tete, More Tame Tem Tame re yate. Re nel gwanke yate. Re kitimena bukrekene yate, re hadebaswaikene yate.
41013027	Re God reri kwomri tame remne werasen yite. Rem weiwar yawar yokwori kwom, yale yokwo, yow yokwori kwom rem etek yite, rem God reri kiyi kenem tatame remne panen wuriwouke yan wurte.
41013028	Kem guwb metka habote. Guwb elbu buyabo, metka supa yabo, kem op webo. Nabe berabo.
41013029	Ari kiyi weye tuma et etopkap, kem etop habote. Kem er wos late, kem sanete, ari yate yabel matnaye.
41013030	An kemne sekeneker webo. Gwopte tetane tame rem ab be sate tetane, ari weye wos rem late tetane.
41013031	Nelkene selkene ab legete tetane. Ari tuma re som temente tetane.
41013032	Jisas re som webem. Wos yaper tete yabel tame rem be mettene. God reri kwomri tame rem be mettene. Aren, an God Reri Yen, aren mere, an be mettene. God eterwou re mettene.
41013033	Kem be mettene, be yabelke et wos re tete. Eker kem ei si.
41013034	Er yabel re gwopkap. Tame wuri re reri kwom mesegenen kai kwomke yim. Yite nenbem, re yaku nen tame wulare wulare remne yaku peteran remne op wem. Kem er yaku nen. Ake eru lakere tame rene re op wem. Ne ake eru heyar lakerete. Op wen re ek mesegenen yim.
41013035	Kem heyar la. Makapke ake mutame re sene yate? Kem be mettene. Yabel warbet ek yate, o neir bor ek yate, o kwokwo webet ek yate, o ei berabet ek yate? Opkap kem heyar lakerete.
41013036	Re agetage sene yate, kemne tuknamente kap late.
41013037	Ari kemne webo tuma an aboyei tatame remne kirkir op webo. Kem heyar lakerebet!
41014001	Yabel pes tete, Egesi Yabel pes tete nenbem. Yabel wuri reri sig gwor. God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabel. Agerbo wuri reri sig gwor, Be Peltene Geil Abo Yabel. Er Egesi Yabel peske temente, God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene rem op wem. Nem berasen Jisas rene keikeren pen sate.
41014002	Rem op wem. Awos bukre ate yabel nem rene kap keikerete. Nem rene er yabelke keikerete, tatame rem kap late, rem kap muwen eike kap ten naite. Rem op wem.
41014003	Jisas re Betani kwomke temenem, re kiyi numa pemenem tame, Saimon, reri akek yin temenem. Jisas re awos abem, ta wuri te etek yam, te alabasta pak nenem gin sen yam. Gin et bes yenbokene kwar, tokwo bukrek tupabem kwar yewomenem. Te gin bursan kwar te Jisas reri tarek sirem.
41014004	Rane tame rem etop lam, rem pap yoken etemwou etemwou op wem. Berke er kwar te bupo me sirpitiye?
41014005	Er kwar et tokwo bukrek tupam. Er kwar nem kel natokwo tupate weye, nem kel nugwape, 300 kel silva, poten woskene bo tatame remne newote weye. Rem ta tene tuma kwobke wem.
41014006	Jisas re op wem. Kem berke tene etopkap tuma weye? Kem tene tuma mane wete. Te anne yenbo wosker nenye.
41014007	Woskene bo tame rem kemkene som temente, kem remne tewok tewok kebese heyar nente. Aren, an kemkene sou be temente.
41014008	Teri kebese nentekap te nenye. Te er bes yenbokene kwar ari weske sirye, te ari wesom per taibo wulek nenye. Yuri an sate, rem anne sele meike raste. Te etop muwkuwtekye.
41014009	An kemne sekenewai webo. Rem ari Tuma Yenbo nugwape nowselke yin wesowte tetane. Gwor ta teri nenyekap rem kirkir habon wesowte tetane.
41014010	Letpeis tewo pes kerem anepoi tame remri wuri, Judas Iskariot, re God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen remne lasyim. Rem Jisas rene keikerete selem, Judas re remne op wem. An kemne Jisas rene peterate.
41014011	Rem etop metem, rem okbop ten Judas rene op wem. Nem nene kel newote. Op wem, re Jisas rene remri letke raste kelow sopte yim.
41014012	Be Peltene Geil Abo Yabel reri temnas yi yabel tem. Er yabel rem sipsip yen pebo, tatame rem God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabelke ate. Er yabel Jisas reri anepoi tame rem yan Jisas rene op wem. Awos nem mak nerete?
41014013	Re reri anepoi tame pes repne werasen op wem. Kep kwom sagke yin wurte. Kep tame wuri late. Re okkene gin wuri semente. Kep rene late, kep rene semowte.
41014014	Re ake wuri wurtek, kep ake mutame rene op wemette. Tuma Peikbo Tame re op weye. Ari awos ate emi ma? An God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem awos ari anepoi tame remkene ate selbo.
41014015	Op wete, ake mutame re ake puri bukre, ya yokwok tetane ake puri, kepne peterate. Tame rem er ake puri kiyi heyarem, awos abo tiykene awos nerebo woskene etek tetane. Kep nemri awos etek nerete.
41014016	Reri anepoi tame pes rep kwom sagke yim, Jisas re wemkap rep etop lam, rep God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem awos etek nerem.
41014017	Yabel warbem, Jisas reri anepoi tamekene rem etek yam.
41014018	Rem tiyke simenen awos abem, Jisas re op wem. An kemne tuma sekeneker webo. Kemri tame wuri, nemkene awos abo tame, re anne yena tete tetane.
41014019	Anepoi tame rem et tuma metem, rem pap yaper metem. Rem wulare wulare rene wemetem. Kap, ne anne webo?
41014020	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem tame letpeis tewo pes kereye. Kemri tame wuri re geil poten ankene let ware wurik warbo, er tame re anne yena tete tetane.
41014021	Tuma sekene. More Tame Tem Tame re sate. God Reri Siglowri Tuma wemkap re ek sate tetane. Anne yena tete tame, yuri re nugwape mus mette tetane. Nawo te rene be wurte wem, et yenbo.
41014022	Rem abem, Jisas re geil wuri poten re God rene wese an belokteyewom, anepoi tame remne newopiti pete yan op wem. Kem poten a. Gwor ari om.
41014023	Rem am, re ok ware wuri poten God rene wese an remne newom, aboyei rem wain ok am.
41014024	Re remne op wem. Gwor ari nep. Rem anne pen sate, ari nep yerte. Et nugwape tatame remne peteran muwkuwtekte, God reri teiktem tuma et sekene.
41014025	An kemne sekeneker webo. An nowselke temente, an wain ok sene be ate. Yuri an God reri panen si kwomke temente, an wain ok ager etek ate.
41014026	Op wemke, rem God rene sekwo wuri lomun wurakwuten rem Oliv Kwowke yin yaukwutem.
41014027	Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. God Reri Siglowke basrasen Tuma op wem. God re sipsip lakerebo tame rene pete, sipsip rem amekiren yikwute yakwutete tetane. (Sakaraia 13:7) Kem etopker nente tetane. Kem aboyei kem anne mesegenen amen yite tetane.
41014028	An sele meike wayen site, an kemne Galili yokwok temnas yite.
41014029	Pita re Jisas rene op wem. Aren, an nene be mesegen amen yite. Rem etop nente, an op be nente.
41014030	Jisas re rene op wem. An nene sekene webo. Gwopte neir kwokwo re tewo pes be wementek, tewo mur ne ari sig nesen op wete. An Jisas rene be latene.
41014031	Pita re Jisas rene kwobke op wem. An nekene sate, et yenbo. Neri sig an be neste. Op wemke, anepoi tame rem aboyei etop kirkir wem.
41014032	Rem Getsemani nowke yim, Jisas re anepoi tame remne op wem. Kem gwotek simente. An God rekene tuma namrete yibo.
41014033	Op wen re Pita, Jems, Jon remne panen yim. Jisas re pap yaperwai tem.
41014034	Re remne op wem. An pap yaperwai teye, an sate keraket tetane. Kem gwotek ten lakere.
41014035	Op wem, re opre kera yin selke waren tuknan re God rene op wem. Kwobo la kelow temente, anne yaper nente wos kap tete.
41014036	Apiy, ari Apiy. Ne aboyei wos kebese nenbo. An selbo, anne yaper nente wos et anne be tete, an mus bukre be mette. Et neri wos. Ari selbokap ne kap nente. Neri habobokap, ne etop nente. Re op wem.
41014037	Re sene yin lam, anepoi tame mur rem me tuknamenem, re remne teren Pita rene op wem. Saimon, ne berke tuknatene? Ne kera be lakereye.
41014038	Kem ei si. Kem God rekene tuma namrete, yaper seilabo wos kemne kap tete. Kemri wuribai kem God rekene tuma namrete selbo. Sene kem wesom teselye, le metye, kem tuknaye. Wuribai re kitimenakene, wesom re kitimenakene bo.
41014039	Re sene yin God rekene tuma sene namrem. Kiyi wem tumakap re sene etop wem.
41014040	Re sene yan lam, rem le meten tuknamenem. Re remne yan terem, rem rene tuma namrete habolaweyem.
41014041	Tewo murwe re sene yan remne op wem. Kem som tuknatene, ege som sitene? Yow. Ekla. Tame yaper rem More Tame Tem Tame rene potte yawo.
41014042	Kem opu wayen tete. Nem yite. Ekla. Anne yena tebo tame re yawo.
41014043	Jisas re som webem, reri anepoi tame remri wuri, Judas, re yam. Nugwape tame rem rekene yam. Rem arepkene pakukene kirkir setermenem. God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame, Juda remri keryen tame rem er tame remne werasen Jisas rene keikerete yam.
41014044	Kiyi Judas re er tame remne op wem. An tame wuri rene ragiy boite, er tame re Jisas. Kem rene keikeresuken rene heyar lakeren rene panen yite.
41014045	Judas re yam, agetage re Jisas rene yin op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame. Op wemke, re rene ragiy boyem.
41014046	Tatame rem etop lan rem Jisas rene narsukem.
41014047	Tame wuri re etek tetemenem, re reri arep poten God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen reri yaku bop nen tame reri wan arepke bokekwunem.
41014048	Jisas re remne op wem. Kem anne potte yawo, berke kem arep pakukene kirkir sen yawo? Berke kem anne wule biragiyebo tame remne potbokapke yawo?
41014049	Nugwape yabel an God Reri Kwoborke temenem, an kemne tuma peikbem, kem anne etek be keikerem. Kemri nenbokap kem bupo boker nenbo. God reri Siglowri Tuma et sekene tete tetane.
41014050	Op wemke, anepoi tame aboyei rem rene mesegenen amen yim.
41014051	Muyensi yen tame wuri re wulkap matewou peikmenem, re Jisas rene semowmenem. Rem rene keikerete habom.
41014052	Keikerelaweyem, rem reri matewou keikeren beraren potem, re sogwul bop wayen amen yim.
41014053	Rem Jisas rene God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen reri akek panen yim. God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen, Juda remri keryen tame, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem etek wuriwouke wurmenem.
41014054	Rem Jisas rene panen yim, Pita re remne kai kera tiptuwu semowem. Rem God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen reri akek yam, re makelek yin sim. Re nause yen remkene etek simenem. Reri wes negel yam, re ker ganke simenem.
41014055	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen, Juda etermri Saberawiykene Tame aboyei, rem Jisas rene pen sate selem, rem eterne yaper nenem tuma soplaweyem.
41014056	Nugwape tame rem yan Jisas rene tuma yikokom, rem tuma wuriwou be wem. Rem agerbo agerbo tuma wem, eker keryen yen rem rene pen sate tuma tobo be wuri metem.
41014057	Sene rane tame rem teten rene yikokon op wem.
41014058	Nem metem, Jisas re op wem. An gwor tamek nenem Kwobor berayewote. Sene yabel murke an tamek be nente Kwobor sene nente.
41014059	Remri wem tuma er agerbo agerbo tumawou rem wem. Rem tuma wuriwou be wem.
41014060	God Reri Kwoborri Keryen Yen re wayen teten Jisas rene op wem. Berke remri weye tuma ne tuma sein be webo?
41014061	Jisas re elen me tem, re tuma sein be wem. Keryen Yen re rene sene wemetem. Kap, God re nene lebam, ne tatame remne potte? Kap, ne God Reri Yen? Ne nemne wesow.
41014062	Jisas re op wem. Et aren. Yuri kem late, More Tame Tem Tame re Keryen Yen tete, re kitimenakene God reri mame yokwok site. Sene re nel gwanke sene yate.
41014063	Keryen Yen re meten re pap yoken reri tame oub pekan op wem. Re God rene tuma yaperker weye. Nem agerbo tame remne reri yaper nenbokap sene be wemette.
41014064	Reri weye tuma yaper kem metye. Kem map habobo? Nem rene berke nente? Rem aboyei op wem. Re yaper nenye, rene pen sate.
41014065	Rane tame rem Jisas rene sablokwo kwuspayewom, rem rene mate bitmik opokwun rene ek pem. Rem rene tame kwuyen op wem. Ne nemne wesowte. Yike nene peye? Ei nai tame rem rene let papke powyek puwburowem.
41014066	Pita re ake makelek temenem, God Reri Kwobor Keryen Yen reri yaku nen ta te etek yam.
41014067	Te lam, Pita re ker ganke simenem. Te rene heyar lan rene op wem. Neren mere, ne Nasaret kwomri Jisas rekene sewurbem.
41014068	Pita re op wem. Yehow. Aren bokem. Neri webo tuma an be sanetene. Op wen re ake makele mesegenen yim, kwokwo wem.
41014069	Yaku nen ta te Pita rene lam, te meknik tetemenem tame remne op wem. Gwor tame re Jisas reri anepoi tame remri tame wuri.
41014070	Pita re tuma sene nesen op wem. Yehow. An remri wuri bo. Keraket tem, meknik tetemenem tame rem Pita rene op wem. Sekenekem. Ne remri tame wuri. Ne Galili yokwori tame.
41014071	Pita re op wem. An kemne sekenewai webo. An kemne sekene be wete, God re anne pete. Kemri webo tame an be latene.
41014072	Op wemke, kwokwo re tewo peswe wem. Pita re op metem, re sene habom. Jisas re anne kiyi wem. Kwokwo re tewo pes be wementek, tewo murwe ne ari sig nesen op wete. An rene be latene. Op sene habom, re sebera yan kenakem kiram.
41015001	Ei berabem, God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen, Juda tame remri keryen tame, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame, Juda etemri Saberawiykene Tame, aboyei rem wuriwouke wuren Jisas rene nente tuma agetage namrem. Rem Jisas rene kepke bogen Keryen Yen Pailat rene rem rene panen yin reri letke rasem.
41015002	Pailat re Jisas rene op wemetem. Kap, ne Juda tatame remri keryen yen o bo? Jisas re sein op wem. Neren ne etop weye.
41015003	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen rem Jisas rene nugwape tuma wem.
41015004	Opkap, Pailat re Jisas rene sene wem. Rem nene nugwape tumaker weye. Berke ne remne tuma sein be webo?
41015005	Jisas re tuma sein be wem, Pailat re eker danekene sekem.
41015006	Nabek nabek God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabel tetbo, Pailat re ake yaperke temenem tame wuri akwulke werasen yibem. Nugwape tatame remri webem tame, Pailat re rene werasen yibem.
41015007	Er yabel nugwape tame rem ake yaperke temenem. Rem gavman remkene nayen rane tame remne pen sam. Etemri tame wuri re Barabas.
41015008	Nugwape tatame rem yan duwem, Pailat rene op wemetem. Ne kiyi nenbemkap sene nente. Ne ake yaperke tetane tame wuri rene akwulke wen yite.
41015009	Pailat re sein op wem. Kem map habobo? An kemri Judari keryen yen rene werasen yite?
41015010	Pailat re etop bupo boker wem. Re heyar sanem, God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen rem Jisas rene wuribai yaper temenem, eker rem rene tuma nente panen yam.
41015011	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen rem nugwape tatame remne op wem. Kem Pailat rene wete, re Jisas rene be werasen yite, re Barabas rene werasen yite.
41015012	Pailat re tatame remne sene op wemetem. Kem tame wuri webo re Juda remri keryen yen, an rene berke nente?
41015013	Rem sein yaye op wem. Rene me kwuren peikkerete.
41015014	Pailat re remne wemetem. Re be yaper wos nenem? Rem sene yaye op wem. Rene me kwuren peikkerete.
41015015	Pailat re op habom. An remri wem tuma nente, rem okbop tete. Opkap re Barabas rene werasen akwulke yim. Re ei nai tame remne op wem. Kem Jisas rene kepke wurbete. Sene kem rene panen yin me kwuren peikkerete.
41015016	Ei nai tame rem Jisas rene keryen yen reri ake makelek panen yim. Rem nugwape ei nai tame remne etek yate wem.
41015017	Keryen yen remri kupkap tame oub wubokap ei nai tame rem Jisas rene tame kwuyen rene kupkap tame oub wuri wuruwem. Sene rem kwokwolobu poten keryen yen remri tare gurerekap kwuren reri tare gurereruwem.
41015018	Rem rene pir op wem. Arkwu re eteke. Ne Juda tame remri keryen yen, ne heyar me temen.
41015019	Rem pakuk reri tarek pen rene sablokwo kwuspayewom. Rem gulke pan rene wekwuyen makwuyen tame kwuyem.
41015020	Rem tame kwuye mesegenem, rem kupkap tame oub sene lugpoten reri tame oub sekene poten rene sene wuruwem. Sene rem rene mek peikkerete panen yim.
41015021	Rem Jisas rene panen yibem, rem nowke yabem tame wuri rene kelowke lam. Reri sig Saimon, re Aleksanderkene Rufuskene etepri ha. Re Sairini kwomri tame. Op lan ei nai tame rem rene yak keikeren re Jisas rene kwobo lan Jisas rene peikkerete me re sen yim.
41015022	Rem Jisas rene panen kwow eisowke yin yawum. Kwow sig Golgota. Er sig reri tuma tobo et Tame Tare Bairi Emi.
41015023	Rem Jisas rene wain okkene saukaye okkene luwben rene newote selem, re ate muwem, re be am.
41015024	Ei nai tame rem rene kwurmenem mek etek peikkerem. Rem satu barow ten reri tame oub wesam.
41015025	Kerwu yabel borke simenemke, rem rene mek peikkerem.
41015026	Rem me wulale wuri poten tuma etek basrasen reri tare ya yokwok etek peikkerem. Remri rene nenem tuma rem op basrasem. JUDA TATAME ETEMRI KERYEN YEN.
41015027	Rem etop nenem, rem bisi a tame pes repne kirkir me kwuren peiken etek keikerem. Wuri rem Jisas reri let mame yokwok teteruwem, wuri rem reri let giriy yokwok teteruwem.
41015028	God Reri Siglowke basrasem Tuma er yabel sekene tem. Siglow Tuma op wem. Rem rene tame yaper remri wuri lam. (Aisaia 53:12; Luk 22:37)
41015029	Jisas rene peikkeremenem emi tatame rem eter kelowke yi yabem, rem rene tame kwuyebem, tare kwarbem, rene op webem. Kiyi ne op wem. An God Reri Kwobor berayewon sene yabel murweke an sene nente. Ne etop nente wem.
41015030	Ne kworer kwobo la. Ne me mesegenen sene yerte. Rem rene op webem.
41015031	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen etem, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame etem mere, rem tame kwuyen op webem. Kiyi re agerbo tatame remne kwobo labem, gwopte re kworer kwobo kebese be late.
41015032	Re wem, re God re Lebam Tame, re Juda tame remri keryen yen. Re me mesegenen yertek, nem etop late, nem op wete. Et sekene. Re Krais, re Juda tame remri keryen yen. Op wem. Tame pes rep Jisas rekene me kwuren peiken peikkerem tame, etep mere rep rene kirkir tame kwuyem.
41015033	Yabel nina let kere temenem, nowsel neirkap tektekwunen yin perpe yabel sene pasem.
41015034	Yabel warte nenbemke, Jisas re remri tumak yaye op wem. Eloi. Eloi, lama sabaktani. Op wem tuma tobo re gwop. Ari Apiy God. Ari Apiy God, ne berke anne mesegenye?
41015035	Op wemke, rane tatame rem etek meknik temenem, rem reri wem tuma heyar be metem, rem op wem. Metye. Re kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, rene tebo.
41015036	Remri tame wuri re amen yan yamoub poten sen yan kwole yabem wain okke sokwunen keyen me tewok leyen rene ate sen tetem. Re op wem. Wai. Nem late. Kap, Elaija re yan rene kwobo late o bo? Re op wem.
41015037	Jisas re taye yaye piten re ek sam.
41015038	Re samke, God Reri Kwoborke eismenem mate re ya yokwok pekan yeren kelare kelare tem.
41015039	Ei nai taresi tame wuri re Jisas reri bitmi yokwok tetemenem, re lam, Jisas re yaye ten ek sam. Etop lam, re op wem. Sekenewai. Er tame re God Reri Yen.
41015040	Rane ta rem kaike kera teten leklek temenem. Remri wuri te Makdala kwomri ta. Teri sig Maria. Wuri teri sig Salome. Agerbo ta wuri teri sig Maria. Te Jemskene Josepkene repri nawo. Jems pes temenem. Gwot ta teri yen Jems, re muyensi yen tame.
41015041	Kiyi Jisas re Galilike temenem, er ta rem rekene sewurbem, rene kwobo labem. Nugwape ta rem rekene Jeruselemke yam, rem etek temenem.
41015042	Perpe tem, Arimatea kwomri tame, Josep, re yam. Re Saberawiykene Tame etemri wuri. Tatame rem lam, re tame yenbo. God re kwom panen site, re etop kowmenem.
41015043	Re habom. Wore et Egesi Yabel, nem yaku be nente. Gwopte nem wos heyarte. Op habom, re be akem, re molkene ten Pailat rene yin Jisas reri kupa potte wemetem.
41015044	Pailat re danekene seken op habom. Kap, Jisas re saye? Op habom, re ei nai taresi tame rene wen yan rene op wemetem. Jisas re saye o re be satene?
41015045	Ei nai taresi tame re Pailat rene op wem. Jisas re saye. Pailat re etop metem, re Josep rene op wem. Ne Jisas reri kupa poten sen yite.
41015046	Josep re yin wulkap mate tupan sen yin Jisas reri kupa neneyeren matek leirasem. Sene re tame kupa sen yin pa purik rasen pa bukre gelkwun yan sele ragerkerem.
41015047	Makdala kwomri Maria, Josep reri nawo Mariakene rep leklek temenem, Jisas reri kupa rasem emi rep lam.
41016001	Juda tatame remri Egesi Yabel legemke, Makdala kwomri Maria etet, Jems reri nawo Maria etet, Salome etet, rem yin bosmame kwar tupam. Kwar rem Jisas reri kupa etek kereraste selem.
41016002	Sande kerwu ei berabem, ta rem sele late yim.
41016003	Rem etemwou etemwou tuma namren op wem. Yike eru ragertene pa gelkwute?
41016004	Op namren rem yin lam, pa bukre gelkwun yin kena tuknamenem. Er pa re bukrewai.
41016005	Rem pa purik wuren lam, muyensi yen tame re mame yokwo etek simenem. Re wulkap tame oub lagu wun simenem. Rem etop lan danekene sekem.
41016006	Re remne op wem. Kem danekene kap sekete. Kem Nasaret kwomri Jisas rene sopbo. Rem me kwuren peiken rene etek peikkerem, re sam. Re sene wayen yiwo. Re gwor be tetane. Reri kupa rasem emi gwo, kem la.
41016007	Kem opu yi. Pitakene Jisas reri agerbo anepoi tamekene remne op wete. Jisas re Galili yokwok kemne temnan kowte yiwo. Kem Galilike yin rene etek late. Re kemne etop kiyi wem. Kem remne etop wete.
41016008	Rem pa puri wuran amen yim. Rem habolaweyen let tewo morapkap bulam. Rem kenakem akem, eker tame wurikene tuma be namrem. Rane kiyiri siglow et gwor tuma kirkir tetane.
41016009	[Sande ei berabem, Jisas re sene wayen sim, re Makdala kwomri Maria tene kiyi yin lam. Kiyi gambo letrane kelare pes kere rem Maria tene gureremenem, Jisas re gambo wekrokem.
41016010	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem pap yaper tem, rem kiraterbem. Maria te yin remne op wesowem.
41016011	Jisas re tetane. An rene laye. Rem metem, rem teri tuma ometeke be habom.
41016012	Yuri reri anepoi tame pes rep kwom mesegenen kelowke yibem, rep Jisas rene lam. Rep rene kiyi temenemkap be lam.
41016013	Rep sene yim, Jisas reri agerbo anepoi tame remne etop wesowem, rep Jisas rene laye. Rem etop metem, rem op wem. Kep me yikokobo.
41016014	Yuri anepoi tame rem letpeis tewo wuri kerem, rem sin abemke, Jisas re remne lasyam, re remne tuma wem. Rem omuteke habobo wule be sem. Kiyi rane tatame rem Jisas rene lam, rem anepoi tame remne op wem. Jisas re sene wayen yiwo. Nem rene laye. Anepoi tame rem remri tuma omuteke be metem, eker Jisas re remne tuma wem.
41016015	Re remne op wem. Kem aboyei nowselke yin God reri Tuma Yenbo nugwape nugwape tatame remne wesowen sewurte.
41016016	Tatame rem anne omuteke habote, kem remne okke tirmunen nenewaite, God re remne potte, rem pow tete tetane. Tatame rem anne omuteke be habote, God re remne tuma nenen pete tetane.
41016017	Anne omuteke habobo tatame rem bukre wos nente. Rem ari sig wete, rem ari kitimenak omugambo remne wekrokte. Rem agerbo agerbo tumak namrete.
41016018	Rem sopo letke potte, sopo remne be tan sate. Rem tame sabo ok ate, rem be sate. Rem sikanuma nen tame remne let raste, rem heyar sene tete. Jisas re etop wem.
41016019	Haneyen Jisas re remne wen mesegenen God re rene wemke, re God reri kwomke sene yawum, re God reri mame yokwok sim.
41016020	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem kwomke kwomke tuma wesowen sewurbem. Haneyen Jisas re remne kwobo labem, rem yaku yenbo etop nenbem. Tatame rem anepoi tame remri nenem bukre wos lam, rem op wem. Remri webo tuma et sekene.]
42001001	Keryen yen Tiofilus, kiyi nugwape tame rem God reri nenbemkap rem basrasem.
42001002	Tame rem Jisas rene lam, rem reri tobotan yam yaku lam, rem nemne etop wesowem. Remri lan wesowemkap rane tame rem etop basrasem.
42001003	Aren mere, an er tuma basrasen nene newopitite selbo. Remri basrasem tumakap an etop heyar lam, an etop heyar basrasbo.
42001004	Er tuma rem nene kiyi wesowem, ne metem. Er tuma an basrasen nene newopitite, ne op mette, neri kiyi metem tuma et sekene.
42001005	Kiyi Herot re Juda tatame remri keryen yen temenem, God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame wuri re temenem. Reri sig Sekaraia. Re Abiya reri sukuw. Ta te Aron reri sukuw. Ta teri sig Elisabet.
42001006	God re lam, rep tatame yenbo. Keryen Yen reri tumakene reri wulekene rep meten nenbem.
42001007	Rep yenkene bo. Elisabet te yen game am ta. Rep ker tem.
42001008	Yabel wuri Sekaraia re agerbo tamekene rem God reri yaku God Reri Kwoborke nenbem.
42001009	Reri yaku nen tamesip rem rene op wem. Gwopte ne God rene bos yenbo yabo wos liste. Op wem, re Kwobor purik yin wurem.
42001010	Re boskene wos lisbem, nugwape tatame rem kwom geike wuriwouke wuren God rekene tuma namrebem.
42001011	Re lam, God reri kwomri tame re bos yenbo yabo wos lisbem emi mame yokwok tetemenem.
42001012	Etop lam, Sekaraia re danekene seken kenakem akem.
42001013	God reri kwomri tame re rene op wem. Sekaraia, ne mane akte. God re neri rekene namrebem tuma metem, neri ta Elisabet te tauryen wurte, ne reri sig Jon wete.
42001014	Rene wurte, neri pap kwuye mette, ne okbop tete. Nugwape tatame rem yen late, rem kirkir okbop tete.
42001015	Yuri er yen re God reri yaku yenbo nente. Keryen Yen re etop late, re rene tame yenbo wete. Er yen re ok yaper kap ate. Rene nawo te wurte, God Reri Wow re rekene som temente.
42001016	Re Israel tatame remne God Reri Tuma wesowte, nugwape tatame rem meten Keryen Yen God rene omuteke habote.
42001017	God re rene weraste, re God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, eterkap tete. Re kitimenakene tete. Yenha rem gwule tete, re remne tuma wesowte, rem sene heyar site. God rene be habobo tatame re remne tuma wesowte, rem wuribai yenbo potte. Re tatame remne op wete. Kem kemri yaper nenbo wos mesegente. Haneyen re yate tetane. God reri kwom tame re Sekaraia rene etop wem.
42001018	Sekaraia re God reri kwom tame rene op wem. Neri weye tuma et sekene o bo? An mapurke mette? An ari takene nes ker tem.
42001019	God reri kwom tame re sein op wem. An Gebriel. An God reri bitmik tetebo. Re anne werasen yawo, an nene tuma yenbo weye.
42001020	Ari weye tuma ne omuteke be metye, opkap ne tuma tibe tete tetane, ne tuma be namrete. Tuma tibe ten yin an nene weye tuma re sekene tete, neri ta te yen wurtek, ne tuma sene ek namrete tetane.
42001021	Sekaraia re God Reri Kwobor purik wurmenem, nugwape tatame rem rene sene wurate kowmenem. Rem op wem. Sekaraia re be wuratene. Re kap berke nenyek, re God Reri Kwobor purik som tetane?
42001022	Op wem, re sene yan wuram, re tuma tibo tem, re remne tuma letwouke peterabem. Rem op wem. Re wurmenye, re kap nugsikap laye, re tuma tibo teye?
42001023	Sekaraia re God Reri Kwoborke nenbem yaku legem, re reri akwulke sene yim.
42001024	Yuri Elisabet te yen panebem, liyp letrane te akek berasen sim.
42001025	Te op wem. Keryen Yen God re anne pap metem, an yen panebo. An tatame remri bitmik yite, an sebera sene be yate.
42001026	Elisabet te yen panebem liyp letrane kelare wuri kere yim, God re reri kwom tame Gebriel rene werasen Galili yokwok tetane kwom Nasaretke yim.
42001027	Re muyensi yen ta wuri tene tuma wesowte yim. Er ta rem tene tame get wemenem. Tame reri sig Josep. Re kiyi temenem Keryen Yen Devit reri beig. Muyensi yen ta teri sig Maria.
42001028	God reri kwom tame re tene pir op wem. Keryen Yen God re nene heyar nenem. Re nerenkene tetane.
42001029	Maria te etop meten te habolaweyen op habom. Er mapkap tuma?
42001030	God reri kwom tame re tene op wem. Maria ne kap akte. God re nene heyar nenem.
42001031	Yuri ne yen panete. Ne tauryen wurte, ne rene sig Jisas wete.
42001032	Yuri re keryen ken tete, tatame rem rene op wete. Re Hevenke tetane God Eterri Yen. Op wete. Kiyi Devit re keryen yen temenemkap, yuri Jisas re reri yaku potte, re keryen yen tete.
42001033	Re warege Jekop reri beig remne som panen site. Re keryen yen som temente.
42001034	Maria te God reri kwom tame rene op wem. An yen mapurke panete? An tame be yitene.
42001035	God reri kwom tame re tene sein op wem. God Reri Wow re nerenke yate tetane. God reri kitimena bukrewai re nene newote tetane. Opkap ne yen wurte, rem op wete. Er yen re yenbosubuwai. Er yen re God Eterri yen.
42001036	Metye. Neri lake Elisabet kiyi rem tene op webem. Te yen be panete. Te yen game am. Rem op webem, gwopte te ker teye, te yen panebo. Te liyp letrane kelare wuri keretene.
42001037	Aboyei wos God re kebese nenbo. Op wem.
42001038	Maria te op wem. An God reri yaku nen ta. Neri weyekap re anne etop nente, et yenbo. Op wemke, God reri kwom tame re tene mesegenen ek yim.
42001039	Keraket tem, Maria te wos teren agetage te kwowke yim, te Judia yokwori kwom etek yim.
42001040	Te Sekaraia reri akek wuren Elisabet tene pir wem.
42001041	Elisabet teri sek temenem yen re kirpem. God Reri Wow re Elisabet tene gureremenem.
42001042	Te Maria tene yaye op wem. God re nene heyar nenem. Re agerbo ta remne etop be nenem. Neri sek tetane yen God re rene kirkir heyar nente.
42001043	Ari Keryen Yen reri nawo te anne lasyawo, an okbop teye.
42001044	Neri weye pir an metye, agetage ari sek tetane yen re okbop ten re kirpeye.
42001045	God re reri wem tuma nente tetane. Ne etop omuteke habobo, ne okbop teye. Elisabet te etop wem.
42001046	Maria te op wem. An Keryen Yen rene boteyatebo, an reri sig bukre webo.
42001047	Ari wow God rene okbop tebo. God re anne Kwobo Labo Tame, re anne yenbo nenbo, an heyar tetane.
42001048	An reri yaku nen ta eisow. Re anne habom, an boteyatebo. Gwopte tetane tatame, yuri temente tatame rem wete, God re anne yenbo nenem, an metekwasbo.
42001049	God re kitimenakene, re anne bukre wos nenye, gwopte tetane tatame, yuri tete tatame rem anne tuma yenbo wete. God reri sig et yenbosubuwai.
42001050	Kiyiri tatame, gwopteri tatame, yuri tete tatame rem God reri sig bukre wete, God re remne pap mette tetane.
42001051	God re kitimenakene tame, yike tatame rem remri sig kworer bukre webem, re remne wekroken rem yikwete yakwetebo.
42001052	Re sig bukre temenem kwom panen si keryen yen remne teitkwunem. Sig bukre be temenem tame remne wepoten remri sig bukre wem.
42001053	Sikwoi sam tatame re remne awos newom, rem seketem. Wosbaskene tatame re remne wos be newom. Re remne bupo me werasen yikwetem.
42001054	Kiyi re nemri yei warege remkene tuma natobom. Er tuma re etop nenem. Re reri yaku nen tame Israel remne kwobo lam.
42001055	Re nemri warege Abraham rene be serem. Re rene pap metbem. Abraham reri nanem remne re kirkir pap som metbem.
42001056	Op wem, Maria te Elisabet tekene liyp mur ten te akwulke sene ek yim.
42001057	Elisabet te yen wurte yabel tem, te tauryen wurem.
42001058	Teri kwomri tatame, teri lakemase rem metem, Keryen Yen re tene heyar nenem, rem okbop bukre ten boteyatem.
42001059	Yabel letrane kelare mur kere tem, tame rem yam. Rem yen reri mare tumas kutem reri sig, har Sekaraia eterri sig tapene yate wem.
42001060	Nawo te me sewayen op wem. Yehow. Nem reri sig Jon wete.
42001061	Rem tene sein op wem. Er sig et neri tame beigri sig bo.
42001062	Op wem, rem har rene letke mukuteken rene op wemetem. Yen reri sig ne berke wete?
42001063	Op wem, ha re siglow wemetem, rem poten sen yan rene newom, re yen sig Jon etek basrasem. Rem etop lan danekene sekem.
42001064	Sekaraia re tumakene sene tem, re God rene tuma yenbo wem.
42001065	Kwomri tatame rem lam, re tumakene tem, rem weskene akem. Nugwape Judia nowselke tetane kwowke temenem tatame rem er tuma metem,
42001066	rem op lam, God reri kitimena er yen rekene temenem. Etop lam, rem kenakem habon op wem. Yuri er yen re haneyen tete, re be yaku potte?
42001067	God Reri Wow re Jon reri ha Sekaraia rene gureren re yuri tete wos wesowem.
42001068	Re op wem. Nem Israel tame, nem Keryen Yen rene tuma yenbo wete. Re reri tatame remne kwobo lan remne potem.
42001069	Re reri yaku nenbem yen Devit reri beig wuri potem. Er tame re kitimenakene, re nemne poten nem pow tete.
42001070	Kiyi God re reri tuma wesow tame yenbo remne tuma wesowem. Sene er tame rem tatame remne er tuma etop wesowem.
42001071	God re op wem. Kemri peiktamekene kemne wuribai yaper tetane tame remne an teitkwunte tetane.
42001072	Re sene op wem. An yeiwarege remne pap meten kiyi natobom tuma yenbo an be serbo. An som habobo.
42001073	Re nemri warege Abraham rekene tuma natobom. Kiyi wemkap gwopte re etop nente.
42001074	Re nemne peiktame remri letke potte, nem reri yaku nente, nem kap akte.
42001075	Opkap nem kwokwos kwokwos pow temente, God re late, nem reri wule yenbo nenbo, re selbo wule aboyei nem potem.
42001076	Sekaraia re op wem, Ari yen, yuri ne Keryen Yen rene temnas yin reri kelow heyarte. Tatame rem nene op wete. Re Hevenke Tetane God Reri Tuma wesowbo tame. (Malakai 3:1)
42001077	-
42001078	Ne tatame remne op wete. Kemri yaper nenbo wos kem mesegente, God re kemne potte. Nemri God re pap meten elen me nenbo Tame. Malebo tuw re nemne werasen re tatame remri yaper nenbo wos poten septin nemne potte.
42001079	Opkap kerneirke sitene tatame rem yabel geike tete. Re nemne kelmenabo kelow peterate, nem pap kwuye mette tetane. (Aisaia 9:2)
42001080	Op wemke, yuri Jon re haneyen tem, re God rene habom. Re tamekene bo emik yin Israel tatame remne tuma wesowte yabel kowmenem.
42002001	Yuri Romri Keryen Yen Ogastus re wule wuri nenem. Re op wem. Nugwape kwomri tatame remri sig nem potte.
42002002	Kiyi rem tatame remri sig be potbem. Sene re etop nenem. Er nabe Kwirinius re Siria yokwori keryen yen temenem.
42002003	Nugwape tatame rem remri maime kwomke yim. Rem remri sig newote yim.
42002004	Josep re Devit reri beig. Kiyi Devit reri nawot te rene Betlehemke wurem, eker Josep re Galili yokwori kwom Nasaret mesegenen Judia yokwori kwom Betlehemke yim.
42002005	Re reri ta Maria tekene rep etop repri sig newote yim. Maria tene Josep rene get wemenem, ayi ayabem, te yen panebem, rep etep yim.
42002006	Yin Betlehemke temenem, Maria teri yen wurte yabel ek tem.
42002007	Te masetebo yen, tauryen wurem. Te rene matek leyen bulmakau remri awos abem yibuk yewon rasem. Tatame tuknabo ake bukre tatamek pulaumenem, eker rep bulmakau remri akek yin temenemke, te yen etek wurem.
42002008	Sipsip lakerebem tame rem Betlehem kwom sag meknik temenem. Neirke rem remri sipsip etek lakerebem.
42002009	God reri kwomri tame wuri re yan Keryen Yen God reri yabel rik pasrasem. Sipsip lakerebem tame rem kenakem akem.
42002010	God reri kwom tame re remne op wem. Kem mane akte. Metye. An kemne tuma yenbo wesowte yawo. Ari wete tuma, nugwape tatame rem okbop ten boteyatete tetane.
42002011	Gwopte neir ta wuri te Devit reri kwomke yen wurye. Yuri er yen re kemne potte tetane. Reri sig Krais, re Haneyen.
42002012	Kem ari tuma metbo, kem op webo. Reri tuma et sekene o sekene bo? Kem yin rene late. Nawo te rene matek leyen rastene. Re bulmakau awos abo yibuk tuknatene. Kem etop late, kem ari webo tuma sene habon op wete. Reri weye tuma et sekene.
42002013	Op wemke, agetage God reri kwom tame nugwapewai rem rekene yan wuren rem God rene tuma yenbo wem, rem reri sig bukre op wem.
42002014	Ukyawai Hevenke tetane God, nem rene yenbowai webo. Re metekwasbo nowselke tetane tatame remne pap pultete, rem pap yenbo temente.
42002015	God reri kwom tame rem sipsip lakere tame remne mesegenen God reri kwom Hevenke sene yawum. Sipsip lakere tame rem op wem. Nem ayi. Keryen Yen reri nemne weye tuma nem Betlehem kwomke yin late.
42002016	Op wemke, rem agetage yin lam, Mariakene Josepkene rep etek temenem. Yen re bulmakau remri awos abo yibuk tuknamenem.
42002017	Rem etop lan wuran God reri kwomri tame reri wem tuma rem tatame remne etop wesowem.
42002018	Nugwape tatame rem sipsip lakerebo tame remri tuma metem, rem danekene sekem.
42002019	Maria te remri wem tuma som habobem, te be serem.
42002020	Sipsip lakerebo tame rem sene yim. Yibem, God reri kwom tame reri wem tuma, remri lam wos rem habom, rem God reri sig bukre wem.
42002021	Yabel letrane kelare mur kera yim, rem yen reri mare tumas kuten reri sig wem. Rem reri sig Jisas wem. Kiyi nawo te yen rene be panemenem, God reri kwom tame re er sig weruwem.
42002022	Liyp wuri tem, Mariakene Josepkene rep yen sen Jerusalemke yim. Rep Moses Reri Wule nenen Keryen Yen God rene yen newote yim.
42002023	God reri wule op wem. Kemri masetebo yen tauryen, kem poten Keryen Yen God rene newon op wete. Gwor yen et nereri.
42002024	God reri agerbo wule op wem. Kem apbour pes o mur poten lisen anne newote. Op wemke, Mariakene Josepkene rep God rene ap pes newote yim.
42002025	Tame wuri re Jerusalemke temenem. Reri sig Simeon. Re tame yenbo, re God rekene tuma namrebem, sekwo lombem tame. Israel tatame remne potte tame rene re kowmenem. God Reri Wow re eterkene temenem.
42002026	Kiyi God Reri Wow re rene op wem. Ne kiyi be sate. Ne Keryen Yen reri lebam yen, Krais, rene latek, ne ek sate.
42002027	Op wem, God Reri Wow re rene wem, re God Reri Kwoborke wurem. Kiyi wem wulekap, nawoha rep Jisas rene etop nente sen yam.
42002028	Simeon re yen rene letke poten semenem, re God rene wese an op wem.
42002029	Keryen Yen, an neri yaku nen tame. Neri kiyi wem wos an laye, ari wuribai kwuye metye, eker an sate, et yenbo.
42002030	Nemne Potte Tame an rene areri lek laye.
42002031	Neren, ne rene werasen re nugwape tatame remne heyar nente. Re yawo, an etop laye.
42002032	Re tuwkap. Re agerbo kwomri tatame remne kelow yenbo peterate yawo. Israel tatame nugwape remri sig re bukre wete tetane.
42002033	Jisas reri nawoha rep Simeon reri wem tuma op metem, rep danekene sekem.
42002034	Simeon re remne tuma yenbo wem. Re yen reri nawo Maria tene op wem. Metye. God re gwor Yen rene lebam. Rane Israel tatame rem rene magel taite, rem sene yaper tete tetane. Rane rem rene pap yewote, rem sene heyar tete tetane. God re rene werasem, tatame rem rene tuma yaper wete tetane.
42002035	Agerbo tatame rem etop late, tuma yaper wete tame remri berastene wuribai et tegek tete. Yuri ne pap yaper tete tetane. Opkap metbo mus et pik pebo muskap. Simeon re Maria tene etop wem.
42002036	Tuma wesow ta wuri, teri sig Ana, te Fanuel eterri yen, te Aser reri tame beigke temenem. Kiyi te tame yimenem, nabe letrane kelare pes kere tem, tame re ek sam.
42002037	Nabe nugwape (84) te wane ta simenem, te keryen ta temenem. Te God Reri Kwobor be mesegenbem. Neirkene yabelkene te God rene lom yokwobem, te awos lek labem, te God rekene tuma namrebem.
42002038	Er yabel nawoha rep Jisas rene sen yim, et ta te yan yen rene lam. Te God rene wese an te tatame remne er yen rene God rene kowmenem tatame nugwape remne wesowem.
42002039	Keryen Yen reri wem wule rem etop nenem, Josepkene Mariakene rep repri kwom Nasaretke sene yim. Nasaret et Galili yokwok tetane.
42002040	Yen re haneyen tem, re kitimenakene nugwape purerekene temenem. Etop temenem, God re rene pap meten rene heyar nenem.
42002041	Nabe wulare wulare Jisas reri nawoha rep God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabel habon awos ate Jerusalemke yaubem.
42002042	Jisas reri nabe letpeis tewo pes kere tem, remri kiyi nenbemkap, rem etop sene nenem. Rem God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabelke habon Jerusalem kwomke yawum.
42002043	Er egesi yabel bukre legem, rem akwulke sene yim. Muyensi yen tame, Jisas, re Jerusalemke som temenem. Nawoha rep etop be sanem.
42002044	Rene be lam, rep op habom. Re agerbo tatamekene yibem. Rep yabel wuri yimke, rep repri tame beig remri borke rene sopen yim.
42002045	Rep rene be lamke, rep Jerusalemke rene sopte yim.
42002046	Yabel pes rep rene soplaweyem. Yabel murwek rep rene lam, re God Reri Kwoborke wuren simenem. Re tuma peikbem tame remri borborke sin remri tuma metbem. Re remne tuma sein wemetbem.
42002047	Tame rem reri purere, reri sein webem tuma metem, rem danekene sekem.
42002048	Nawoha rep rene op lam, rep danekene sekem. Nawo te rene op wem. Yen, berke ne nesne opkap nenye? Nes nene soplaweiwo, nes ha rekene wuribai yaper teye.
42002049	Re repne sein op wem. Berke kep anne sopye? An ari Apiy reri akek sitene. Kep etop be mettene?
42002050	Reri op wem tuma tobo rep be sanem.
42002051	Re repkene Nasaret kwomke sene yin tem, re kwokwos kwokwos repri tuma meten tobobem. Reri webem tuma nawo te poten etetri wuribaike tebem.
42002052	Jisas re haneyen tem, re purere yenbo potem. Tatame rem rene okbop tem, God eter mere, re rene okbop tem.
42003001	Taiberius re Rom tatame remri keryen yen temenem. Nabe letpeis tewo letrane (15), re keryen yen som temenem. Pontius Pailat re Judia yokwori tatame remri keryen yen. Herot re Galili yokwori tatame remri keryen yen. Reri maser, Filip, re Ituria yokwo, Trakonitis yokwori tatame remri keryen yen temenem, Lisanias re Abilene yokwori tatame remri keryen yen temenem.
42003002	Anaskene Kaiafaskene rep God reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen temenem. Er yabel Jon, Sekaraia reri yen, re tamekene bo emik temenem, God re rene tuma wepeteyam.
42003003	Jon re Jordan Peik yokwori kwomke kwomke yin tatame remne tuma wesowbem. Re op webem. Kem kemri yaper nenbo wos mesegente, an kemne okke panen waren tirmunte. God re kemri yaper nenbo wos poten septite, re kemne tuma be wete. Re op webem.
42003004	Kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Aisaia, re er tuma siglowke op basrasem. Tame wuri re tamekene bo emik temente, re tuma yaye op wete. Kem Keryen Yen reri kelow nowbte. Kem reri kelow heyar nente.
42003005	Wau temente, kem sel yewote. Kwow bukre temente, kem sel tan heyarte. Kwur kwartene kelow kem heyar sene rasen sagwunate. Pa temente kelow kem heyar sene nente.
42003006	Op nente, nemne potte Tame rene God re werasen yate. Nem etop late.
42003007	Nugwape tatame rem Jon rene lasyam, Jon re remne okke panen waren tirmunte. Re remne op wem. Kem sopo yaperkap, kem wuribai yaperkene tatame. Yuri God re pap yoken tatame remne paku pete, re kemne kirkir pete tetane. Yike kemne amete wem?
42003008	Kiyi kem wule yenbo nente. Kem op nente, nem sanete, kem yaper nenbo wos mesegenye. Kem mane op wete. Abraham re neremri warege. Re tame yenbo, eker nerem mere, nem tame yenbo. Kemri op webo tuma et tuma sekene bo. Kem Abraham reri nan, kem tame yenbo bo. Reri nenbemkap, kem etop be nenbo. Kemri wuribai yaper kem mesegente, kem tame yenbo ek tete. God re selte, re gwor pa poten tatame nente, sene rem Abraham reri yen tete. Kem bupo kap op wete. Nem Abraham eterri yen.
42003009	Yuri yate tame re wer sete tamekap. Re me teite, re somok teite. Nugwape me rem supa yenbo be yabo, re er me remne teyen kerke liste tetane.
42003010	Re op wemke, nugwape tatame rem rene op wemetem. Nem berke nente?
42003011	Re remne sein op wem. Tame re tame oub pes temente, wuri re tame oubkene bo tame rene newote. Awos tetane tame re etopwou nente. Re awoskene bo tame remne awos newote. Re op wem.
42003012	Kel potbem tame rem Jon rene lasyam, Jon re remne okke tirmunte wem, rem rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, nem berke nente?
42003013	Re remne sein op wem. Kem kel potte, kem keremri keryen yen eter webokapwou potte. Kem kel tep bisi kap ate. Re remne op wem.
42003014	Ei nai tame rem rene yan op wemetem. Nerem, nem mapurke nente? Re remne sein op wem. Kem tame remne kap pen remri kel ek potte. Kem tame remne tuma kap yikokon nenen remri kel ek potte. Kem kemri yaku nenbo tokwowou kem poten okbop tete.
42003015	Tatame rem Jon reri tuma metem, rem rene op habom. Kap Jon re Krais, God eter lebam tame?
42003016	Jon re remne op wem. An kemne okke panen waren tirmunte. Yuri tame wuri re yate tetane, re tame bukre, tame yenbo. An tame eisow. An tame yenbo bo, nes wolbaye wurik be site. An eisow yen, an selke site. Er tame re God Reri Wow kemne newote tetane. Kemri yaper nenbo wos re kerke liste tetane.
42003017	Rais wes tame rem poten ker petewarbokap, er tame re tatame yaper remne kerke petewarte tetane. Er ker re som eibet tetane. Tame rem rais om poten akek rasbokap, re tatame yenbo remne reri akek panen yite tetane.
42003018	Op wem, Jon re God Reri Tuma Yenbo remne weiwebem, agerbo agerbo tuma re remne kirkir wesowbem.
42003019	Yuri Jon re Keryen Yen Herot rene tuma op wem. Ne neri mase reri ta, Herodias, tene kerepoten panem. Et yaper. Agerbo yaper wos nugwape ne kirkir nenbem.
42003020	Op wemke, Herot re yaper sene nenem, re Jon rene ake yaperke wen wurem.
42003021	Jon re nugwape tatame remne kiyi okke panen waren tirmunem, yuri re Jisas rene kirkir panen okke waren tirmunem. Waren wayem, Jisas re God rekene tuma namrebem, rem lam, gwan beram.
42003022	God Reri Wow re nelke bour apkap rene yeren sim. Tuma wuskiy nelke op wem. Ne ari meseke mogul Yen. An nene okbop tebo.
42003023	Kiyi Jisas re yaku tobotam, reri nabe et tame wuriri ok agerbo tameri letpeis (30). Tatame rem rene op habom. Re Josep eterri yen. Josep re Heli eterri yen.
42003024	Heli re Matat eterri yen. Matat re Livai eterri yen. Livai re Melki eterri yen. Melki re Janai eterri yen. Janai re Josep eterri yen.
42003025	Josep re Matatias eterri yen. Matatias re Amos eterri yen. Amos re Nahum eterri yen. Nahum re Esli eterri yen. Esli re Nagai eterri yen.
42003026	Nagai re Mat eterri yen. Mat re Matatias eterri yen. Matatias re Semen eterri yen. Semen re Josek eterri yen. Josek re Joda eterri yen.
42003027	Joda re Joanan eterri yen. Joanan re Resa eterri yen. Resa re Serubabel eterri yen. Serubabel re Sealtiel eterri yen. Sealtiel re Neri eterri yen.
42003028	Neri re Melki eterri yen. Melki re Adi eterri yen. Adi re Kosam eterri yen. Kosam re Elmadam eterri yen. Elmadam re Er eterri yen.
42003029	Er re Josua eterri yen. Josua re Elieser eterri yen. Elieser re Jorim eterri yen. Jorim re Matat eterri yen. Matat re Livai eterri yen.
42003030	Livai re Simeon eterri yen. Simeon re Juda eterri yen. Juda re Josep eterri yen. Josep re Jonam eterri yen. Jonam re Eliakim eterri yen.
42003031	Eliakim re Melea eterri yen. Melea re Mena eterri yen. Mena re Matata eterri yen. Matata re Natan eterri yen. Natan re Devit eterri yen.
42003032	Devit re Jesi eterri yen. Jesi re Obet eterri yen. Obet re Boas eterri yen. Boas re Salmon eterri yen. Salmon re Nason eterri yen.
42003033	Nason re Aminadap eterri yen. Aminadap re Atmin eterri yen. Atmin re Arni eterri yen. Arni re Hesron eterri yen. Hesron re Peres eterri yen. Peres re Juda eterri yen.
42003034	Juda re Jekop eterri yen. Jekop re Aisak eterri yen. Aisak re Abraham eterri yen. Abraham re Tera eterri yen. Tera re Nahor eterri yen.
42003035	Nahor re Seruk eterri yen. Seruk re Reu eterri yen. Reu re Pelek eterri yen. Pelek re Eber eterri yen.
42003036	Eber re Sela eterri yen. Sela re Kainan eterri yen. Kainan re Arpaksat eterri yen. Arpaksat re Siem eterri yen. Siem re Noa eterri yen. Noa re Lamek eterri yen.
42003037	Lamek re Metusela eterri yen. Metusela re Enok eterri yen. Enok re Jaret eterri yen. Jaret re Mahalalel eterri yen. Mahalalel re Kenan eterri yen.
42003038	Kenan re Enos eterri yen. Enos re Set eterri yen. Set re Adam eterri yen. Adam re God eterri yen.
42004001	Jisas re Jordan Peik mesegenen yim, God Reri Wow re eterkene temenem, re Jisas rene panen re tamekene bo emik yin temenem.
42004002	Neir tame pesri ok, yabel tame pesri ok (40), re etek temenem. Jisas re awos be abem, re bupo me temenem. Yuri er yabel aboyei legem, re kwoi sam, gambo remri keryen yen, Satan, re yan rene seilam.
42004003	Satan re rene op wem. Ne God reri yen sekene temente, ne wetek, gwor pa rem nakwu tete, ne poten ate. Ne etop nente, an lan op wete. Ne God Eterri yen.
42004004	Jisas re rene sein op wem. God reri siglow re op webo. Tatame rem awoswou ate habote, rem heyar be temente.
42004005	Sene Satan re Jisas rene panen kwowke yawun Jisas rene agetage aboyei nowselri kwom peteram.
42004006	Re Jisas rene op wem. An nene er kwom newote, ne er kwom panen site. Aboyei nugwape yenbo kanbo wos er kwomke tetane, an nene ab newokeipte. Et wos aboyei et areri. An yike tamene newote wete, ankene newote.
42004007	Ne gulke pan anne lom yokwote, aboyei wos an nene newote.
42004008	Jisas re rene sein op wem. God reri siglow op webo. Kem Keryen Yen God eternewou lom yokwobet, eternewou yaku nenbet.
42004009	Sene Satan re Jisas rene Jerusalem kwomke panen yim. Re rene God Reri Kwobor magelke panen yawun tetem, re rene op wem. Ne God Reri Yen temente, ne opu kirpen war.
42004010	God reri siglow op webo. God re reri kwomri tame remne werasen yate, rem nene kwobo late.
42004011	Tuma sene op webo. Neri tewo pak be pete, rem nene letke poten ne heyar waren tetete.
42004012	Op wem, Jisas re rene sein op wem. God reri siglow op webo. God re neri Keryen Yen, ne rene kap seilate.
42004013	Satan re rene seilaweyem, re rene mesegenen yim, re agerbo yabelke rene sene seilate kowem.
42004014	God Reri Wow re Jisas eterkene temenem, re Galili yokwok sene yim. Jisas reri nenem wos kwomri kwomri tatame rem metem.
42004015	Jisas re God reri akek wuren tatame remne tuma yenbo wesowbem, rem reri sig bukre webem.
42004016	Yuri Jisas re Nasaret kwomke yim. Kiyi re eisow yen temenem, re Nasaret kwomke temenem. Re kiyi nenbemkap, egesi yabelke re God reri akek wurem. Re God Reri Siglowke basrasmenem tuma late tetem.
42004017	Rem Aisaia reri basrasem siglow rene newom, re tuma wuri sopen lan re op wem.
42004018	Keryen Yen Reri Wow re arenke tetane. Re anne lebam, an woskene bo tatame remne tuma yenbo wesowte. Re anne werasen yan tuma wesowte, ake yaperke tetane tame rem ake yaper mesegenen sene yite. Le si tame rem heyar sene late. Re anne werasen yam, an pap yaper metbo tatame remne tuma yenbo wesowte, rem pap kwuye mette.
42004019	Re anne werasen yam, God re reri tatame remne potte yabelri tuma an remne etop wesowte.
42004020	Op wem, Jisas re siglow sene gwolbekerem, re ake lakere tame rene sene newon re sene ek sim. Nugwape tatame rem God reri akek simenem, rem eternewou leklek temenem.
42004021	Re remne op wem. God reri basrasem tuma kem gwopte metye, er tuma re gwopte sekene teye.
42004022	Op wem, tatame rem reri sig bukre wem. Re remne tuma yenbo heyar wemke, rem op habo op habon op wem. Er tame re Josep eterri yen. Mapurke re er tuma webo?
42004023	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem tuma anne op wete. Ne tatame remne heyar nenbo tame, ne kworer heyar nente. Kem anne sene op wete. Neri Kaperneamke nenem wos nemri metemkap, ne neri maime kwomke sene nente.
42004024	An kemne sekeneker webo. Tuma wesow tame reri kwomri tatame rem rene pap be yewobo, rem rene magel taibo.
42004025	Metye. An kemne sekeneker webo. Kiyi Elaija re temenem, nugwape wane ta rem Israelke temenem. Nabe mur, liyp letrane kelare wuri kerem, mou be tibem. Nugwape tatame kwomke kwomke rem akwoi sim.
42004026	God re Elaija rene Israelri wane ta etemne be werasen yim. Yehow. Re rene werasen Sarefat kwomri wane ta etetnewou lasyim. Sarefat kwom et Saidon yokwok tetane.
42004027	Sene God Reri Tuma wesowbem tame, Elaija, re temenem, nugwape nomape tame rem Israelke temenem. God re remne heyar be nenem. Yehow. Siria yokwori tame, Naman, eternewou God re rene heyar nenem.
42004028	Tatame rem God reri akek temenem, rem Jisas reri wem tuma etop metem, rem kenakem pap bukre yokem.
42004029	Rem teten Jisas rene keikeren rene ya yokwo keren kwom geike liyten wurem. Rem remri kwom sitene kwowke rene panen yawum. Rem rene etek sokwunte nenem.
42004030	Re etemri borke yin remne mesegenem.
42004031	Jisas re Kaperneam kwomke yim. Kaperneam kwom et Galili yokwok tetane. Egesi Yabel re God reri akek wuren remne tuma peikem.
42004032	Rem reri tuma metem, rem danekene sekem. Keryen yen remri wesowbemkap re remne etopkap wesowbem, eker rem danekene sekem.
42004033	God reri akek temenem tame rene gambo gureremenem, re tuma yaye op wem.
42004034	Jisas, ne Nasaret kwomri tame. Ne kap nemne berke nente? Ne nemne kap botkute yawo? Nem nene latene. Ne God eterri tame yenbo. Re nene werasen yam.
42004035	Jisas re rene tuma sein op wem. Ne elen me te. Ne er tame rene mesegenen yite. Op wem, gambo re tame rene etemri bitmik selke teren rene mesegenen ek yim. Gambo re rene yaper be nenem, re bupo me yim.
42004036	Nugwape tatame rem etop lam, rem danekene sekem, rem etemwou etemwou op wem. Reri weye tuma et mapkap tuma? Re kitimenakene tamekap webo, gambo rem reri tuma metbo, rem tame remne mesegenen yibo.
42004037	Nugwape kwom rem Jisas reri nenem wos aboyei metkeipem.
42004038	Jisas re God reri ake mesegenen yin Saimon eterri akek wurem. Saimon reri owyit te yaper metbem, wesom kirkir nignigbem, rem Jisas rene tene kwobo late wem.
42004039	Re yin tukna tiy meknik tetem, teri yaper kwuye mette wem. Op tem, teri yaper boyem, agetage te wayen teten remne awos nenem.
42004040	Yabel warbem, tatame rem hekna habana sikanuma nenbem tametiy remne Jisas eterne panen yam. Jisas re reri let nugwape tatame remne wulare wulare keren yin rem kwuye metem.
42004041	Gambo yaper rem nugwape tatame remne mesegenen yim. Rem yaye op wem. Ne God Eterri yen. Jisas re remne sewayen op wem. Kem etop mane wete.
42004042	Ei berabemke, Jisas re er kwom mesegenen tamekene bo emik yim. Tatame rem rene sopen yin lam, rem rene keikerete wem. Rem op habom. Re nemne kap mesegenen yite.
42004043	Re remne op wem. God re anne werasen yam, an God reri kwom panen site tuma yenbo agerbo kwomke wesowen sewurte.
42004044	Op wemke, re Judia nowselke sewurbem, re God reri akek wuren tatame remne God Reri Tuma yenbo wesowbem.
42005001	Yuri Jisas re Genesaret peik kupa barke temenem, nugwape tatame rem meknik yan teten kur rasem. Rem God eterri tuma mette yam.
42005002	Jisas re lam, pere pes peik barke liyten yawun rasmenem. Omyen potbem tame rem pere mesegenen remri wuli ok keyate yim.
42005003	Jisas re perek waren sim, re pere mutame, Saimon, rene op wem. Ne pere puwkwunem opre wur. Op nenem, Jisas re perek sin re tatame remne tuma peikbem.
42005004	Tuma peiken legem, re Saimon rene op wem. Ne ik piyan yi. Ne, nerenkene yaku nenbo tamekene kem wuli okke sene rasen omyen pot.
42005005	Saimon re rene sein op wem. Haneyen. Neir nem yaku bukre keren yan nemne eikene beraye. Nem omyen be wuri potye. Neren weyek, an neri tuma meten wuli ek raste nenbo.
42005006	Op wen rem yin wuli rasen omyen nugwape wuren wulikene weyarte nenem.
42005007	Rem remri yaku nen tamesip remne yate tem. Rem agerbo perek temenem, rem yan omyen poten pere peske yewon pulawem. Pere rep gergerte nenem.
42005008	Saimon Pita re op lam, re yin Jisas eterri tewo tobok gulke pan op wem. Haneyen, an yaper wos nenbo tame. Ne anne mesegenen yite.
42005009	Pita eter, eterkene temenem tame rem remri potem omyen lam, rem danekene sekem.
42005010	Saimon eterri anepoi Jemskene Jonkene etop mere rep danekene sekem. Rep Sebedi eterri yen. Jisas re Saimon rene op wem. Ne mane akte. Kiyi ne omyen potbem. Ne omyen potbokap, yuri ne tatame remne etopkap potte. Ne tatame remne ari tuma yenbo wesowtek, rem ari anepoi tete.
42005011	Op wemke, rem pere liyten yawun peik barke rasen rem remri wosbas aboyei mesegenen rene semowwen yim.
42005012	Yuri Jisas re agerbo kwomke yin temenem, nomape tame re eter kwomke kirkir temenem. Re Jisas rene lam, re gulke pan gwuromen rene op wem. Haneyen, ne selte, ne anne heyar nente.
42005013	Jisas re rene let keren op wem. An selye. Ne heyar me tete. Op wemke, eter webem tuma egegekene rene temenem numa sok tem.
42005014	Jisas re rene op wem. An nene heyar nenye. Ne yikene kap wesowte. Agetage ne yin God reri Kwoborke yaku nenbo tame rene neri wesom peterate. Moses reri kiyi wem tuma ne etop nente. Ne God rene kwar pete. Ne op nente, tatame rem lan sanete, neri numa sok tem, ne heyar tetane.
42005015	Tatame rem reri nenbemkap wesowem, nugwape kwomri tatame rem er tuma meten rem Jisas rene lasyabem. Rem remri hekna habana sikanuma nenbem tatame re remne heyar nente kirkir panen yabem.
42005016	Rane yabel re tatame remne mesegenen tamekene bo emik yin God rekene tuma ek namrebem.
42005017	Yuri Jisas re tatame remne tuma peikbem, Farisi tame, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem yan etek kirkir simenem. Rem Galili yokwokene Judia yokwokeneri kwomke kwomke yam. Rane rem Jerusalem kwomke yam. Keryen Yen God re Jisas rene kitimena newom, re hekna habana sikanuma nenbem tatame remne heyarem.
42005018	Rane tame rem kuw let tewo negel met tame rene tamewopke yewon sen yan akek wuren Jisas eterne meknik raste nenem.
42005019	Rem rene sen wurlaweyem, emi natkelbesem. Rem rene ake magelke sen yawun rope okmei wuri regen tame wopkene rene newokwunen nugwape tatame etemri borke Jisas eterri bitmi tobok rasem.
42005020	Jisas re lam, rem reri kitimena omuteke habom, eker re kuw let tewo negel met tame rene op wem. Ari tametiy, an neri sebera ya wos poten septiye.
42005021	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene Farisi tamekene rem etemwou etemwou op webem. Er tame re yike? Reri op weye tuma, re God rene tuma yaper weye. Tame rem agerbo tame remri sebera ya wos kebese be poten septibo. Yehow. God eterwou re etop nenbo.
42005022	Jisas re remri wuribai lam, re remne op wemetem. Kem berke opkap wuribai potye?
42005023	Be tuma an kebese be wete? An op wete. An neri sebera ya wos poten septiye. Et bukre wos, o an rene op wete. Ne heyar teten sene wayen yite, et bukre wos?
42005024	An More Tame Tem Tame, an gwor nowselke tetane. An kitimenakene tame, eker an yaper nenbo wos kebese poten septite. Ari kitimena an kemne peterate. Kem la. Op wemke, re kuw let tewo negel met tame rene op wem. An nene webo. Ne wayen teten neri tamewop poten sen neri akwulke yi.
42005025	Agetage er tame re tatame etemri bitmik teten reri tamewop poten eterri akek sen yim. Yibem, re God reri sig bukre webem.
42005026	Tatame rem danekene sekem, rem God rene tuma yenbo op wem. Gwopte nem kiyi be lamenem wos laye.
42005027	Yuri Jisas re weran yin lam, kel potbem tame re kel rasbem akek simenem. Tame reri sig Livai. Jisas re rene op wem. Ne arenkene yate.
42005028	Op wemke, re teten nugwape wos mesegenen Jisas eterkene yim.
42005029	Sene Livai re Jisas rene nugwape awos eterri akek nenem. Kel potbem tamekene agerbo tame nugwapekene rem wuriwouke sin repkene awos abem.
42005030	Farisikene Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene rem op lam, rem Jisas reri anepoi tame remne op wemetem. Kem berke kel potbo tamekene agerbo wule yaper nenbo tame remkene awos etop abo? Et yaper.
42005031	Jisas re remri wem tuma metem, re remne tuma sein op wem. Yaper be metbo tame rem dokta remne be lasyibo. Sikanuma nen tame etemwou rem dokta remne lasyibo.
42005032	Opkap an tatame yenbo etemne be potte yatene. Yehow. An yaper wos nenbo tatame etemne potte yatene.
42005033	Re op wemke, rane tatame rem Jisas rene op wem. Nugwape yabel tatame remne Okke Panen Waren Tirmunbo tame, Jon, reri anepoi tame rem wule yenbo sebo. Rem awos pelebiten God rekene tuma namrebo. Farisi remri anepoi tame rem etopkap kirkir nenbo. Neri anepoi tame rem op be nenbo. Nugwape yabel rem awos abo, rem awos be pelebitebo.
42005034	Re remne sein op wem. Tame re ta panete nenbo, re reri tametiy remne ta pane kisen awos ate ten yate. Ta panete tame re temente, rem kap awos pelebitete? Yehow. Rem awos som abet.
42005035	Yuri ta panete tame re sene yite, reri tametiy rem awos pelebitete. Gwopte an ari anepoi remkene tetane, eker rem awos abo.
42005036	Re remne sikur sakur tuma op wem. Tame rem weyartene tame oub suba tetane, rem tame oub ager kera be poten weyartene tame oub subak rasen kambo. Rem op nente, tame oub ager re weyarte, subakene ager kerakene repne kwuye be late.
42005037	Yuri nenem wain ok tame rem kiyiri ok tibo girbuw subak be yewobo. Op nente, yuri nenem wain ok re wayen pulaubo, girbuw suba re pekan yuri nenem wain ok re selke sirpitibo. Op nenbo, girbuw re yaper tebo.
42005038	Yuri nenem wain ok rem girbuw agerke yewobo, girbuw re be pekabo.
42005039	Tame rem kiyiri wain okwou abo. Rem yuri nenem wain ok abo, rem okbop be tebo. Rem op webo. Kiyiri wain ok et yenbo. Jisas re etop wem.
42006001	Yuri agerbo Egesi Yabelke, Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem wit now borborke yibem. Anepoi tame rem wit supa kwosen yin etemri letke semenen am.
42006002	Farisi tame rem lan op wem. Neri anepoi tame rem egesi yabelke wit supa kwosen abo, rem nemri wule biragiyebo. Et yaper.
42006003	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Devit re kiyi temenem keryen yen. Reri nenem wos rem basrasem. Kem kap er siglow be latene. Kiyi Devit re eterri sukuwkene rem kwoisam, rem kap be awos am?
42006004	Devit re God reri akek wuren God rene rasem geil poten am. Re reri sukuw remne kirkir newon am. Nemri wule gwop. God rene newobo geil God eterri akek yaku nenbo tame etemwou abo. Nugwape tatame rem be abo. Devit re reri sukuwkene rem er wule beragiyen God rene newom geil poten am. Rem op nenem, rem tuma be wem.
42006005	An More Tame Tem Tame. Aren, an egesi yabelri Keryen Yen. Be wos an egesi yabelke nente wete, remkene nente. Jisas re op wem.
42006006	Agerbo Egesi Yabel, Jisas re God reri akek yin wuren tatame remne tuma peikbem, ya yaper tame reri mame yokwo ya telmenem, re etek simenem.
42006007	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene Farisikene rem Jisas rene tuma nente kelow tobo sopbem. Opkap, rem rene leklek heyar temenem. Re kap tame rene Egesi Yabelke heyarte o be heyarte? Re heyarte, nem rene tuma nente.
42006008	Jisas re remri wuribai lan re ya yaper tame rene op wem. Ne wayen remri bitmik tete. Op wem, re wayen etek tetem.
42006009	Jisas re tatame remne op wem. An kemne wemetbo. Nemri wule Egesi Yabel map webo? Egesi yabelke nem yenbo wos nente, o nem yaper wos nente? Egesi Yabel tame re sate nenbet, nem rene kwobo lan heyar nente, o nem rene yaper nenen re sate?
42006010	Re remne lan kwuren sene re ya yaper tame rene op wem. Ne neri let sigil. Re let sigilpitimke, reri let heyar tem.
42006011	Farisi tamekene Moses Reri Wule peikbem tamekene rem op lam, rem pap yoken etemwou etemwou op wem. Nem Jisas rene pen sate.
42006012	Jisas re kwowke yawun God rekene tuma namren yin eikene beram.
42006013	Re reri anepoi tame remne wen yan wuriwouke wuren re letpeis tewo pes kere tame etemnewou lebam. Lebam tame remri sig gwor.
42006014	Wuri re Saimon. Jisas re rene agerbo sig Pita wem. Wuri re Andru, Saimon eterri mase. Agerbo rem Jems, Jon, Filip, Bartolomyu,
42006015	Matyu, Tomas. Wuri re Alfius eterri yen Jems. Wuri re Saimon, reri agerbo sig Selot.
42006016	Wuri re Judas, Jems eterri yen. Wuri re Judas Iskariot. Yuri Judas re Jisas rene yena tem.
42006017	Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem kwow mesegenen waren selwawke tetem. Nugwape tatame rem yam. Judia yokwori tatame, Jerusalem kwomri tatame, peik barke tetane kwom pes Tairkene Saidonkeneri tatame rem yan etekwou temenem.
42006018	Rem Jisas reri tuma mette, remri temenem sikanuma re remne kirkir heyarte yam. Gambo yaper gureremenem tatame etem mere rem yam, Jisas re gambo remne wekrokem.
42006019	Nugwape tatame rem lam, Jisas reri kitimenak tatame remne heyar tebem. Op lamke, rem kirkir heyar tete selem, eker rem Jisas rene let kerelate yam.
42006020	Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne lan op wem. Kem woskene bo tame, kem metekwaste. God reri panen sitene kwom et keremri.
42006021	Gwopte kwoi sabo tame kem metekwaste. Kem awos an sekete tetane. Kirabo tame kem metekwaste. Yuri kem sak keyete tetane.
42006022	An More Tame Tem Tame, kem anne omuteke habobo. Opkap, tatame rem kemne be metekwaste, rem kemne magel taite, rem kemne tuma yaper wete, rem kemne op wete. Kem tatame yaper. Rem op nente, kem okbop tete.
42006023	Kemri tokwo bukre et God eterri kwomke tetane, eker kem okbop ten metekwaste. Gwopte tetane tatame remri yeiwarege rem God Reri Tuma wesowbem tame remne etop yaper nenbem.
42006024	Wosbaskene tame, kem pap yaper tete tetane. Gwopte kem wosbaskene tetane, kem okbop tebo. Yuri kem okbop be tete tetane.
42006025	Gwopte awos an seketbo tatame, yuri kem pap yaper tete, kem kwoi sate tetane. Gwopte sak keyebo tatame, yuri kem pap yaper tete, kem kirate tetane.
42006026	Nugwape tatame rem kemri sig yenbowai webo. Remri yeiwarege kiyi rem yikoko tuma wesowbem tame remri sig etop kirkir yenbo webem. Opkap tatame kem ei etop habo. Yuri kem yaper tete tetane.
42006027	Ari tuma metbo tatame, an kemne webo. Kem kemri peiktame remne pap yewote. Tatame rem kemne be metekwasbo, kem remne heyar nente.
42006028	Tatame rem kemne tuma yaper webo, kem remne tuma yenbo sein wete. Tatame rem kemne yaper wos nenbo, kem remne God rekene tuma namrete.
42006029	Tame rem kemne op yokwo powyek puwburowte, kem pelkeren op yokwo powyek sene taite, rem sene puwburowte. Tame rem kemri tame oub potte wete, kem remne tame oub wuriwou kap newote. Kem remne pes newote.
42006030	Tame rem kemri wos bupo me potte wete, kem remne eger kap tete. Kem remne bupo me newote, yuri kem remne mane op wete. Ne nemne sein newote.
42006031	Kem selye, tatame rem kemne yenbo nente. Kem etop selbokap, kem agerbo tatame remne etopwou nente.
42006032	Tame rem yaper nenbo tame remne pap yewobo, yaper nenbo tame rem remne pap sein yewobo. Rem agerbo tame remne pap be yewobo. Kerem, kem aboyei tatame remne pap yewote. Kemne pap yewobo tame etemnewou kem pap yewote, God re kemne heyar be nente tetane.
