42017011	Jisas re Jerusalemke yibo kelowke yibem, re Samaria yokwo Galili yokwo borborke yim.
42017012	Re kwom wurik wurmenem, numa pe tame letpeis rem yan rene kelowke lam. Rem kaike teten
42017013	yaye op wem. Jisas, Haneyen, ne nemne pap mette.
42017014	Re remne lan op wem. Kem opu yi. Kem kemri wes God reri Kwoborke yaku nenbo tame remne yin peterate. Rem kelow yibem, remri wes heyar sene tem.
42017015	Etemri yen wuri re reri wes lan reri wes yenbo tem, re puboten sene yan re God reri sig bukre webem.
42017016	Re yan Jisas reri tewo tobok gulke pan rene wese am. Er tame re Juda tame bo. Re Samariari tame.
42017017	Jisas re rene lan op wem. Tame letpeis remri wes heyar teye. Letrane kelare eis kere tame rem mak yiwo?
42017018	Rem sene be yan God rene wese be aye. Samaria tame eterwou re sene yan God rene wese aye.
42017019	Jisas re rene op wem. Ne opu wayen yi. Ne anne omuteke haboye, eker ne heyar teye.
42017020	Farisi tame rem Jisas rene op wemetem. Makapke God re kwom panen site? Jisas re remne tuma sein op wem. God re kwom panen site, tatame rem lek be late.
42017021	Rem op be wete. Ekla. Re gwok tetane. O rem op be wete. Re kelarek tetane. Metye. God re keremri borborke kwom panen sim.
42017022	Sene Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem. Yuri kem habote, kem More Tame Tem Tame reri yabel wuri late habote. Kem be late.
42017023	Tatame rem kemne op wete. Ukla. Re etek tetane. O rem op wete. Ekla. Re gwok tetane. Op wetek, remri tuma kem kap meten mane sopen yite.
42017024	Pelale abo, nugwape emi tuwkap kerebokap, an More Tame Tem Tame, an yatek, an etopkap yate tetane. Nugwape tatame rem anne etop late tetane.
42017025	Kiyi an mus bukre mette. Gwopte tetane tatame rem anne magel taite.
42017026	Kiyi Noa re temenem yabel tatame remri nenbemkap, an More Tame Tem Tame, an sene yate yabel tatame rem etopkap nente tetane.
42017027	Noa re temenem yabel tatame rem nowselri woswou habobem. Rem awos abem, ta panebem, etopwou habobem. Rem God rene be habobem. Etop nenbem, sene Noa re sip bukre nenen etek temenem, rem etop som nenbem. Ok wayen kusyewom, nugwape tatame rem aboyei ok an saiwom.
42017028	Yuri Lot re temenem, rem etopwou nenbem. Rem awos abem, tokwo natokwo tupabem, rem now yaku nenbem, rem ake nenbem.
42017029	Op temke, Lot re Sodom kwom mesegenen yibem, kerkene pa nelke yeren tatame rem eter kerke ein ab saiwom.
42017030	An More Tame Tem Tame, an yan kwom geike tete yabel, tatame rem etopkap som nenbet tetane.
42017031	An yate yabel tame wuri re eterri ake magelke simente, reri wosbas ake purik temente, re kap wuren potte. Re yaper tete tetane. Tame re nowke temente, re akek sene kap yite. Re yaper tete tetane.
42017032	Kem Lot reri ta tene habote. Rem amen yibem, te teri wos potte sene pubotem, God re tene pen sam.
42017033	Tame rem etemri kworer wesomwou habote, rem yaper tete tetane. Tame rem etemri kworer wesomwou be habote, rem heyar som temente tetane.
42017034	An kemne webo. An More Tame Tem Tame an yatek, er neir tame pes rep tiy wurik tuknamente, wuri rene an panen yite, wuri an rene etek mesegente.
42017035	Ta pes rep awos etop nenbet, an yatek, wuri tene an panen yite, wuri tene an etek mesegente.
42017036	(Tame pes rep etop nowke temente, an yatek, wuri rene an panen yite, wuri rene an etek mesegente).
42017037	Jisas reri anepoi tame rem rene op wemetem. Haneyen, et wos et mak tete? Jisas re remne sikur sakur tuma op wem. Tame kupa rasbo emi kware rem yan wuriwouke sibo.
42018001	Jisas re habom, reri anepoi tame rem God rekene kwokwos kwokwos namrete, rem kap pwoite. Eker re remne sikur sakur tumak op wem.
42018002	Tuma met tame re kwom wurik temenem, re God rene be aken re nugwape tatame remne be habobem.
42018003	Wane ta wuri te kwom sag kirkir temenem. Kwokwos kwokwos te tuma met tame rene lasyibem, rene op webem. Tame rem anne tuma nenbo. Ne anne kwobo lan tuma nente.
42018004	Tuma met tame re tene kwobo late muwem. Yuri re eterri wuribaike op wem. An God rene be akbo. An tatame remne be habobo.
42018005	Wane ta te anne som wemetbet, wemetbet. Etopkap an muweye. Eker an tene tuma kwobo lan nente. An tene kwobo be late, te kwokwos kwokwos te yabet tetane, an tiselte tetane. Eker an muweye.
42018006	Haneyen re sene op wem. Er tuma met tame yaper reri tuma kem mette.
42018007	Eter nenemkap, God eterri kenem tatame rem rekene kwokwos kwokwos neirkene yabelkene som namrebet, God re remne kwobo be late? Re kap kowen agetage be kwobo late? Yehow.
42018008	An kemne webo. Re agetage remne kwobo late tetane. An More Tame Tem Tame, yuri an map late? Tatame rem kap anne omuteke habon God rekene tuma namrete, o rem omuteke be habon God rekene tuma be namrete?
42018009	Rane tame rem kworer yenbo habobem, rem agerbo tatame remne muwebem. Er tame remne Jisas re sikur sakur tuma op wem.
42018010	Tame pes rep God Reri Kwoborke wurem, rep God rekene tuma namrete. Wuri re Farisi tame, wuri re kel potbem tame.
42018011	Farisi tame re yin teten eterri wuribaike God rekene tuma namren op wem. God, setate. An agerbo tame etemkap bo. Rem bisi abo, rem tuma yikokobo, rem bisi yibo. An etemkap bo. An gwor kel potbo tame eterkap bo.
42018012	Sande wurik yabel pes an nene habobo, an awos pelebitebo. Nugwape wos an potbo, an letpeis pekarasen wuri an nene newobo.
42018013	Kel potbem tame re kaike teten selwouke lan reri merguw pen op wem. God, an yaper wos nenbo tame. Ne anne pap mette.
42018014	Jisas re anepoi tame remne op wem. An kemne webo. Kel potbem tame re reri akek sene yim, God re rene tame yenbo wem. Farisi tame reri yaper nenbo wos eterkene som tetane. Tame re reri sig kworer bukre wete, God re reri sig teitkwunte tetane. Tame re reri sig kworer teitkwunte, God re reri sig bukre wete tetane.
42018015	Tatame rem yen remne Jisas rene panen yam, rem geibile yen kirkir sen yam. Rem habom, Jisas re remne let keren God rene wemette, re remne heyar nente. Rem eker sen yam. Jisas eterri anepoi tame rem etop lan remne sewayem.
42018016	Jisas re yen remne wepoten meknik yan tem. Re anepoi tame remne op wem. Kem remne kap sewaite. Yike tatame rem yen etemkap tete, God rene omuteke habote, rem God eterri panen si kwomke yite. Eter yen rem hame ya.
42018017	An kemne sekeneker webo. Yen rem God reri panen sibo kwomke yibokap, kem etop be habote, kem God reri panen si kwomke wurte tetane.
42018018	Juda etemri keryen tame re yin Jisas rene op wemetem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne tame yenbo. Be wule an nentek, an heyar somsom temente?
42018019	Jisas re rene sein op wem. Berke ne anne yenbo weye? Gwor nowselri tatame rem yike yenbo be wuri tetane. God eterwou re yenbo.
42018020	Ne wule mettene. Wule re op webo. Ne agerbo tameri ta tene bisi mane yite. Ne alwo pi mane pete. Ne bisi mane ate. Ne tuma mane yikokote. Ne nawoha etepri tuma mette.
42018021	Op wemke, keryen tame re rene op wem. Kiyi an eisow yen ten yan gwopte an haneyen tem, an er wule heyar setene.
42018022	Jisas re er tuma metem, re rene sein op wem. Wos wuri ne be nentene. Neri nugwape wos agerbo tame hame tupate. Er potte tokwo ne wosbaskene bo tatame remne newon ne yan arenkene temente. Op nente, yuri ne God reri kwomke yin temente, ne wos yenbo potte tetane.
42018023	Tame re etop metem, re pap yaperwai tem. Bupo bokem. Reri nugwape wosbas tame rem tupate wemker re muwem. Eker Jisas reri wemkap re be nenem.
42018024	Jisas re etop lam, tame re pap yaper tem, re rene op wem. Woskene tame rem remri nugwape wosbas habobet, rem God reri panen si kwomke yite habobo, God re remne op webo. Kem yaku bukre keretek, kem ek yite.
42018025	Kamel por re mate lag taukke wurte wete, re wurlaweite. Etopkap, wosbaskene tame re God reri panen si kwomke yite habobo, re yaku bukrewai keretek, re ek yite.
42018026	Tatame rem reri tuma metem, rem op wem. Etopkap temente, yike tatame rem heyar somsom temente?
42018027	Jisas re sein op wem. Be wos tame rem kebese be nente, God eter re kebese nente tetane.
42018028	Pita re op wem. Metye. Nerem, nem nemri kwomkene woskene mesegenem, nem nerenkene anepoi tame yibo.
42018029	Jisas re op wem. Ekeya. An kemne sekeneker webo. Tame rem God reri yaku nente, rem remri ake, yenta, lakemase, nawoha remne mesegenen yaku nente.
42018030	Er tame gwopte God re remne heyar sein nente tetane. Yuri rem heyar som temente tetane. Jisas re op wem.
42018031	Jisas re letpeis tewo pes kere tame remne panen yin op wem. Kem met. Nem Jerusalemke yite. God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame rem nugwape tuma basrasem. More Tame Tem Tame rene basrasem tuma re gwotepte sekene teye.
42018032	Rem anne keikerete, sene agerbo tame rem Juda tame bo, rem anne potte. Rem anne tame wekeye makeyete, tuma yaper wete, sablokwo kwuspate.
42018033	Sene rem anne paku pete, anne pen sate. Yabel pes tetek, murwek an sene wayen site.
42018034	Reri anepoi tame rem tuma tobo be metem. Tuma tobo re me berasem, Jisas reri wem tuma rem wor tem.
42018035	Jisas re Jeriko kwom meknik yabem, le si tame re kelow kelarek simenem. Re tatame remne kel wos nasegerebem.
42018036	Re metem, nugwape tatame rem tuma kukwonen yabem, re rane remne op wemetem. Kem berke nenbo?
42018037	Rem rene sein op wem. Nasaret kwomri Jisas re yabo.
42018038	Re yaye op wem. Jisas, ne Devit eterri tame beig. Ne anne pap mette.
42018039	Kiyi temnam tame rem rene sewayen op wem. Ne elen me te. Op wemke, re sene yaye tem. Ne Devit eterri tame beig. Ne anne pap mette.
42018040	Jisas re yan teten remne op wem. Kem rene arenne panen yate. Rem rene panen yamke, Jisas re rene op wemetem.
42018041	Ne selye, an nene berke nente? Re sein op wem. Haneyen, an selye, an le sene heyar late.
42018042	Jisas re rene op wem. Neri le heyar tete. Ne anne omuteke habobo, an nene heyar nente. Eker ne heyar teye.
42018043	Reri wem tuma egegekene reri le yenbo tem, re welepe sene lam. Re Jisas rene semowen yibem, re God reri sig bukre webem. Tatame rem op lam, rem God reri sig bukre kirkir webem.
42019001	Jisas re Jeriko kwomke yin wurem, kwom mesegenen yibo kelowke re yite habom.
42019002	Tame wuri, reri sig Sakius, re Jerikoke temenem. Re kel potbem tame remri keryen yen. Re kel wurkene tame.
42019003	Sakius re Jisas rene late wem. Nugwape tatame rem etek temenem, Sakius re selkware tame, re Jisas rene kebese be lam.
42019004	Re kiyi temnan amen yin re yipige mek yawun sin op habom. Jisas re gwotre kelowke yate tetane.
42019005	Jisas re yan niruwen rene op wem. Sakius, ne agetage yer. Gwopte an neri akek yin tete.
42019006	Op wem, re agetage yeren Jisas rene panen eterri akek yim, re okbop bukre tem.
42019007	Nugwape tatame rem op lam, rem Jisas rene gwule ten op wem. Re wule yaper nenbo tame reri akek yibo, et yaper.
42019008	Sakius re teten Haneyen rene op wem. Haneyen, ne met. Gwopte an ari wos pekan giriy pes raste. Giri wuri an woskene bo tame remne newote. An tame remne yikokon remri wos bisik am, gwopte an remne wos tewo eis an sein newote.
42019009	Jisas re rene op wem. Gwopte gwor akek tetane tatame God re remne potye. Gwor tame eter mere, re Abraham eterri nan.
42019010	An More Tame Tem Tame, an yam, an yaper wos nenbo tatame remne sopen potte yam, remri yaper nenbo wos an poten septite yam.
42019011	Tatame rem metem, Jisas re Jerusalem meknik yan tem, tatame rem op webem. God re kwom panen site yabel matnaye. Remri wem tuma Jisas re metmenem, re tatame remne sikur sakur tuma eker wem.
42019012	Keryen yen wuri re kai kwomke yin remri keryen yen tete wem, re etek yin sene yate wem.
42019013	Yite nenbem, re reri yaku nen tame letpeis remne ten yam. Re remne tame wuri ok kel (K20) remne wulare wulare newon remne op wem. Kem gwor kel poten tokwo potbo yaku nenbet. An sene yate, an ari kel sene potte.
42019014	Reri kwom tame rem rene muwem, eker re yimke, rem rane tame remne werasen rene semowen kai kwomri tame remne op wem. Er tame nem rene muweye, re neremri kwom panen si tame kap tete.
42019015	Re kwom panen si tame tem, yuri re sene yam, kiyi kel newom yaku nen tame remne re ten yam, rem degerbokene mapsen potem, re remne etop wemetem.
42019016	Tame wuri re kiyi temnas yan re op wem. Haneyen, an neri newom tokwo, tame wuri ok kel (K20), poten tokwo pot yaku nenem, an sene degerbokene, 200 kel potem.
42019017	Re rene sein op wem. Ne yaku nen tame yenbo. Ne yaku yenbo nenem. Ne wos eisow heyar lakerem, opkap an nene yaku yenbo newote. Ne kwom sag letpeis lakerete.
42019018	Yuri tiptuwu yam tame re op wem. Haneyen, an neri tame wuri ok kel (K20) poten tokwo pot yaku nenem, sene an degerbokene kel, 100, an sene potem.
42019019	Etop wemke, re rene op wem. Ne kwom sag letrane lakerete.
42019020	Agerbo yaku nen tame re yan op wem. Haneyen, neri tame wuri ok kel (K20) an som setene. Er kel an mate megke peiken berasem.
42019021	An neri wule lam. Ne molkene tame. Agerbo tame remri wos ne ermetke yin potbo. Agerbo tamek awos nanekwobo, awos ne ermetke yin potbo. Opkap an nene akbo.
42019022	Haneyen re rene op wem. Ne yaku nen tame yaper. Ne lam, an molkene tame, agerbo tame remri wos an ermetke potbo. Awos agerbo tamek nanekwobo, an ermetke yin potbo. Ne etop lam, berke ne ari kel bupo me berasem?
42019023	Ari kel ne kel rasbo akek rasruwte wem, kel re sene nugwape tete wem. Etop nente wem, an sene yan kel degerbokene sene potte wem.
42019024	Op wemke, re meknik tetemenem tatame remne op wem. Kem eterri kel poten kel nugwape setene tame rene newote.
42019025	Rem rene op wem. Haneyen, re 200 kel poten tetane.
42019026	Re op wem. An kemne webo. Woskene tame o purerekene tame an rene kupakene sene newote tetane. Tame re be wos o be purere wuri be temente, reri temente eisow woskene o eisow purerekene an sene potte.
42019027	Ari peiktame, an kwom panen site muwem tame remne kem panen yan remne ari bitmik pen sate. Jisas re er sikur sakur tuma etop wem.
42019028	Re etop wen re Jerusalem kwomke yibem kelowke sene yim.
42019029	Jisas re Oliv Kwowke tetane kwom peske yam. Kwom pes et Betfagekene Betanikene. Re reri anepoi tame pes repne werasen temnas yim.
42019030	Re repne op wem. Kep er kwomke yin wurte, kep late, donki yen wuri etek tentene. Er donki tame rem eterri magel lu kiyi be sim, kep er donki kep sauken panen yate.
42019031	Op nente, tame re kepne op wemette. Kep berke donki yen kep saukbo? Op wemette, kep sein op wete. Haneyen re nesne werasye, nes donki eterne panen yite.
42019032	Rep yim, Jisas reri repne wem tuma sekene tem.
42019033	Rep donki yen kep saukbemke, donki yen mutame re repne op wemetem. Kep berke nente, kep donki yen kep eker saukbo?
42019034	Rep sein op wem. Haneyen re er donki yaku tetane, nes eker saukpotbo.
42019035	Rep donki yen Jisas rene panen yim. Repri wumenem tame oub lagu rep poten donki reri magel luke petamke, Jisas re ek yawun sim.
42019036	Re yibem, tatame rem remri wumenem tame oub lugen kelowke petan yimke, Jisas re eter luwke yim. Rem habom. Jisas re Keryen Yen. Eker rem etop nenem.
42019037	Re Jerusalem meknik yan tem, re Oliv Kwowke warbem kelow etek warbem. Reri nugwape anepoi tatame rem okbop tem. Jisas reri kiyi nenbem wos rem lam, rem God rene tuma yenbo yaye op wem.
42019038	God re reri werasen yam kwom panen si Keryen Yen rene heyar nente. God re tatame remne heyar nente. Nem God reri sig bukrewai webo.
42019039	Rane Farisi tame rem nugwape tatame etemkene temenem, rem Jisas rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne neri anepoi tatame remne sewaite. Rem elen me tete. Rem etopkap tuma kap wete.
42019040	Jisas re sein op wem. An kemne webo. Etem rem tuma ribo tete, pa etem rem yaye tete.
42019041	Re Jerusalem meknik yan temenem, re kwom lam, re kwom kiram.
42019042	Re op wem. Heyar site wule kem late, et yenbo. Gwopte me berastene, kem kebese be late.
42019043	Kem met. Yuri agerbo yabel tete, neri peiktame rem yan ei naite. Rem luw tayen yawun waren kwomri tatame remne lelete. Kem kebese be werate.
42019044	Rem yan ei naite, neri kwomke tetane tatame remne rem ab pekeipte tetane. Rem nereri ake aboyei berayewote tetane. Ake nenbem pa rem ab berayewon pete warte tetane. God re kemne potte yam, kem op be habom, eker kemri peiktame rem kemne etop nente tetane.
42019045	Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke yin wuren lam, tatame rem kel pot yaku etek nenbem. Re remne wekrokem.
42019046	Re remne op wem. Kiyi temenem tame rem God Reri Tuma op basrasem. Ari ake et arenkene tuma namrebo ake. Rem op basrasem, kem op be nenbo. Eterri akek kem kel potbo yaku nenbo, tatame remri kel ek potbo. Etop nenbo, eterri ake et bisi a tame etemri berasen sibo akekap.
42019047	Op wem, nugwape yabel re tatame remne God eterri Kwobor tuma wesowbem. God eterri Kwobor yaku nen tame etemri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame, Juda tatame remri keryen yen rem Jisas rene pen sate habom.
42019048	Nugwape tatame rem reri tuma mette habom, eker keryen tame rem rene pen sate kelow be wuri lam.
42020001	Agerbo yabel Jisas re God eterri Kwoborke wuren tatame remne God Reri Tuma Yenbo remne wesowbem, God eterri Kwoborke yaku nen tame etemri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame, Juda tatame remri keryen tame rem rene lasyam.
42020002	Rem rene op wem. Ne nemne wesowte. Nereri nenbo yaku, yike nene newom, ne er yaku nenbo? Yike nene kitimena newom?
42020003	Re remne sein op wem. An kemne tuma wuri wemette. Kem anne wesowte.
42020004	Jon re yam, re tatame remne okke panen waren tirmunem. Yike rene er yaku werasem? God re rene werasem o tame rem rene werasem? Kem anne wesowte.
42020005	Rem etemwou etemwou namren op wem. Nem map wete? Nem kap op wete. God re rene werasem. Nem op wetek, re nemne sein op wete. Mapurke kem Jon reri tuma be habom?
42020006	Nem kap op wete. Tame rem rene werasem. Nem op wetek, gwotek tetane tatame nugwape rem pa poten nemne seite tetane. Tatame rem op webo. Jon re God eterri tuma wesowbem tame. Opkap, rem pa poten nemne seite tetane.
42020007	Etemwou etemwou namremke, rem Jisas rene tuma sein op wem. Nem be mettene, yike rene werasen yam.
42020008	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem anne be wesowye, aren mere, an kemne be wesowte, yike anne werasen yam.
42020009	Jisas re sikur sakur tuma tatame remne op wem. Tame wuri re wain now nenem. Re er now re rane yaku nen tame etemri letke rasen rem kel yaku nente. Op nenemke, re gene kwom wurik yin nugwape yabel re etek temenem.
42020010	Wain supa okwomenem, now mutame re reri yaku nen tame wuri werasen now yaku lakerebem tame remne lasyim. Re now mutame reri wain supa potte yim. Now lakerebem tame rem rene paku pen rene werasen bupo sene yim, re wain supa be sen yim.
42020011	Sene now mutame re agerbo yaku nen tame werasen yim, rem rene paku pen werasen re bupo me sene yim, re wain supa be sen yim.
42020012	Tewo murwe re yaku nen tame rene werasen yim. Rem rene pen rene rem botkun kwom geike septi wurem.
42020013	Now mutame re op wem. An mapurke nente? Ari yen sekene, yen yenbo, an rene werasen yite. Rem kap reri tuma mette tetane.
42020014	Now yaku lakerebem tame rem yen rene lam, rem etemwou etemwou op wem. Now mutame reri yen sekene re yabo. Yuri yener re ha reri wos potte tetane. Nem rene pen satek, gwor now nem potte.
42020015	Rem yen rene keikeren now kwopok yokwo liyten wuren rene etek pen sam. Jisas re sikur sakur tuma wekeipem, re tatame remne op wemetem. Now mutame re now yaku lakerebem tame remne mapurke nente?
42020016	Re yin now yaku nen tame remne pen sate wem, re agerbo tame remne er yaku newote tetane. Tame rem op metem, rem op wem. Re etop mane nente.
42020017	Jisas re remne lan op wem. Ari weye tuma et sekene. Kiyi temenem tame rem God Reri Tuma etop basrasem. Rem op basrasem. Tame rem seg wuri habom, et seg yaper, rem poten septim. Er seg et nawo seg tem, et seg yenbosubuwai. (Buk Song 118:22)
42020018	Aboyei tame rem ari weye segke rene waren ragerte, er tame remri wesom yaper tete tetane. Er seg tame wuri ragerte, tame re sate tetane.
42020019	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame etem, God reri yaku nen tame etemri keryen yen rem Jisas reri wem sikur sakur tuma metem, rem op habom. Jisas re nemne weye. Op habomke, rem rene eipye keikerete wem. Rem nugwape tatame remne lam, rem remne akem, rem rene be keikerem.
42020020	Rem rene pelebiten rem rene leklek tem. Rem habom. Nem Jisas rene tuma wuri wemette, re tuma yaper sein wete o bo? Re tuma yaper sein wete, nem rene keikeren Romri keryen yen rene panen yin rene tuma nente. Op habom, eker rem yikoko tame remne tupan remne werasen Jisas rene tuma wemette yim.
42020021	Rem Jisas rene op wemetem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, nem mettene. Neri webo tuma et yenbo, et tuma sekene. Tatame remri webo tuma ne be habobo. God Reri Tuma yenbo, reri tuma sekene ne wesowbo.
42020022	Ne map habobo? Nem Keryen Yen Sisar rene kel newote o bo?
42020023	Remri yikokom tuma Jisas re sanem, re remne op wem.
42020024	Kem anne kel wuri peterate. Rem rene peteramke, re remne op wemetem. Gwor kel et basrastene sigkene wowkene, et yikeri? Rem op wem. Et Sisar eterri.
42020025	Jisas re op wem. Sisar eterri wos kem eterne newote. God reri wos kem God eterne newote.
42020026	Op wemke, re tuma yenbo tatame remri bitmik wem, rem danekene seken tuma ribo tem, rem rene be keikerem.
42020027	Sadyusi tame rem op webem. Sabo tame rem sene be wayen site. Opkap remri rane tame rem yan Jisas rene op wemetem.
42020028	Tuma Peikbo Tame, warege Moses re tuma basrasen nemne op wem. Masetebo yen re ta panete, yuri re sate, re yenkene bo, reri mase re sene reri wane tene panen tekene yen sete. Er yen et laker eterri yen. Moses re etop basrasem.
42020029	Kiyi letrane kelare pes kere lakemase rem temenem, masetebo yen re ta panem, rep yenkene bo, re bupo me sam.
42020030	Mase re wane tene panem, rep yenkene bo, re bupo me sam.
42020031	Bor tame re etopwou nenem. Masem rem etopwou etopwou nenem. Rem wane etetnewou panebem, rem yenkene bo, rem bupo me sakeipem.
42020032	Yuri ta te etet mere sam.
42020033	Kem webo. Yuri sabo tame rem sene wayen site tetane. Kiyi aboyei lakemase letrane kelare pes kerem tame rem ta tene panem. Yuri yike sekene teri tame tete.
42020034	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Gwopte tetane tatame rem narpanebo.
42020035	God re remne yenbo wete tatame yuri rem sene wayen God reri kwom yenbok yin temente, rem be narpanete tetane.
42020036	Rem God eterri kwomri tamekap temente. Rem be sate, rem som temente. God re remne wetek, rem sene wayen site, God re remne eterri yen wete.
42020037	Sabo tatame rem sene wayen site tetane, Moses re nemne kiyi etop peteram. Kiyi Moses re kerke eibem me eisow meknik yin tetemenem, God re rene op wem. An yeiwarege Abraham, Aisak, Jekop etemri Keryen Yen God.
42020038	Opkap God re nemne peteram, kiyi sam tatame re etemri God bo. Yehow. Re kelpe tetane tatame etemri God. Reri tatame rem kelpe som tetane.
42020039	Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem tuma sein op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne sein tuma yenbo weye.
42020040	Rene sene wemette rem me akem.
42020041	Jisas re tatame remne op wemetem. Moses Reri Wule peikbo tame rem op webo. Krais re Devit reri tame beig. Mapurke rem op webo?
42020042	Devit re Buk Song basrasen op wem. Keryen Yen God re ari Keryen Yen rene op wem. Ne haneyen, ne areri let mame yokwok site.
42020043	Yuri an wete, ne neri peiktame remne teitkwunen ne remne kwom panen site tetane. (Buk Song 110:1)
42020044	Kem late. Devit re Krais rene Keryen Yen wem. Mapurke er tame re Devit reri beig tem? Jisas re op wem.
42020045	Tatame rem etek som temenem, rem Jisas reri tuma metbem. Jisas re reri anepoi tame remne op wem.
42020046	Wule peikbo tame remri nenbokap kem etop lan kap nente. Rem selbo, tatame rem remne late, eker rem tame oub laguna wun sewurbo. Rem kwom geike sewurbek, rem selbo, tatame rem remne pir wen remne tame yenbo wete. Rem God eterri akek wurbo, rem selbo, rem keryen yen etemri wolbayeke site. Rem awos bukre abo, rem selbo, rem keryen yen etemri wolbayeke sin awos ate.
42020047	Rem wane ta remne yikokon remri wos bisik potbo. Sene rem God reri akek wurbo, rem rekene tuma nugwape namrebo. Op nenbo, rem op habobo. Tatame rem nemne yenbo wete. Opkap rem nenbo, yuri God re remne yaperwai sein nente tetan, rem mus bukre mette.
42021001	Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke temenem, re lam, kelkene tatame rem kel sen yan kel yewobo ouke yewobem.
42021002	Re lam, kelkene bo wane ta te kel eisow pes ouke yeworuwye.
42021003	Re etop lam, re op wem. An kemne sekeneker webo. Kelkene tatame rem kel nugwape yewoye. Kelkene bo wane ta te kel eisowwou pes yewoye. Teri yewoye kel et nugwape tatame remri kel teitkwunye.
42021004	Nugwape kel tetane tatame rem kel ranewou God rene newoye, nugwape kel rem som keikeretene. Et ta te kel nugwape bo, teri kel te aboyei newoye. Teri awos tupabo kel te newokeipye. Jisas re op wem.
42021005	Jisas reri anepoi tame rane rem God Reri Kwoborke tuma namren op wem. Gwor ake nem le kwuye labo. Rem pa yenbok nenem. Tatame rem God rene newom wos nem kirkir labo, et yenbo wos. Jisas re op wem. Gwor ake rem nenem, rem pa poten tiren yawem.
42021006	Gwor wos gwopte kem labo, et yenbo. Yuri er pa rem agerbo pa luwke sene be tete tetane. Rem aboyei beran repkan pete warte tetane. Jisas re op wem.
42021007	Re op wemke, rem rene op wemetem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne weye, rem God Reri Kwobor berate. Be yabelke rem etop nente? Be wos nem kiyi lan sanete, rem eipye berate?
42021008	Jisas re op wem. Kem heyar la. Rem kemne kap yikokote. Nugwape tame rem yate tetane, rem ari sig wete tetane. Rem yikokon op wete. Aren, an Krais, God eter lebam tame. Rane rem sene op wete tetane. Yabel matnaye. Op wete. Remri tuma kem kap meten remne kap semowte.
42021009	Yuri kem mette, kwom wuriri tatame rem agerbo kwomri tamekene ei bukre naite tetane, sene kem mette, kwom wuriri tatame rem etemwou etemwou naite tetane. Kem etop mette, kem mane akte. Et nowsel yaper tete yabel bo. Nowsel yaper tete yabel re yuri tete tetane.
42021010	Re remne sene op wem. Kwom wuriri tame rem agerbo kwomri tamekene ei naite tetane, keryen yen wuri reri sukuw rem agerbo keryen yen reri sukuwkene naite tetane.
42021011	Nina bukre yate tetane, agerbo agerbo kwomri tatame rem a kwoi site tetane. Nugwape tatame rem agerbo agerbo sikanuma nente tetane. Nelke agerbo bukre wos yaper kem late tetane.
42021012	Ari weye wos et yuri tete tetane. Kiyi rem kemne keikeren kemne yaper nente tetane. Rem kemne etemri tuma wen akek panen yite tetane, kemne ake yaperke wen wurte tetane. Kem ari yaku nenbet, eker rem kemne kwom panen si keryen yen rene panen yin kemne tuma nente tetane.
42021013	Tuma nente, kem ari tuma yenbo remne wesowte.
42021014	Yuri rem kemne tuma nente. Gwopte kem yuri sene wete tuma kap habote.
42021015	Yuri an kemri sein wete tuma yenbo kemne wesowte, kemne purere yenbo newote. Ari kemne wete tuma kemri peiktame rem be nasweyen teitkwunte tetane.
42021016	Nawoha, lakemase, hayei, mem wopu, tametiy rem kemne peiktame remne wesowte tetane. Peiktame rem keremri rane tame remne pen sate tetane.
42021017	Kem anne omuteke habote, opkap nugwape tame rem kemne gwule tete.
42021018	Kem mane habote. God re kemne lakerete tetane.
42021019	Kem yaku heyar sete, kem kap mesegente. Kem etop nentek, kem heyar som temente tetane. Jisas re op wem.
42021020	Yuri kem late, ei nai tame rem Jerusalem kwomke yan wekuraste tetane. Kem op late, kem sanete, rem kwom ake ab berayewote yabel matnaye.
42021021	Er yabel kem Judiak tetane tatame, kem kwowke sene amen yin tete. Jerusalemke tetane tatame rem kwom mesegenen yite. Tatame rem nowke temente, rem kwom sene kap wurte.
42021022	Er yabel, God re tatame remne pete tetane. God eterri kiyi siglowke basrasmenem tuma re sekene tete tetane.
42021023	Er yabel an yenkene ta, yen muk newon abo ta remne pap metbo. Rem kebese agetage be amete, eker an remne pap metbo. God re selke tetane tatame remne gwule tete, rem nugwape mus bukre mette tetane.
42021024	Agerbo nowselri tame rem rane remne pik pen sate tetane. Rane rem remne keikeren panen yin agerbo nowselke yin tete tetane. Agerbo nowselri tatame rem Jerusalem kwom panen site tetane. Yuri God re op wete. Et yow. Rem kwom sene be panen site. Op wete, rem kwom sene mesegenen yite.
42021025	Er yabel agerbo agerbo wos tete tetane, liyp, yabel, sowkene tete tetane. Tatame rem kenakem akte tetane. Rem kersepkap ok burow bukrekene ken meten lan rem ek akte tetane.
42021026	Nugwape tatame rem agerbo wos selke yate habote, rem kenakem akte. Kitimenakene nelri wos rem nignigen kena kena yite tetane, eker rem kenakem akte.
42021027	Opkap tete, rem late, an More Tame Tem Tame, an nel gwanke sene yate tetane. An kitimena bukrekene yate, an hadebaswaikene yate.
42021028	Yuri ari weye wos tetek, kem mette. God re kemne potte yabel matnaye. Kem teten nelke niruwte. Jisas re op wem.
42021029	Jisas re remne sikur sakur tumak op wem. Kem guwb metka habote.
42021030	Guwb metka rem walku yerbo, kem op webo. Nabe berabo.
42021031	Eker ari kemne kiyi weye tuma et etopkap. Ari weye tumakap etop tete, kem etop sene habote. God re kwom panen site nenbo.
42021032	An kemne sekeneker webo. Gwopte tetane tatame rem be samentek, ari weye wos rem ek late tetane.
42021033	Nelkene selkene rep legete tetane. Ari tumawou re som temente tetane.
42021034	Kem heyar la. Kem ok yaper sou mane an sisi kap pete. Kem nowselri wos mane habote. Kem er woswou nenbet, ari yate yabel et agetage yate tetane.
42021035	Man et portob omap remne potbokap, ari yate yabel aboyei nowselri tatame rem aboyei late tetane.
42021036	Kwokwos kwokwos kem heyar late, God rekene tuma namrete, re kemne kitimena newote. Ari weye wos tete, kem kebese sete. An More Tame Tem Tame, yuri an yate, kem areri bitmik heyar tetete.
42021037	Nugwape yabel Jisas re tatame remne God Reri Kwoborke tuma peikbem. Yabel waren neir tektebem, re Oliv Kwowke yawun etek tuknabem.
42021038	Ei berekwunem, re sene yerem, nugwape tatame rem God Eterri Kwoborke reri tuma mette wurkwutem.
42022001	Awos ate yabel tete nenbem. Awos ate yabelri sig et Yiskene Bo Geil Abo Yabel. Agerbo sig et God Re Israel Remne Isip Remri Letke Sene Poten Habom Yabel. Er yabel Juda tame rem yiskene bo geil abem.
42022002	Er yabel God Reri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem tatame remne akem, rem Jisas rene pen sate kelow sopem.
42022003	Jisas reri anepoi tame letpeis tewo pes kerem etemri tame wuri re Judas. Reri agerbo sig Iskariot. Satan re rene gurerem.
42022004	Re yin God Eterri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen, God Eterri Kwobor lakere tame remri keryen tame remkene namrem. Re Jisas rene, remne newote kelow sopen tuma teiktem.
42022005	Rem okbop tem, rem rene kel newote wem.
42022006	Judas re kirkir wem, re yin Jisas rene keikerete kelow sopte yim. Re habom. Nugwape tatame rem Jisas eterkene be temente, aren etop nente, re et kowmenem.
42022007	Yiskene Bo Geil Abem yabel tem. Et yabel tame rem sipsip yen pen God Re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tatame Remri Letke Sene Potem yabel habon awos abem.
42022008	Rem op habobem. Kiyi God re nemri yeiwarege remne be pem, re remne heyar nenem. Op habobem, eker rem et awos abem. Er yabel Jisas re Pitakene Jonkene repne werasen yin op wem. Kep er awos yin nerete, nem yin ate.
42022009	Rep rene op wem. Nes mak nerete?
42022010	Re repne op wem. Metye. Kem kwom sagke yin wuren kep tame wuri late, re okkene ou semente. Kep eterne semowte. Eter wurte ake kep kirkir etek wurte.
42022011	Kep ake mutame rene op wete. Tuma Peikbo Tame re nene wemetbo. Awos ate emi ma? An ari anepoi tamekene nem God Re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tatame Remri Letke Sene Potem habon awos ate.
42022012	Op wetek, re kepne ake puri bukre, ya yokwok tetane ake puri, kepne peterate. Tiykene wolbayekene etek temente. Kep awos etek nerete.
42022013	Op wemke, rep yin Jisas re wemkap, rep etop lam, rep awos etek nerem.
42022014	Awos ate yabel tem, Jisas re awos ate yin sim. Reri anepoi tame rem eterkene kirkir yin sim.
42022015	Re remne op wem. An God Re Israel Remne Isip Etermri Letke Sene Potem Yabelri awos keremkene a pap teye. Nem kiyi ate, yuri an mus bukre ek mette tetane.
42022016	An kemne webo. An God Re Israel Remne Isip Etemri Letke Sene Potem Yababelri wos sene be ate. Yuri God re kwom panen sitek, awos reri wuleri tobo re tegek tete, an sene ek ate.
42022017	Op wemke, Jisas re ok ware wuri poten God rene wese an remne op wem. Kem aboyei, kem gwor ok poten ate.
42022018	An kemne webo. Wain ok, an nowselke temente, an sene be ate. Yuri an Apiy reri panen si kwom etek temente, an sene ek ate tetane.
42022019	Op wemke, re geil poten God rene wese an belokteyewon remne newopiti pete yan op wem. Gwor areri om, an kemne newobo. Kem atek, kem anne habote. Jisas re op wem.
42022020	Akeipen sene re ok ware wuri poten op wem. Gwor wain ok et areri nep. Rem anne pen sate, ari nep yerte. Et kemne peteran mukuwtekte, God re keremkene agerbo tuma natebote, re keremri yaper nenbo wos poten septite.
42022021	Metye. Anne yena tete tame re arenkene sin awos etep abo.
42022022	An More Tame Tem Tame, an God eterri wemkap sate tetane. Anne yena tete tame re mus bukre mette tetane.
42022023	Op wemke, rem etemwou etemwou op wem. Yike opkap nente?
42022024	Anepoi tame rem tuma nauran op wem. Yike nemri keryen yen tete?
42022025	Jisas re remne op wem. Agerbo kwomri keryen yen rem tatame remne kwom panen sibo, tatame rem remne op webo. Rem nemne heyar nenbo tamekap.
42022026	Keremri tame wuri re op wete. Gwopte an haneyen tete. An rene op wete. Ne eisow yenkap tete, yuri ne haneyen tete. Ne agerbo tatame remne yaku nentek, ne keryen yen ek tete.
42022027	Yike re keryen yen? Kap awos sin abo tame eter, o awos sen yan newobo tame eter? Nowselri tatame rem op webo. Awos sin abo tame, eter re keryen yen. Aren, an kemne webo. Agerbo tatame remne awos yaku nenbo, eter re keryen tame. An keremkene tetane, an awos sen yan newobo tamekap, an yaku nenen kemne kwobo labo.
42022028	Tatame rem anne seilan anne yaper wos nenem, kem arenkene som temenem, kem anne be mesegenem.
42022029	Ari Apiy re anne wem, eker an kwom panen sibo. Opkap an kemne webo, kem tatame remne kwom panen site.
42022030	An kwom panen site yabel kem arenkene sin awoskene okkene ate. Kem keryen yen etemri wolbayek sin Israel tatame remri tame beig letpeis tewo pes kere etemri tuma mette, remne se pete.
42022031	Jisas re op wem. Saimon, ne met. Satan re God rene wemetem, re kemne seilate. Kem anne omuteke som habote o bo? Tame rem wit supa poten segegin supa kena rasbo, sagw septibokap, Satan re kemne etopkap nente tetane.
42022032	Saimon, an God rekene tuma namreye, re nene kwobo late, ne anne omuteke som habote. Ne wule yaper nentek, sene ne wuribai yenbo potte, ne neri lakemase remne kwobo late.
42022033	Pita re rene op wem. Haneyen, an nerenkene ake yaperke kirkir yite. An nerenkene kirkir sate.
42022034	Jisas re sein op wem. Pita, an nene webo. Gwopte neir kwokwo be wementek, tewo mur ne ari sig berasen op wete tetane. An Jisas rene be latene.
42022035	Jisas re anepoi tame remne op wem. Kiyi an kemne werasen yim, kem kel yewobem bus, letke sebem ayer, tewo bus kem be sen yim. Er yabel kem wos merinem? Rem sein op wem. Yehow.
42022036	Re remne op wem. Gwopte tame re kel yewobo bus tetane, o ayer tetane, re poten sete. Tame re akiy bo, re reri tame oub poten tamekene natokwo tupate, re kel poten akiy yin tupate.
42022037	An kemne webo. God reri siglowke rem op basrasem. Tatame rem op wete. Re tame yaper etemri wuri. An kemne webo. God reri siglow re be tuma webo, er tuma re sekene tete nenbo. Kiyi basrasem tuma re sekene tete nenbo.
42022038	Anepoi tame rem rene op wem. Haneyen, ekla. Akiy pes gwor. Re remne op wem. Yow. Ari tuma te ab eteke.
42022039	Jisas re kwom mesegenen yim, re kwokwos kwokwos nenbemkap, re etop sene nenem, re Oliv Kwowke yawum. Reri anepoi tame rem eterkene kirkir yim.
42022040	Yin rem er emik potem, re remne op wem. Kem God rekene tuma namren rene op wemette. Satan re kemne kap keikerete.
42022041	Op wen re remne mesegenen opre yim. Re gulke pan God rekene tuma namrem.
42022042	Apiy, an selbo, anne yaper nente wos et anne be yate, an mus bukre be mette. Et nereri wos. Ari selbokap ne kap nente. Neri selbokap, ne etopwou nente.
42022043	God reri kwomri tame wuri re God eterri kwom mesegenen rene kitimena newom.
42022044	Jisas re pap yaperwai metbem, re God rene som wemetbem, reri kermuskene nepkene yan selke bitibem.
42022045	Re sene wayen yin lam, reri anepoi tame rem pap yaper temenem, rem tuknamenem.
42022046	Re remne teren op wemetem. Kem berke tuknatene? Kem wayen sin God rekene tuma namrete. Satan re kemne sailate nenbo. Kem kap warte.
42022047	Jisas re som webemke, nugwape tame rem ek yam. Jisas reri letpeis tewo pes kere anepoi tame remri wuri, Judas, re temnas yan Jisas rene meknik yan teten rene ragiy boite.
42022048	Ragiy boite nenem, Jisas re rene op wem. Judas, an More Tame Tem Tame, ne anne ragiy boyen ne anne peiktame etemri letke raste.
42022049	Anepoi tame rem Jisas rekene temenem, rem lam, rem rene keikerete nenem, rem rene op wemetem. Haneyen, ne map habobo? Nem remne pete?
42022050	Jisas reri anepoi tame wuri re arep potem. Re God Eterri Kwoborke yaku nenbem tame etemri keryen yen reri yaku nen tame reri mame yokwo wan arepke boken yersiyam.
42022051	Jisas re op wem. Yow. Ne mesegente. Op temke, re er tame reri wan bokem yokwo let kerem, reri wan heyar sene tem.
42022052	Jisas rene keikerete yam tame rem God Eterri Kwoborke yaku nen tame etemri keryen yen, Kwobor lakere tame remri taresi tame, Juda etemri keryen. Jisas re remne op wem. Kem anne keikerete yawo, kem bisi a tame rene pottekap yawo. Kem arep, wer pakukene setene. An bisi a tame bo.
42022053	Aboyei yabel an keremkene nem God Eterri Kwoborke temenem, kem anne etek be keikerem. Gwopte yabel et keremri yabel. Kem wule yaper nente.
42022054	Re op wemke, rem rene keikeren rene God Eterri Kwoborri keryen yen reri akek panen wurem. Pita re tiptuwu semowen yim.
42022055	Tame rem ker ake makele borborke lisen simenem, Pita re kirkir etek yin simenem.
42022056	Yaku nen ta wuri te rene lam, te rene sene heyar lan op wem. Er tame re Jisas eterkene sewurbem tame.
42022057	Pita re op wem. Aren bo. An rene be latene.
42022058	Yuri sene agerbo tame re rene lan op wem. Neren mere, ne etemri tame wuri. Pita re op wem. Yehow. An bo.
42022059	Kerakap tem, agerbo tame re me gwungwunen op wem. Er tame re Galili tame. Re Jisas eterri anepoi tame etemri wuri.
42022060	Pita re op wem. Yehow. Neri webo tuma an be mettene. Op webemke, agetage kwokwo ek wem.
42022061	Jisas re Pita rene petkwo lamke, Pita re Jisas reri kiyi wem tuma sene ek habopitim. Kiyi re rene op wem. Gwopte neir kwokwo be wementek, tewo mur ne ari sig berasen op wete tetane. An Jisas rene be latene.
42022062	Pita re sebera yan re kwom geike wuren kenakem kiram.
42022063	Jisas rene lakerebem tame rem rene sak keyen rene paku pebem.
42022064	Rem reri le matek subkeren rene op wemetem. Ne nemne wesowte. Yike nene pebo?
42022065	Op wem, rem rene agerbo agerbo tuma yaper sene webem.
42022066	Ei beram, Juda keryen tame, God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame rem wuriwowke wurem, rem Jisas rene panen yan Juda Saberawiykene Tame remri bitmik teten rem rene tuma nente nenem.
42022067	Rem op wem. Ne nemne wesowte. God re nene lebam? Re sein op wem. An kemne wesowte, kem be habote tetane.
42022068	An kemne tuma wemetek, kem anne sein be wete tetane.
42022069	Gwopte yabelkene yuri tete yabelkene An More Tame Tem Tame an kitimenakene God eterri let mame yokwok site tetane.
42022070	Op wemke, aboyei tame rem op wemetem. Ne God Eterri Yen o bo? Re sein op wem. Kem kebese weye. An God Eterri Yen.
42022071	Rem op wem. Nem agerbo tame remne be wemette, rem yan gwor tame reri wule wesowte. Reri weye tuma sekene, nem etop metye.
42023001	Keryen tame rem aboyei tetyewon Jisas rene Pailat rene panen yim.
42023002	Rem rene tuma nenen op wem. Nem lam, gwor tame re nemri tatame remne purere yaper newom. Re Romri Keryen Yen, Sisar, rene kel newote weragerem. Sene re op webem. An Juda tatame etemri keryen yen. An Krais, God eter lebam tame. An God reri tatame remne potte.
42023003	Pailat re Jisas rene op wemetem. Ne Juda etemri kwom panen si keryen yen o bo? Re sein op wem. Ekeya. Neren ne etop weye.
42023004	Pailat re God Eterri Kwoborri yaku nen tame remri keryen yenkene nugwape tatamekene remne op wem. Gwor tame re yaper be nenem.
42023005	Rem tuma me gwungwunen op wem. Re Judia yokwori tatame remne tuma wesowen sewurbem. Re Galili yokwok tobotan yin sene gwotek yan tatame remne tuma peiken remri wuribai lisokobem.
42023006	Pailat re remri tuma metem, re remne op wemetem. Er tame re Galili tame?
42023007	Rem op wem. Ekeya. Pailat re op metem, Jisas re Keryen Yen Herot reri yokwori tame, etopkap re Jisas rene werasem, Herot re rene tuma nente. Er yabel Herot eter re Jerusalemke temenem.
42023008	Herot re Jisas rene lam, re okbopsubuwai tem. Kiyi re Jisas reri nenbemkap metem, re rene late wem, Jisas re nente bukre wos late wem.
42023009	Herot re rene nugwape tuma wemetem, Jisas re rene sein be wem.
42023010	God Eterri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen etem, Moses Reri Wule peikbem tame etem, rem teten rene nugwape tuma nenem.
42023011	Herot, eterri ei nai tamekene rem rene wekwuye makwuyen rem rene tuma yaper wem. Rem tame oub yenbosubuwai poten rene wuruwen rene werasen Pailat rene sene lasyim.
42023012	Kiyi Herot re Pailat rekene peiktame temenem, er yabel rep kelmenam, rep tametiy tem.
42023013	God Eterri Kwoborke yaku nen tame remri keryen yen etemne, Juda etemri keryen yen etemne, tatame etemne Pailat re remne wen yan wuriwowke wurem.
42023014	Re remne op wem. Kem er tame rene panen anne lasyawo. Kem op weye. Re tatame remne purere yaper newom. An rene keremri bitmik tuma wuri wemetweiwo. Kerem rene weye tuma an be wuri laye.
42023015	Herot eter mere, re reri gwule be wuri laye, re rene werasen nemne sene lasyawo. Kem met. Er tame re be wos be wuri nenem, nem rene kap pen sate. Et yaper.
42023016	Opkap an rene pakuwou pen mesegenen yite.
42023017	(Nabek nabek God re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tatame Remri Letke Poten Habom Yabel, Pailat re ake yaperke temenem tame wuri werasen akwulke sene yibem. Et etemri wule, rem etop nenbem.)
42023018	Pailat re rene weraste wem, nugwape tatame rem yaye ten op wem. Jisas rene pen sate. Barabas eterne werasen sene akwulke yite. Rem op wem.
42023019	Kiyi Barabas re nugwape tamekene rem kwom panen si tame etemkene kwom sagke ei nayem, re tame wuri pen sam. Eker rem rene ake yaperke wen wurem.
42023020	Pailat re remne sene op wem. An Jisas rene sene werasen yite.
42023021	Rem op wem. Yehow. Rene mek kwuren peikkerete. Rene mek kwuren peikkerete.
42023022	Op wemke, Pailat re tewo murwe remne sene op wemetem. Gwor tame re be yaper wos nenem? An reri gwule be wuri laye, nem rene kap pen sate. Opkap an rene pakuwou pen sene werasen yite.
42023023	Tatame rem yaye som op tebem. Rene me kwuren peikkerete. Remri taye Pailat reri tuma teitkwunbem.
42023024	Pailat re Jisas rene mek kwuren peikkerete kirkir tem.
42023025	Pailat re tatame remri wem tame, Barabas, rene werasen sene akwulke yim. Er tame re kiyi kwom panen si tame etemkene ei nayem, re tame wuri pen sam, rem rene ake yaperke eker wen wurem. Pailat re rene werasen sene yim, re Jisas rene poten tatame remne newon op wem. Kem keremri wuribaike rene nente.
42023026	Ei nai tame rem Jisas rene panen yibem, rem lam, Sairini tame wuri, reri sig Saimon, re yan kwom sagke wurte yabem. Rem rene keikeren me eterri gwarek towruwen sen re Jisas rene semowem.
42023027	Nugwape tatame rem rene semowem, ta rem rene kiran yabem, rem rene simarkwun yabem.
42023028	Jisas re remne petkwo lan remne op wem. Jerusalemri ta, kem anne mane kirate. Kem kerem kworer kirate, keremri yen etemne kirate. Yuri tatame rem remne yaper nente tetane.
42023029	Metye. Yuri agerbo yabel tete, tatame rem op wete. Yen game a ta, yenkene bo ta, yen muk be newobo ta rem okbop tete.
42023030	Et yabel tatame rem mus bukre mette, rem kwow bukre rene op wete. Ne nemne ragerkerete. Rem eisow kwow remne op wete. Kem nemne ragerkerete. Op wete tetane.
42023031	Gwopte rem er okkene me rene opkap wule nente, rem mapkap wule me sauk me nente?
42023032	Nause yen rem agerbo tame pes etepne mere panen yim. Rep bisi abem tame. Rem repne Jisas eterkene pen sate wem.
42023033	Rem kwow eisowke yan yawum. Kwow sig Tame Tare Bai. Kwowke yawun rem rene mek kwuren peikkerem. Rem bisi abem tame pes etepne mere etek kirkir mek kwuren peikkerem. Rem tame wuri rene Jisas reri let mame yokwok teteruwem, tame wuri rene rem let giriy yokwok teteruwem.
42023034	Jisas re op wem. Apiy, ne remri yaper nenbo wos poten septite. Remri nenbo wos rem be sanetene. Op wem, Romri nause yen rem etemwou etemwou satu barow tem, rem reri tame oub wusam.
42023035	Tatame rem teten leklek temenemke, Juda etemri keryen yen rem Jisas rene wekwuye makwuyen op wem. Kiyi re agerbo tatame remne kwobo labem. Re wem, re God eter lebam tame. Et sekene wete, re eter kworer kwobo late.
42023036	Nause yen etem mere, rem rene wekwuye makwuyem. Rem yan meknik teten rene kwole ya ok newote op wem.
42023037	Ne Juda etemri kwom panen si keryen yen, ne neren kworer kwobo late.
42023038	Basrasem tuma wuri rem reri tare ya yokwo etek peikkerem. Rem op basrasem. GWOR TAME RE JUDA TATAME ETEMRI KERYEN YEN.
42023039	Bisi abem tame wuri re Jisas rene tuma yaper op wem. Ne wem, ne Krais, God eter lebam tame. Etopkap ne neren kworer kwobo late, nesne kirkir kwobo late.
42023040	Agerbo bisi a tame re rene tuma sein op wem. Ne God rene be akbo. Rem nemne murmur pen sate weye.
42023041	Kiyi nes yaper wos nenem, sene nes mus metbo, et yenbo. Gwor tame re be gwule be wuri nenem, re mus bupo metbo.
42023042	Re Jisas rene op wem. Jisas, yuri ne kwom panen site sene yatek, ne anne habote.
42023043	Jisas re rene op wem. An nene sekeneker webo. Gwopte ne arenkene kwom yenbok tete tetane.
42023044	Yabel nina let kere temenem, yabel sene be pasem, nowsel neir tektekwunen sene yabel warbemke, yabel sene ek pasem.
42023045	Yabel sene pasem, mate bukre, God Eterri Kwobor eismenem mate, re ya yokwok pekan yeren kelare kelare tem.
42023046	Jisas re yaye op tem. Apiy, ari wow an neri letke rasye. Op wen re ek sam.
42023047	Nause yen etemri keryen yen re er wos lam, re God reri sig bukre wen re op wem. Er tame re tame yenbo sekenewai.
42023048	Nugwape tatame rem etek rene late yam, rem lam, re sam. Rem etop lam, rem pap yaper ten rem sene yikwetem.
42023049	Jisas reri tametiykene Galilike yan rene semowem takene rem yan kaike kera teten rem er wos lam.
42023050	Tame wuri, reri sig Josep, re temenem. Juda etemri kwom wuri, Arimatea, re er kwomri tame. Re tame yenbowai. Re Juda keryen tame etemri wuri.
42023051	Kiyi Juda keryen tame rem Jisas rene pen sate wem, re kirkir be wem. God re kwom panen site, re etop kowmenem.
42023052	Re Pailet rene lasyin Jisas reri kupa potte rene wemetem.
42023053	Pailat re kirkir wem, Josep re yin kupa neneyeren poten sen yin wulkap matek leirasen selek rasem. Er sele rem pa purik nenem, kiyi rem tame kupa be wuri etek be rasmenem.
42023054	Rene rasem yabel et awos heyarbem yabel. Egesi Yabel tete nenbem.
42023055	Galilike yam ta, kiyi Jisas rekene yam ta, rem Josep eterkene yin sele lam. Jisas reri kupa rasem emi rem lam.
42023056	Rem remri akek sene yin bos yenbo yabo kwarkene agerbo bos yabo woskene Jisas reri kupak kerete rem heyarem. Egesi Yabel rem God eterri wule habom, rem bupo me sim, rem yaku be nenem.
42024001	Kwokwos ei berabemke, ta rem remri kiyi heyarem boskene kwar poten sen selek yim.
42024002	Yin lam, pa puri ragerem pa sene gelkwun yin op yokwok temenem.
42024003	Rem yin wuren rem Haneyen Jisas reri kupa laweyem.
42024004	Rem op habo op habom, rem wor tem. Agetage rem lam, tame pes, repri tame oub me malebem, rep meknik yan tetemenem.
42024005	Ta rem etop lan aken rem selke warem. Tame pes rep remne op wem. Mapurke kem kelpe tame rene sa tame etemri emik sopte yawo?
42024006	Re gwor be tetane. Re sene wayen siye. Re kemne wem tuma kem sene habo. Kiyi re kemkene Galilike temenem, re kemne op wem.
42024007	An More Tame Tem Tame, rem anne yaper nenbo tame remri letke raste, rem anne me kwuren peikkerete, an sate. Yabel murwe an sene wayen site.
42024008	Rem Jisas reri kiyi wem tuma sene habopitim.
42024009	Rem sele mesegenen sene yan letpeis tewo wuri kerem tame remne agerbo tame remne remri lam wos remne wesowem.
42024010	Ta rem Makdala kwomri ta, Maria, etet, Joana etet, Jems eterri nawo, Maria, etet. Etem, agerbo takene rem etop tetemenem, rem Jisas Eterri Werasen Yi Tame remne tuma wesowem.
42024011	Jisas eterri Werasen Yi Tame rem op habom. Ta rem tuma bupo me yikokobo. Rem remri tuma omuteke be metem.
42024012	Pita re teten amen selek yim. Re gurowmen niruw wurem, re lam, matewou temenem. Re akek sene yim, reri lam wos, reri metem tuma re op habo op habom.
42024013	Er yabelke tame pes rep etemri tame tep rep Jerusalem meknik tetane kwom eisowke yibem. Kwom sig et Emeus.
42024014	Yibem, Jisas eterne nenem tuma rep etopwou namren yibem.
42024015	Jisas re yan repne bogen etepkene yibem.
42024016	Rep rene lam, rep rene heyar be lam.
42024017	Re repne op wem. Kep yibo, kep be tuma kerepwou namrebo? Op wemke, rep elen me teten pap yaper ten bitmi girbus potem.
42024018	Tame wuri, reri sig Kliopes, re tuma sein op wem. Agerbo agerbo kwom tame nugwape rem yan Jerusalemke tetane, yeki tem wos rem lam. Nerenwou yeki tem wos ne be latene o be mettene.
42024019	Jisas re op wemetem. Be wos? Rep sein op wem. Nasaretri Jisas rene nenem wos. Re yaku bukre nenbem, nemne tuma yenbo wesowbem. God eter, tatame etem rem rene tame yenbo wem.
42024020	God Reri Kwoborri keryen yen, nemri keryen tame rem rene Pailet eterne panen yin tuma nenem, rem rene pen sate natobom, rem rene me kwuren ek peikkerem.
42024021	Er tame, kiyi nem op habom. Kap eter tame re kap Israel tatame remri peiktame remne teitkwunte. Op habom. Rem rene yekik pem, gwopte yabel mur weye.
42024022	Gwopte nem nemri rane ta remri tuma metye, nem danekene sekeye. Ei beraye, rem selek yiwo.
42024023	Rem Jisas reri kupa laweiwo. Rem sene yan nemne op weye. Nem God reri kwom tame pes laye. Rep nemne op weye. Jisas re wow sene potye.
42024024	Nemri tame tep rem selek yiwo, rem ta remri weye wos laye. Eterne rem be laye. Op wem.
42024025	Jisas re repne op wem. Kep purerekene bo. Kiyiri tuma wesowbem tame remri tuma kep sene be habobo.
42024026	Kap kep be mettene, Krais, God Eterri Lebam Tame, re mus kiyi mette, yuri re hadebaswai tete. Opkap er tuma re sekene tem.
42024027	Jisas re repne God reri eterne basrasem tuma repne wesowem. Moses reri basrasem tuma re kiyi wen yim, sene tuma wesowbem tame remri basrasem tuma sene wesowem.
42024028	Rem yin tame pes repri temenem kwom meknik yabem, Jisas re kerakap sene yite habom.
42024029	Rep rene keikeren op wem. Ne neskene gwotek tete. Yabel warbo, neir tekten yabo. Re wuren etepkene tem.
42024030	Rem awos ate nenbem, Jisas re etepkene sin re geil poten God rene pir wen belokteyewon repne newom.
42024031	Op nenem, repri le welepen rep rene heyar lam, re agetage yim, rep rene be lam.
42024032	Rep etopwou etopwou op wem. Nem kelowke yawo, re nesne God reri basrasem tuma tobo nesne wesowye, nesri pap teteye. Rep op wem.
42024033	Rep agetage Jerusalemke sene yim. Yin lam, letpeis tewo wuri kere anepoi tame, agerbo tamekene rem wuriwouke wuren temenem.
42024034	Rem op wem. Sekenewai. Haneyen re selek sene wayewo. Saimon re rene laye.
42024035	Op wemke, rep remne tuma wesowem. Rep Jisas rene kelowke lan akek panen yim, re geil poten belokteyewom, rep rene heyar ek lam. Rep remne etop wesowem.
42024036	Rep tuma wesowbem, rem lam, Jisas re etemri borborke mepen re remne pir wem.
42024037	Rem danekene seken rem aken op habom. Kap nem gambo wuri laye.
42024038	Re remne op wem. Berke kem op habo op haboye? Berke kem wuribai pes teye?
42024039	Kem la. Ari let tewo kem la. Gwor aren. Kem anne let kerelate. Ekla. An wesomkene. Gambo etem rem wesomkene bo, rem tamekap bo.
42024040	Re reri let tewo remne peteram.
42024041	Peteram, rem okbopsubu tem, rem rene omuteke be habobem, rem op habo op habobem. Kap Jisas eter? Opkap re remne wemetem. Kem kap awos tetane o awos bo?
42024042	Rem rene remri lisem omyen tep newom.
42024043	Re poten etemri bitmik am.
42024044	Re remne op wem. Kiyi an keremkene temenem, an kemne er tuma op wem. Nugwape tuma rem kiyi anne basrasem, re sekene tete tetane. Moses eterri siglowri tuma, tuma wesowbem tame etemri siglowri tuma, Devit eterri siglowri tuma sekene tete tetane.
42024045	Op wemke, rem meten God reri basrasem tuma heyar metem.
42024046	Re remne op wem. Siglowri tuma op webo. Krais, God eter lebam tame, re mus bukre mette, yabel murwe re sene wayen site tetane.
42024047	Tatame rem Krais eterri kitimenak tuma wesowte tetane. Rem Jerusalemke kiyi wetek, yuri rem agerbo agerbo kwomke yin op wete. Kem keremri sebera ya wos mesegente, God re keremkene kelmenate.
42024048	Kem er wos lam, kem yin wesowte.
42024049	Metye. Apiy re kiyi wem, re Eterri Wow kemne newote. An rene, kemne weraste nenbo. Kem gwor kwom sagke sin kowen God reri kitimena potte. Jisas re op wem.
42024050	Jisas re op wemke, re remne Betani kwomke panen yim, re reri let nenewayen God rene wemetem, re remne heyar nente.
42024051	God re remne heyar nente wemke, God re rene potem, re God reri kwom Hevenke yawum.
42024052	Yawum, rem reri sig bukre wem, rem okbopsubu ten Jerusalemke sene yim.
42024053	Kwokwos kwokwos rem God Eterri Kwoborke yin God rene pir wen rene tuma yenbo webem.
43001001	Kiyisapewai nelkene nowselkene be temenem, Tuma re temenem. Tuma re God eterkene temenem.
43001002	Kiyisapewai Tuma re God rekene temenem.
43001003	Eterke God re aboyei wos ek nenem. Be wos bupo be wuri tem. Krais eterke re aboyei ek nenem.
43001004	Heyar somsom temenbo wule eterke tetane. Heyar somsom temenbo wule re tatame remne tuwkap kerem. Tatame remri wuribai yenbo potte wule ek tem.
43001005	Er tuw re kerneirke temenem tatame remne keremenem. Kerneirke temenem tatame rem rene be sanem.
43001006	God re tame wuri rene werasen yam, reri sig Jon.
43001007	Tuwkap kerebo Tame rene re tatame remne wesowte yam. Reri tuma mette tatame rem Jisas rene omuteke habote.
43001008	Jon eter re tuwkap kerebo Tame bo. Re tuwkap kerebo Tame eterne wesowte yam.
43001009	Jisas eter re kerebo tuw sekenewai. Re aboyei tatame remne wuribai yenbo newobo tame. Eter re nowselke yam.
43001010	Kiyi God re Krais eterke nowselkene tatamekene nenem. Yuri re yan tatame etemkene temenem, rem rene be metmenem.
43001011	Re reri maime Juda nowselke yam, er nowselri tatame rem rene pap be yewom.
43001012	Rane rem rene pap yewom, er tatame rem rene omuteke habobem, eker God re remne op wem. Kem areri yen.
43001013	Er tatame rem God reri yen bupo be tem. Nowselri wulek rem God reri yen be tem. Mare bisi yibo wulek rem God reri yen be tem. Nawoha etepri wuribaike rem God reri yen be tem. Yehow. God eterri purere wuribaike rem God reri yen sekene tem.
43001014	Tuma re tame tem, re neremkene temenem. Nem reri kitimena bukre, reri sig bukre lam. Et sig et Apiy God eter werasem Yen. Re God Eterri Wuriwou Yen. Pap meten kwobo labo wulekene wule sekenekene et eterkene temenem.
43001015	Jon re Jisas rene habon re tatame nugwape remne ten op wesowem. Er tame rene an kemne kiyi wesowem. An kemne op wem. Ari nawiy te anne kiyi wurem. Agerbo tame wuri reri nawot te rene yuri wurem. Er tame re anne teitkwuntene. An be yamenem, er tame re temenem.
43001016	Jisas re pap bukre meten kwobo labo tame. Eker re nemne kwokwos kwokwos heyarwai nenbo.
43001017	God reri wule letpeis re Moses rene newom, Moses re er wule tatame remne newom. God reri pap meten kwobo labo wule, reri tuma sekene, Jisas Krais eter re nemne newom.
43001018	Yike God rene be latene. Yehow. God Eterri Yen wuriwou re God, eter re eterkene tetane. Eterwou re Har rene nemne heyar peterabem.
43001019	Juda tame rem wuribai pasupem, rem God reri akek yaku nenbem tamekene rane Livai tamekene remne werasem. Rem Jerusalem kwom pelebiten Jon rene lasyin op wemetem. Jon, ne yike sekene?
43001020	Op wemetem, re tuma ribo be tem, re tuma tegek wesowem, re remne sein op wem. God eter lebam tame, Krais, re Keryen Yen bukre. An eterkap bokem.
43001021	Rem rene sene wemetem. Ne yike? Ne Elaija, God reri kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame? Jon re sein op wem. Yehow. An eter bo. Rem rene sene wemetem. Nem God Reri Tuma wesow tame rene kowtene. Ne eter o bo? Re sein op wem. Yehow. An agerbo tame.
43001022	Rem rene sene wemetem. Ne yike? Nemne werasye tame remne nem tuma sein mapurke wete? Opkap ne neri nenbokap nemne wesowte.
43001023	Jon re remne sein op wem. God reri kiyiri temenem tuma wesowbem tame, Aisaia, eter wemkap, an etop nenbo. Aisaia re kiyi op wem. An tamekene bo emik yaye op webo. Kem Haneyen reri yate kelow heyarte. Jon re etop wem.
43001024	Farisi tame rem er tame remne werasen yam.
43001025	Rem Jon rene sene wemetem. Ne weye, ne God eter lebam tame bo, ne Elaija bo, ne God Reri Tuma wesowbo tame bo. Opkap, berke ne tatame remne okke waren tirmunbo?
43001026	Jon re remne sein op wem. An tatame remne okke waren tirmunbo. Ari nenbo yaku et bukre bo. Tame wuri re keremkene tetane, kem rene be latene.
43001027	Re reri yaku tobotate nenbo. Re tame bukre, re tame yenbo. An tame eisow. An tame yenbo bo, nes wolbaye wurik be site. An eisow yen, an selke site.
43001028	Jon re er tuma Betani kwomke wesowem. Betani kwom et Jordan peik kelaruwke tetane. Jon re tatame remne etek okke waren tirmunbem.
43001029	Kwokwos Jisas re kelowke yabem, Jon re rene lan op wem. Ekla. Er tame re God Eterri Sipsip Yen. Jisas re nowselri tatame aboyei remne kwobo lan remri yaper nen wos poten septite.
43001030	Er tame kiyi an kemne op wem. Ari nawiy te anne kiyi wurem, agerbo tame wuri reri nawot te rene yuri wurem. Kiyisapewai re God eterri kwomke temenem, opkap an rene areri Haneyen webo. An etop kiyi webem.
43001031	Kiyi an rene be metmenem, re yike. Tatame rem er tame rene heyar mette, eker an yan Juda tatame remne okke waren tirmunbem.
43001032	Jon re sene op wem. An op lam, God Reri Wow re Heven mesegenen bour apkap re yan yeren Jisas eterke sim.
43001033	An rene be metmenem. God re anne werasen tatame remne okke waren tirmunte werasem. God re anne op wem. Ari Wow re ari kwom mesegenen yeren tame wuri rene yin site. Er tame re God Reri Wow tatame remne newote. Re anne etop wem.
43001034	An etop lam, eker an kemne webo. Er tame re God Eterri Yen sekene.
43001035	Kwokwos Jon re reri anepoi tame peskene rem etek sene temenem.
43001036	Jisas re yibem, Jon re rene lan op wem. Ekla. God Sipsip Yes re gwor.
43001037	Jon reri anepoi tame pes rep op metem, rep Jisas rene semowen yim.
43001038	Jisas re repne petkwolam, rep rene semowmenem, re repne op wemetem. Kep berke yabo? Rep rene sein op wem. Rabai, ne mar akek tetane? Rabai reri tobo et Tuma Peikbo Tame.
43001039	Jisas re repne op wem. Kep yan late. Op wemke, rep yin Jisas reri temenem ake lam. Rep perpek yin lan eterkene sin tektem.
43001040	Tame pes, rep Jon reri wem tuma meten Jisas rene semowen yim tame pes, wuri reri sig Andru. Re Saimon Pita eterri mase.
43001041	Andru re Jisas rene mesegenen agetage re Saimon rene yin lan op wem. Nem agerbo tamekene nem Mesaia rene laye. Mesaia reri tobo et Krais, God Eter Lebam Tame.
43001042	Op wem, Andru re Saimon rene panen Jisas rene lasyim. Jisas re Saimon rene lan op wem. Ne Saimon, Jon eterri yen. Yuri rem neri sig Sifas wete. Op wem. Juda tame remri tumak rem Sifas webo. Grik tumak op webo. Pita. Sig tobo et pa.
43001043	Kwokwos Jisas re Galili yokwok yite wem, re Filip rene lan op wem. Ne arenkene yite.
43001044	Filip re Betsaida kwomri tame. Re Andrukene Pitakene etepri kwom tame.
43001045	Sene Filip re Nataniel rene sopen yin lan rene op wem. Moses re Juda nemne wule siglowke basrasem, re God reri lebam tame rene kirkir basbasem. Kiyi temenem tuma wesowbem tame etem mere basrasem. Er tame rene nem laye. Re Nasaret kwomri tame. Re Jisas, Josep eterri yen.
43001046	Nataniel re rene op wem. Nasaret et kwom yaper. God reri lebam tame, Krais, re er kwomke be tete. Filip re rene sein op wem. Ne opu yan la.
43001047	Jisas re lam, Nataniel re yabem, re rene op wem. Ekla. Israel tame yenbo re yabo. Re tuma be wuri yikokobo.
43001048	Nataniel re rene op wemetem. Ne anne mapurke laye? Jisas re rene sein op wem. Kiyi Filip re nene be wemenye, ne yipige me somok simenye, an nene ek laye.
43001049	Nataniel re rene tuma sein op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne God Eterri Yen. Ne Israel kwom panen si Keryen Yen.
43001050	Jisas re rene tuma sein op wem. An nene op weye. Ne yipige me somok simenye, an nene ek laye. Op weye, ne anne agetage omuteke haboye. An nene etop weye, et eisow wos. Yuri ne ari kitimena bukre late tetane.
43001051	An kemne tuma sekene webo. Yuri kem late, God reri kwomri eru tagworaste, reri kwomri tame rem More Tame Tem Tame eterke wuyerbet tetane.
43002001	Yabel pes tem, murwuk tame wuri re ta panem. Galili yokwori kwom, Kana, etek panem. Jisas reri nawo te ta pane kisbem akek temenem.
43002002	Rem Jisas rene kirkir wemetem, re reri anepoi tamekene rem ta pane kisbem awos ate yam.
43002003	Tatame nugwape rem sin abem, wain ok legem. Jisas reri nawo te rene op wem. Rem wain ok bo.
43002004	Jisas re tene sewayen op wem. Nawiy, et nereri wos. Yurik an kitimenakene bukre wos ek nente. Gwopte bo.
43002005	Te awos nenbem tame remne op wem. Jisas re kemne be wos wuri nente wete, kem meten etop nente.
43002006	Juda tatame remri wule rem let ok keyan awos ek abem. Eker, rem er ake ou bukre letrane kelare wuri kere etek tukmenem. Er ou bukre wulare wulare rem ok nugwape, 100 lita, yewon pulaubem.
43002007	Jisas re awos nenbem tame remne op wem. Kem er ou letrane kelare wuri kere ok etek tin pulaute. Op wem, rem ok tin pulawen tukruwem.
43002008	Re remne sene op wem. Ware wuri kem poten sen yin awos lakere tame rene newon alate. Op wem, rem ware wuri poten tin sen yin newom.
43002009	Awos lakere tame re er ok alam, er ok re wain ok sekene tem. Remri ok tim emi re be lam. Re ta panem tame rene wepotem.
43002010	Re rene op wem. Neren yuri newoye wain ok et yenbowai. Nugwape tatame rem gesa tebo, rem tokwo bukrek tupabo wain ok kiyi newopiti pete yabo. Tatame rem nugwape wain ok an sisi pebo, yuri rem tokwo eisowke tupabo wain ok remne sene ek newon abo. Neri nemne nenbo wule yenbowai. Neri tokwo bukrek tupam wain ok ne yuri sen yan nemne newoye.
43002011	Jisas re temnas yi kitimenakene yaku bukre tobotan nenem. Re Galili yokwok temenem kwom, Kana, etek nenem. Re reri sigkene kitimenakene tatame remne etek peteram. Reri anepoi tame rem reri kitimena lam, rem rene omuteke habobem.
43002012	Jisas re Kana kwom mesegenen Kaperneam kwomke warem. Reri nawo, mase, reri anepoi tame rem kirkir etop warem. Rane yabel rem eter kwom sagke temenem.
43002013	God Re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tatame Remri Letke Sene Potem Habom Yabel matnamke, Jisas re Jerusalemke yim.
43002014	Re God Reri Kwoborke wuren lam, tame nugwape rem kel pot yaku etek nenbem. Rem kwar pete bulmakau, sipsip, ap sen yan tatame rem tupabem. Rane rem tiyke sin agerbo nowselri kel natokwo tupabem.
43002015	Jisas re rewo guli poten remne wurbeten wukroken yim. Sipsipkene bulmakaukene remne kirkir wukrokem. Re natokwe tupabem tame remri kel rasbem tiy poten legalen petem, kel rem aboyei panbilen pitim.
43002016	Ap tupabem kel potbem tame remne re op wem. Kem poten yikute. Gwor kwobor et areri Apiy Eterri Kwobor. Kem kel gwok mane natokwo tupate.
43002017	Op wemke, reri anepoi tame rem God reri basrasem tuma wuri sene habom. Basrasem tuma op webo. Apiy God, neri kwobor an metekwasbo, eker an yaku bukre nenen heyar lakerebo, kwobor re heyar temente. Er tuma rem etop habom.
43002018	Sene Juda tame rem Jisas reri gwule lan rene op wemetem. Nene yike wemke, ne remne wukrokye? Ne nemne kitimenakene bukre wos peterate, nem nene tuma be wete.
43002019	Jisas re remne sein op wem. Kem God Reri Kwobor berayewote, yabel murwu, an sene nente.
43002020	Juda rem op wem. Gwor kwobor rem nenem, nabe nugwape (46) rem yaku nenen legem. Yabel murwu ne kebese sene be nente.
43002021	Jisas re God Reri Kwobor wem, re eterri kworer wesom habon eker wem. Yuri re sate, yabel mur tete, re sene wow poten wayen site.
43002022	Yuri God re Jisas rene wow sene newom, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem Jisas reri wem tuma sene habopitim, rem God reri siglowke basrasem tuma omuteke habom, rem Jisas reri wem tuma kirkir omuteke habom.
43002023	God re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tame Remri Letke Sene Potem Yabel, Jisas re Jerusalemke temenem, re kitimenakene bukre wos nugwape nenbem. Nugwape tatame rem etop lam, rem Jisas rene omuteke habom.
43002024	Jisas re remri tuma omuteke be habom.
43002025	Re aboyei tatame remri wulekene wuribaikene lamenem. Rene agerbo yenke be wesowte.
43003001	Tame wuri reri sig Nikodemus, re Farisi tame. Re Juda remri temnas tame wuri.
43003002	Er tame re Jisas rene neirke lasyin op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, nem mettene, God re nene werasen yam, ne nemne tuma peikbo. Ne wos kitimenakene bukre nenbo, opkap nem mettene, God re nerenkene tetane.
43003003	Jisas re rene tuma sein op wem. An nene sekeneker webo. Tame rem wuribai ager be potte, rem God reri kwomke be yite tetane.
43003004	Nikodemus re rene sein op wem. Tame re ker tebo, mapurke re wuribai ager potte.
43003005	Jisas re rene tuma sein op wem. An nene sekeneker webo. Tatame rem okke be tirmunte, rem God Reri Wow be potte, rem agerbo wuribai be potte, rem God reri kwomke be yite.
43003006	Ta te yen rene warwite, re nowselri tame tete. God Reri Wow re tatame remne gurerete, rem God reri yen tete.
43003007	Ari nene weye tuma ne danekene kap sekete. Ne agerbo purere potte, ne God reri kwomke yite.
43003008	Poli re reri purerek agerbo agerbo emik yibo. Poli reri ken ne metbo, ne be labo, re mak yibo o mak yabo. Etopkap God Reri Wow re agerbo agerbo tatame remne gurerebo, rem wuribai yenbo potbo.
43003009	Nikodemus re Jisas rene sein op wem. Er tuma tobo re mapkap?
43003010	Jisas re rene sein op wem. Ne Israel remri tuma peikbo tame. Mapurke ne tuma tobo be mettene?
43003011	An nene sekeneker webo. Nemri metbo wos, nemri labo wos nem etop wesowbo. Nemri wesowbo tuma kem omuteke be habobo.
43003012	Nemri nowselke labo wos an kemne etop wesowbo, kem omuteke be metbo. Eker Hevenke tetane wos an kemne wesowte, kem mapurke omuteke mette?
43003013	Yike tatame rem God reri kwomke be wuri yautene. Yehow. An More Tame Tem Tame, arenwou an God reri kwomke temenem. Er kwom an mesegenen ek yerem.
43003014	Kiyi Moses re tamekene bo emik temenem, re selke nenem sopo mek peiken nenewayen paruwem. Sikenuma nenbem tatame rem etop labem, rem be sabem, rem sene kwuye metbem. Etop nenbemkap, an More Tame Tem Tame, rem anne etop nente, rem anne mek nenewayen parute tetane.
43003015	Op nente, tatame rem anne omuteke habote, rem yaper be tete, rem heyar somsom temente tetane. Jisas re etop wem.
43003016	God re aboyei nowselri tatame remne pap yewom, re Reri Yen wuriwou rene werasen yam, re nowselri tatame remne kwobo lan sam. Tatame rem rene omuteke habote, rem yaper be tete, rem heyar somsom temente tetane.
43003017	God re reri yen rene werasen yam, re tatame etemne tuma nente boker yam. Re remne potte, rem pow tete tetane.
43003018	Tatame rem rene omuteke habote, God re remne tuma be nente. Tatame rem God Reri wuriwou Yen rene omuteke be habote, God re remne tuma bukre kiyi nenem.
43003019	Tuma nenbo tobo gwor. Tuwkap kerebo tame re nowselke yam. Nugwape tatame rem yaper nenbo, rem kerneirke tete habobo. Rem wule yaper nenbo, rem tuwkap kerebo tame rene muwebo.
43003020	Yaper wos nenbo tatame rem op habobo. Yaper nen wos nem kwom genike kap nenen tatame rem kap late. Eker rem tuwkap kerebo tame rene muwen rene amekwunbo.
43003021	Wule yenbo sekene nenbo tatame rem tuwkap kerebo tame rene omuteke habobo. Eker agerbo tatame rem labo, remri nenbokap et God eterri wemkap.
43003022	Yuri Jisas re reri anepoi tamekene rem Judia yokwok yim, rane yabel re etemkene etek temenem, re tatame remne okke waren tirmunbem.
43003023	Jon eter mere, re tatame remne Ainon kwomke okke waren tirmunbem. Ainon kwom et Salim kwom meknik tetane, nugwape ok etek tetane. Eker re remne etek okke waren tirmunbem. Tatame rem etek yan re remne okke waren tirmunbem.
43003024	Er yabel Keryen Yen Herot re Jon rene ake yaperke be wen wurmenem.
43003025	Juda tame wuri re Jon reri anepoi tame remkene naurem. Rem okke warbo tirmunbo wuleke naurem.
43003026	Sene Jon reri anepoi tame rem Jon rene lasyin op wemetem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, kiyi ne nemne Jisas rene wesowbem. Re kiyi nerenkene Jordan peik kelaruwke temenem. Eter mere, re tatame remne okke waren tirmunbo. Nugwape tatame rem eterkene yibo.
43003027	Jon re tuma sein op wem. Hevenke tetane God re tame wuri rene wos be wuri newote, er tame re wos be potte.
43003028	An kemne kiyi wem tuma kem metem. An op wem. An God eter lebam tame bo. God re anne werasen an kiyi temnas yam.
43003029	Metye. Tame re ta panebo, et ta te reri akek yin tebo, te rekene tuma etop namrebo. Ta panebo tame reri nowur re ta panebo tame rene labo, reri tuma metbo, re okbopsubuwai tebo. Nowu re okbop tebokap, an kirkir etop okbop tebo. Nugwape tatame rem Jisas rene lasyin eterkene temenbo, an okbop tebo.
43003030	Jisas reri sig bukre tete. Areri sig eisow tete, an etop selbo. Jon re etop wem.
43003031	God reri kwomke yam tame re keryen yen bukre. Agerbo keryen yen rem eisow. Nem nowselri tatame, nem nowselri wos habon wesowbo. More Tame Tem Tame re tame bukrewai. Re nowselri tame remne teitkwuntene.
43003032	God reri kwomke lan metem wos re wesowbo, tatame rem reri tuma omuteke be metbo.
43003033	Yike tatame rem Jisas reri tuma omuteke metbo, rem op webo. God re tetane.
43003034	God reri werasen yam tame re God Reri Tuma wesowbo. God re gesa be tebo, re reri Wow reri kitimena bukre aboyei rene newon re God reri kitimenak heyar wesowbo.
43003035	Apiy God re Reri Yen rene pap yewotene, re aboyei wos reri letke rasem.
43003036	Tatame rem God Reri Yen rene omuteke habote, rem heyar som temente tetane. Tatame rem reri tuma omuteke be mette, rem heyar somsom be temente tetane. God re remne pap som yokbet tetane.
43004001	Farisi tame rem metem, nugwape tatame rem Jon reri tuma omuteke meten re remne okke waren tirmunbem. Sene rem metem, tatame nugwapewai rem Jisas reri tuma omuteke meten okke waren tirmunbem.
43004002	Jisas eter re tatame remne okke be waren tirmunem. Reri anepoi tame rem tatame remne okke waren tirmunbem.
43004003	Jisas re metem, Farisi tame rem er tuma metem, eker re Judia yokwok pelebiten Galili yokwok sene yim.
43004004	Reri yibem kelow et Samaria yokwo borborke yibem.
43004005	Re Samaria yokwori kwom wurik yam. Kwom sig et Sikar. Kiyi temenem tame, Jekop, re reri yen Josep rene newom sel et eter kwom meknik tetane.
43004006	Jekop reri kiyi perem ok tibem okmei eter emik tetane. Yabel nina let kere temenem, Jisas re genek yam, re wos teselen re yan er okmei barke etek sim.
43004007	Jisas re simenem, Samaria ta wuri te ok tite yam. Jisas re tene op wem. Ne ok sen yan an ok ate.
43004008	Reri anepoi tame rem kiyi kwom sagke awos tupate yim.
43004009	Samaria ta te rene sein op wem. Ne Juda tame. An Samaria ta. Mapurke ne anne ok wemetbo? Juda remri wule gwopkap. Juda tatame rem Samariari tatame remkene awos wurik be sin abo. Eker te rene etop wemetem.
43004010	Jisas re ta tene tuma sein op wem. God re nene newote wos ne mette, nene ok wemetye tame ne anne mette, eker ne arenne ok wemette, an nene ok newon ate, ne heyar som temente tetane.
43004011	Ta te rene op wem. Haneyen, ne ok tite warekene bo. Gwor okmei ok re ukweiwai tetane. Tatame rem heyar som temente okmei ok ne mak tite?
43004012	Nemri warege, Jekop, re gwor okmei peren nemne mesegenem. Eter, reri yen etem, reri bulmakau etem rem gwor ok abem. Kap ne tame bukre, ne warege Jekop rene teitkwuntene.
43004013	Jisas re tene tuma sein op wem. Tatame rem gwor ok ate, yuri rem sene ok segete tetane.
43004014	Metye. Tatame rem ari newote ok ate, yuri rem ok sene be segete. An remne newote ok et som sekbo sekokkap. Rem ate, rem heyar somsom temente tetane.
43004015	Op wemke, ta te rene op wem. Haneyen, ne anne er ok newote. Yuri an ok sene be segete, an gwor okmeike ok sene be yan tite.
43004016	Jisas re tene op wem. Ne yin neri tame rene panen ya.
43004017	Ta te sein op wem. An tamekene bo. Jisas re tene op wem. Neri webo tuma et sekene. Ne tamekene bo.
43004018	Neri kiyi situkwem tame rem letrane. Sene nekene tetane tame re nereri tame sekene bo. Ne weye. An tamekene bo. Et sekenewai.
43004019	Ta te sebera yan rene op wem. Haneyen, an haboye, ne God Reri Tuma wesowbo tame. An nene tuma wuri wemette.
43004020	Nem Samariari tatame, nemri yeiwarege rem gwotek tetane kwowke yawun God rene lom yokwobem. Kem Juda, kem webo. Tatame rem Jerusalem kwomke yin God rene etek lom yokwote. Berke kem etop webo?
43004021	Jisas re tene sene op wem. Ta, ne ari tuma omuteke mette. Yuri tatame rem gwor kwowke be yawun Apiy God rene sene be lom yokwote. Rem Jerusalem kwomke be yin lom yokwote.
43004022	Kem Samariari tatame, kemri lom yokwobo tame rene kem be mettene. Kem bupo me lom yokwobo. Nem Juda, nem nemri lom yokwobo God rene heyar mettene, eker nem rene lom yokwobo. Aren an Juda tame. God re anne werasem, an nowselri tatame remne potte, rem pow tete tetane.
43004023	Apiy God re selbo, tatame rem wuribai yenbokene wule sekenekene rene lom yokwote. Re opkap tatame remne sopbo. Ekeya. Opkap tatame rem God rene welepe lom yokwote yabel matnaye. Gwopte rem etop nente.
43004024	God re wow. Eker, rene lom yokwobo tatame rem rene God Reri Wowkene wule sekenekene rene lom yokwote.
43004025	Ta te rene op wem. God reri lebam tame, nem rene Krais webo, re yate tetane, an etop mettene. Re yate, re nemne nugwape wos peterate tetane.
43004026	Jisas re tene op wem. Nekene tuma namrebo tame, aren, an Krais. Op wem.
43004027	Reri webem tuma agegekene, reri anepoi tame rem sene yam. Yan lan Jisas re ta tekene tuma namrebem, rem op habo op habom. Remri yike be wuri tene op be wemetem. Ne be wos wemetbo? O remri yike be wuri rene op wemetem. Berke ne tekene tuma namrebo?
43004028	Op tem, ta te teri ok tibem gin etek mesegenen kwom sagke sene yin kwomri tatame remne op wem.
43004029	Kem opu yan la. Tame wuri re ari kiyi nenbem anne ab wesowye. Re kap yike? Kap re God eter lebam tame?
43004030	Op wem, kwomri tatame rem etop metem, rem kwom sag mesegenen Jisas rene late yim.
43004031	Ta te tatame remne wete yimenem, Jisas reri anepoi tame rem rene op wem. Tuma Peikbo Tame, ne awos ate.
43004032	Re remne op wem. Ari tetane awos kem be latene.
43004033	Reri anepoi tame rem etemwou etemwou namrelan op wem. Kap tame wuri re awos sen yan newoye o bo?
43004034	Jisas re remne op wem. Ari Apiy re anne werasen yaku nente wem. Ari awos gwopkap. Anne werasen yam tame eter selbokap an etop nente, re anne newom yaku an nenen legete.
43004035	Kem op webo. Liyp eis legete, nem kwoi ek perte. An kemne op webo. Kem yin aboyei now lan sewurte. Kwoi rem okwon sitene.
43004036	God rene omuteke habobo wule wesowbo tatame remne God re heyar sein nenbo. Er omuteke habobo tatame rem heyar som temente. Etopkap, kwoi berbo tamekene kwoi perbo tamekene rem kirkir etop okbop tebo.
43004037	Sange tame rem op webo. Tame wuri re kwoi berbo, agerbo tame re kwoi perbo. Er tuma et sekene.
43004038	An kemne werasen yim, kem agerbo tame reri berem kwoi kem yin perte. Agerbo tame rem yaku bukre nenen rem kwoi berem. Sene kem yin remri berem kwoi perbo. Jisas re op wem.
43004039	Samaria kwom sagri tatame nugwape rem ta teri tuma metem. Te remne op wem. Jisas re ari kiyi nenbem wos anne wesowkeiye. Op wemke, tatame rem Jisas rene omuteke habom.
43004040	Op tem, Samaria tatame rem yan tewok tewok wemetem, Jisas re etemkene temente. Eker, yabel pes re eter kwomke temenem.
43004041	Sene nugwape tatame rem reri tuma sekene metem, rem rene omuteke habom.
43004042	Rem ta tene op wem. Nem neren wem tumawou boker omuteke meten nem er tame rene omuteke haboye. Yehow. Nem reri tuma neremri wanke metem, eker nem webo, er tame re nowselri tatame remne potbo, rem pow tebo.
43004043	Yabel pes tem, Jisas re Samaria yokwo pelebiten Galili yokwok yim.
43004044	Jisas re kiyi op wem. Tuma wesow tame remri maime kwomri tatame rem remne yenbo be webo, rem remne magel taibo.
43004045	Galili yokwok yim, Galiliri tatame rem rene pap yewom. Kiyi er tatame rem God Re Israel Tatame Remne Isip Tatame Remri Letke Sene Potem Habon Awos Abo Yabel awos Jerusalemke ate yim. Jisas re awos abem yabelke nenemkap rem aboyei lam, rem okbop tem. Eker, Jisas re remri kwomke yam, rem rene pap yewom.
43004046	Re Galili yokwok tetane kwom Kana etek yim. Kiyi re etek temenem, re wemke, kelpok re sene wain ok yenbo tem. Er kwomri keryen yen reri yaku nen tame reri yen re yaper bukre meten Kaperneam kwomke temenem.
43004047	Er keryen tame re metem, Jisas re Judia yokwo pelebiten Galilike yam. Op metem, re Jisas rene lasyin rene tewok tewok op wemetem. Ari yen re sate nenbo. Ne Kaperneamke yin rene heyarte.
43004048	Jisas re rene sein op wem. An agerbo agerbo kitimenakene bukre wos be nente, kem anne omuteke be habote.
43004049	Keryen tame re rene op wem. Haneyen, ne arenkene yite. Ari yen kap sate.
43004050	Jisas re rene op wem. Ne opu yi. Neri yen re be sate. Tame re Jisas reri tuma omuteke meten ek yim.
43004051	Re kelowke som yibemke, reri yaku nen tame rem rene kelowke lasyan op wem. Neri yen reri yaper boiwo. Re kwoye metye.
43004052	Re remne op wemetem. Re makapke kwuye metem? Rem rene sein op wem. Yere re yaper metmenem, yabel me pen wuri temenemke, re ek kwuye metem.
43004053	Op wemke, har re habopitim. Yere gwotepkap yabelke Jisas re op wem. Neri yen re be sate. Eker re reri yentakene rem Jisas rene omuteke habom.
43004054	Jisas re Judia yokwok pelebiten Galili yokwok yan temenemke, re er yen rene heyarem, et eter tewo peswe nenem kitimenakene bukre wos.
43005001	Yuri Juda remri Egesi Yabel bukre tete nenbemke, Jisas re Jerusalemke yin yawum.
43005002	Jerusalem kwom ser bukre peikmenem. Er ser reri eru wuri rem op webo. Sipsip Eru. Okmei wuri eter eru meknik temenem. Okmei sig rem Hibru tumak op webo. Betesda. Okmei barke egesibem ake tiytare letrane etek temenem.
43005003	Nugwape sikanuma nen tame rem etek tuknamenem. Rane rem lesi tame, rane tewo yaper te tame, rane tewo negel met tame, rem er ake tiy tarek tuknan ok leklek tebem. (Leklek tebem, rem ok nina kowmenem.
43005004	Rane yabel God reri kwomri tame wuri re okmeike yeren ok nina saberbem, kiyi temnas warbem tame remri sikanuma agetage legebem.)
43005005	Tame wuri re etek tuknan kowmenem, rene nenbem sikanuma nabe et nugwape (38).
43005006	Nabe nugwape re etek tuknan kowmenem. Jisas re op lam, re rene op wemetem. Ne sene yenbo tete selye o bo?
43005007	Sikenuma nen tame re rene sein op wem. Haneyen, ok nina yate, anne yike tamek poten okke panen warte? An warte seilabo, agerbo tame rem kiyi agetage warbo, anne gwotek mesegenbo.
43005008	Jisas re rene op wem. Ne opu wayen teten neri tukna wos poten sen yi.
43005009	Agetage re kwuye metem, re reri tukna wos poten sen akwulke yim. Op tem yabel et Juda etemri Egesi Yabel.
43005010	Juda tame rem op lam, rem gwule tem, rem kwuye metem tame rene sewayen op wem. Gwopte Egesi Yabel. Ne tukna wos mane poten sen yite. Ne op nente, ne nemri wule biragiyebo.
43005011	Re remne sein op wem. Anne heyarye tame eter anne werasye.
43005012	Rem rene op wemetem. Yike nene weye, ne neri tukna wos poten sen yite?
43005013	Kwuye metem tame re Jisas rene heyar be lam. Re rene soplaweyem. Nugwape tatame rem temenem, Jisas re yim, eker re Jisas rene soplaweyem.
43005014	Yuri Jisas re God Reri Kwoborke wuren re kwuye metem tame rene etek lan rene op wem. Gwopte ne kwuye meten heyar teye. Ne kiyi nenem wule yaper sene kap nente. Ne yaper wos sene nente, nugwape yaper wos bukre nene sene tete tetane.
43005015	Op wem, kwuye metem tame re yin Juda tame remne op wesowem. Anne heyar nenye tame re Jisas.
43005016	Jisas re er tame rene Egesi Yabelke heyar nenem, eker Juda rem saberen Jisas rene yaper nenbem.
43005017	Jisas re Juda remne sein op wem. Ari Apiy re yaku kwokwos kwokwos nenbo. Opkap aren mere, an etop nenbo.
